 are doing good.\r\n\r\nWith every other ad platform - Facebook, Google, Twitter, Yahoo, you name it - people are turned off by advertising. They don\'t want it. They didn\'t say \"yes\" to the ads, even if they said \"yes\" to the product or service.\r\n\r\nRight now we are preparing to populate our app with ads. Most large brands and ad agencies need us to have a large user base before they will even consider advertising with us, so like many organizations we have the \"Chicken or the egg\" dilemma.\r\n\r\nWe are currently offering great discounted ad packages - send us an email - ads (at) getadora.com<strong> to start the process.</strong>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWL6X2G4C68\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Advertising','','publish','open','closed','','ads','','','2015-02-11 22:36:50','2015-02-11 22:36:50','',0,'http://getadora.com/?page_id=51',2,'page','',0),(895,1,'2015-02-11 22:36:04','2015-02-11 22:36:04','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-591  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a> <a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-592  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a>Adora Advertising is different for one HUGE reason... When anyone looks at our ads they KNOW they are doing good.\r\n\r\nWith every other ad platform - Facebook, Google, Twitter, Yahoo, you name it - people are turned off by advertising. They don\'t want it. They didn\'t say \"yes\" to the ads, even if they said \"yes\" to the product or service.\r\n\r\nRight now we are preparing to populate our app with ads. Most large brands and ad agencies need us to have a large user base before they will even consider advertising with us, so like many organizations we have the \"Chicken or the egg\" dilemma.\r\n\r\nWe are currently offering great discounted ad packages - <strong>fill out the interest form below and we\'ll contact you to start the process.</strong>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWL6X2G4C68\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Advertising','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2015-02-11 22:36:04','2015-02-11 22:36:04','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(823,4,'2014-12-03 09:21:10','2014-12-03 09:21:10','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-591  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a> <a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-592  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a>Adora Advertising is different for one HUGE reason... When anyone looks at our ads they KNOW they are doing good.\r\n\r\nWith every other ad platform - Facebook, Google, Twitter, Yahoo, you name it - people are turned off by advertising. They don\'t want it. They didn\'t say \"yes\" to the ads, even if they said \"yes\" to the product or service.\r\n\r\nRight now we are preparing to populate our app with ads. Most large brands and ad agencies need us to have a large user base before they will even consider advertising with us, so like many organizations we have the \"Chicken or the egg\" dilemma.\r\n\r\nWe are currently offering great discounted ad packages through our Indiegogo campaign. Visit our campaign and be one of the first to support us.\r\n\r\n<strong>You can also fill out the interest form below and we\'ll contact you to start the process.</strong>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWL6X2G4C68\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Advertising','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-12-03 09:21:10','2014-12-03 09:21:10','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(720,6,'2014-11-21 01:38:37','2014-11-21 01:38:37','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-591  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a> <a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-592  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a>Adora Advertising is different for one HUGE reason... When anyone looks at our ads they KNOW they are doing good.\r\n\r\nWith every other ad platform - Facebook, Google, Twitter, Yahoo, you name it - people are turned off by advertising. They don\'t want it. They didn\'t say \"yes\" to the ads, even if they said \"yes\" to the product or service.\r\n\r\nRight now we are preparing to populate our app with ads. Most large brands and ad agencies need us to have a large user base before they will even consider advertising with us, so like many organizations we have the \"Chicken or the egg\" dilemma.\r\n\r\nThis is where you get the deal...! We are offering small and medium sized B2C startups/businesses the opportunity to secure excellent advertising at a great price.\r\n\r\nRight now, through November 24th<em>,</em> you can test our platform for <strong>FREE</strong>. We are giving away two different ad packages:\r\n\r\nSmall Biz Pack -        10,000 impressions\r\nMedium Biz Pack -   100,000 impressions\r\n\r\n<strong>Fill out the interest form below and we\'ll contact you to start the process.</strong>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWL6X2G4C68\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Advertising','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-11-21 01:38:37','2014-11-21 01:38:37','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(535,1,'2014-09-30 22:01:56','2014-09-30 22:01:56','','Adora Advertising','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-09-30 22:01:56','2014-09-30 22:01:56','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(536,1,'2014-09-30 22:09:43','2014-09-30 22:09:43','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/AffiliateProgram.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-595 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/AffiliateProgram.jpg\" alt=\"AffiliateProgram\" width=\"470\" height=\"394\" /></a>Hi, welcome to our info page on the Adora Affiliate Program.\r\n\r\nWe want you to promote our app along with causes and charities that are important to you, to your customers, lists, blog readers, social networking followers, and anyone else or through any other avenue where you have a voice. In return for this you have two amazing rewards:\r\n\r\nYou\'ll feel great knowing you\'ve helped do more good through Adora and that is a great feeling, but...\r\nWe all know that an Affiliate Program needs to help you in return financially so...\r\n\r\nWe have one of, if not the best, affiliate programs available: Depending on your reach and how you come to us you can get <em>up to*</em> <strong>$2.00 </strong>per user per month for up to 6 months--how long depends on how soon you become an affiliate.\r\n\r\nYour users will need to download the Adora App. It\'s free. And as long as they keep using the app, you can earn your reward bonuses. Our Affiliate Program is expected to change dramatically as