ards:\r\n\r\nYou\'ll feel great knowing you\'ve helped do more good through Adora and that is a great feeling, but...\r\nWe all know that an Affiliate Program needs to help you in return financially so...\r\n\r\nWe have one of, if not the best, affiliate programs available:\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">You get <em>up to*</em> <strong>$2.50 </strong>per user per month for up to 12 months--how long depends on how soon you become an affiliate.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Those who sign up before Dec 1st will keep their reward bonuses for 12 months</li>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Those who sign up on December 1st or later will keep their reward bonuses for 6 months</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYour users will need to download the Adora App. It\'s free. And as long as they keep using the app, you can earn your reward bonuses. Our Affiliate Program is expected to change dramatically in 2015, but any affiliate who signs up before the December 17th deadline will be able to continue adding users through 2015.\r\n\r\n<em>*up to $2.50 means that how much you make per user depends on how often your customers use their phone.</em>\r\n\r\nOur app is coming out soon, but our advertising will not begin until <em>late October / early November</em>. We pay our affiliates after we get paid by the advertisers, so you can expect your first payment from Adora to come around the 1st of January 2015.\r\n\r\nTo get started fill out this form and we\'ll register you into our affiliate program.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRW5XG6L3866\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','536-revision-v1','','','2014-11-20 22:12:10','2014-11-20 22:12:10','',536,'http://getadora.com/536-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(537,1,'2014-09-30 22:09:43','2014-09-30 22:09:43','','Adora Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','536-revision-v1','','','2014-09-30 22:09:43','2014-09-30 22:09:43','',536,'http://getadora.com/536-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(52,1,'2014-04-30 08:58:04','2014-04-30 08:58:04','<h2>Before We Jump In</h2>\r\nIt is always exciting and enlightening when you sit down and try to put together a plan. Vague ideas become polished, new ones develop, and issues come up that need to be overcome. This process helps a team find out if the idea is even a valid opportunity.\r\n\r\nWhen we were all young entrepreneurs, working on our first business plan, the horizon was always bright and simple. As we go about the execution of one plan after another we learn that planning is important but never perfect. We learn that while the horizon is always bright we know that the shadows below the horizon contain pit falls, challenges, storms, detours and sometimes you must completely turn around and backtrack.\r\n<h4></h4>\r\nWe want to create the best plan possible, but at the same time, let all of you who may be reading this know that we understand that any plan will change and more than likely change a lot.\r\n\r\nBecause we know that change is inevitable we are going to focus on the first 18 months, and even then we really only have control of the plan for the rest of 2014 (8+ months or so). Why? Because <strong>this app has the ability to explode,</strong> and we are only going to try and control growth for the first 3-5 months of the beta period. After that, after we release the full referral program, we have no idea how fast we will grow.','Plan','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 08:58:04','2014-04-30 08:58:04','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(53,1,'2014-10-03 23:04:23','2014-10-03 23:04:23','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-591 size-full alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"246\" height=\"515\" /></a> <a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-592  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a>Adora Advertising is different for one HUGE reason... When anyone looks at our ads they KNOW that they are doing good.\n\nWith ever other ad platform - Facebook, Google, Twitter, Yahoo, you name it - people are turned off by advertising, they don\'t want it, they didn\'t say yes to the ads even if they said yes to the product.\n\nRight now we are looking to populate our app with ads. Most large brands and ad agencies need us to have a large user base before they will even consider advertising with us, so like many organizations we have the \"Chicken or the egg\" dilemma.\n\nThis is where you get the deal...! We are offering small and medium sized B2C startups/businesses the opportunity to secure some great advertising at a great price.\n\nRight now, <em>for a limited time,</em> you can test our platform out for <strong>FREE</strong>. We are giving away two different ad packages:\n\nSmall Biz Pack -        10,000 impressions\nMedium Biz Pack -   100,000 impressions\n\n<strong>Fill out the interest form below and we\'ll contact you to start the process.</strong>\n\nEXTRA: Starting in November we are going to be Featuring a new business every week, and those businesses will get unlimited* advertising through the end of the year.\n\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWL6X2G4C68\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Advertising','','inherit','open','open','','51-autosave-v1','','','2014-10-03 23:04:23','2014-10-03 23:04:23','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(543,1,'2014-10-02 17:41:13','2014-10-02 17:41:13','Adora Advertising is different for one HUGE reason... When anyone looks at our ads they KNOW that they are doing good.\r\n\r\nWith ever other ad platform - Facebook, Google, Twitter, Yahoo, you name it - people are turned off by advertising, they don\'t want it, they didn\'t say yes to the ads even if they said yes to the product.\r\n\r\nRight now, <em>for a limited time,</em> you can test our platform out for FREE. We are giving away two different ad packages:\r\n\r\nSmall Biz Pack -        10,000 impressions\r\nMedium Biz Pack -   100,000 impressions\r\n\r\n<strong>Fill out the interest form below and we\'ll contact you to start the process.</strong>\r\n\r\nEXTRA: Starting in November we are going to be choosing a new business every week, and those businesses will get unlimited* advertising through the end of the year.','Adora Advertising','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-10-02 17:41:13','2014-10-02 17:41:13','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(407,5,'2014-05-22 12:53:05','2014-05-22 12:53:05','So I like to keep up with a lot of subjects and one of my favorite publications, online and in print is the Harvard Business Review.\r\n\r\nThis morning I came across and article by Clay Christensen and Derek van Bever titled - \"<a title=\"The Capitalist’s Dilemma\" href=\"http://hbr.org/2014/06/the-capitalists-dilemma/ar/6\" target=\"_blank\">The Capitalists Dilemma</a>\"\r\n\r\nGreat article and it sums up what is broken about Capitalism. Now on its face this actually contradicts the idea that <em>is</em> capitalism, the idea that it corrects itself so if it is broken it will just fix naturally.\r\n\r\nI agree with this to a point but I really like some of the points in the article:\r\n\r\n1. The cash is there but the talent is not - we are having a hard time finding MEN and WOMEN who have the gumption to make hard choices. We see a lot of decision paralysis.\r\n\r\n2. Market-Creating Innovation is scary, capital intensive, risky and if it fails the financial markets punish you - see point 1.\r\n\r\n3. Long term, good decisions are discouraged because of investor pressure.\r\n\r\nThen at the end they talk about the shift in mindset that needs to be disseminated through business schools. So again we come back to talent.\r\n\r\nWe need to stop operating out of fear, and start making the right choices regardless of investor pressure. Like James &amp; Benton mention above, if we just act as we see we should the investors will either adjust or find other markets and businesses to invest in.\r\n\r\nI cant wait to see a market where the right choice is made regardless of stock reaction. Where we are brave enough to take that hit and move on because we KNOW it is the right long term choice.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for talent right now, looking for people who don\'t need to be hand held. We want people who will fight for a decision they think is the right one, even if it might not be liked by our investors.\r\n\r\nDon\'t get me wrong, I love and will love our investors! BUT if they trust us enough to invest then I hope they trust us enough to stand next to us when we make the hard choices, because we will.','A plea for TALENT!','','publish','open','open','','plea-talent','','','2014-05-22 13:16:41','2014-05-22 13:16:41','',0,'http://getadora.com/?p=407',0,'post','',0),(54,1,'2014-04-30 09:08:23','2014-04-30 09:08:23','<h2>Before We Jump In</h2>\r\nIt is always exciting and enlightening when you sit down and try to put together a plan. Vague ideas become polished, new ones develop, and issues come up that need to be overcome. This process helps a team find out if the idea is even a valid opportunity.\r\n\r\nWhen we were all young entrepreneurs, working on our first business plan, the horizon was always bright and simple. As we go about the execution of one plan after another we learn that planning is important but never perfect. We learn that while the horizon is always bright we know that the shadows below the horizon contain pit falls, challenges, storms, detours and sometimes you must completely turn around and backtrack.\r\n<h4>We want to create the best plan possible, but at the same time, let all of you who may be reading this know that we understand that any plan will change and more than likely change a lot.</h4>\r\nBecause we know that change is inevitable we are going to focus on the first 18 months, and even then we really only have control of the plan for the rest of 2014 (8+ months or so). Why? Because this app has the ability to explode, and we are only going to try and control growth for the first 3-5 months of the beta period. After that, after we release the full referral program, we have no idea how fast we will grow.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.quotesvalley.com/images/31/there-are-three-types-of-lies-lies-damn-lies-and-statistics-3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"475\" height=\"203\" />','Plan','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 09:08:23','2014-04-30 09:08:23','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(55,1,'2014-04-30 09:25:05','2014-04-30 09:25:05','<h2>Before We Jump In</h2>\r\nIt is always exciting and enlightening when you sit down to put together a plan. Vague ideas become polished, new ones develop, some ideas are tossed for better ones,  and issues come up that need to be overcome. This process helps a team find out if the main idea is even a valid opportunity. We are excited to have gone through this process and come out knowing how truly awesome this idea is.\r\n\r\nThere was a time when we were inexperienced entrepreneurs, working on our first business plan, the horizon was always bright and simple. The numbers we make up, yes we make them up, are best guesses and we think that everything is going to work out just as we\'ve planned. But much to our surprise things just don\'t work out as we thought, the crystal ball doesn\'t work. Sometimes things turn out far better than we thought and sometimes they don\'t.\r\n\r\nWe <strong>learn</strong>, as we go about the execution of one plan after another, that planning is important but never perfect. We <strong>learn</strong> that while the horizon is always bright we <strong>know</strong> that the shadows below the horizon contain pit falls, challenges, storms, detours and sometimes you must completely turn around and backtrack. This process is hard but necessary, it build teams or breaks them, prefects ideas or exposes them, and businesses bloom or fade.\r\n<h4>We want to create the best plan possible, but at the same time, let all of you who may be reading this know that we understand that any plan will change and more than likely change a lot.</h4>\r\nBecause we know that change is inevitable we are going to focus on the first 18 months, and even then we really only have control of the plan for the rest of 2014 (8+ months or so). Why? Because this app has the ability to explode, and we are only going to try and control growth for the first 3-5 months of the beta period. After that we have no idea how fast we will grow.\r\n\r\nOne thing we are going to do - try not to lie with numbers, data, and fluffy words.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.quotesvalley.com/images/31/there-are-three-types-of-lies-lies-damn-lies-and-statistics-3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"475\" height=\"203\" />','Plan','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 09:25:05','2014-04-30 09:25:05','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(56,1,'2014-04-30 09:35:32','2014-04-30 09:35:32','','SunsetRoad','','inherit','open','open','','sunsetroad','','','2014-04-30 09:35:32','2014-04-30 09:35:32','',51,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/SunsetRoad.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(57,1,'2014-04-30 09:36:29','2014-04-30 09:36:29','<h2>Before We Jump In</h2>\r\nIt is always exciting and enlightening when you sit down to put together a plan. Vague ideas become polished, new ones develop, some ideas are tossed for better ones,  and issues come up that need to be overcome. This process helps a team find out if the main idea is even a valid opportunity. We are excited to have gone through this process and come out knowing how truly awesome this idea is.\r\n\r\nThere was a time when we were inexperienced entrepreneurs, working on our first business plan, the horizon was always bright and simple. The numbers we make up, yes we make them up, are best guesses and we think that everything is going to work out just as we\'ve planned. But much to our surprise things just don\'t work out as we thought, the crystal ball doesn\'t work. Sometimes things turn out far better than we thought and sometimes they don\'t.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/SunsetRoad.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-56\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/SunsetRoad.jpg\" alt=\"SunsetRoad\" width=\"1000\" height=\"438\" /></a>We <strong>learn</strong>, as we go about the execution of one plan after another, that planning is important but never perfect. We <strong>learn</strong> that while the horizon is always bright we <strong>know</strong> that the shadows below the horizon contain pit falls, challenges, storms, detours and sometimes you must completely turn around and backtrack. This process is hard but necessary, it build teams or breaks them, prefects ideas or exposes them, and businesses bloom or fade.\r\n<h4>We want to create the best plan possible, but at the same time, let all of you who may be reading this know that we understand that any plan will change and more than likely change a lot.</h4>\r\nBecause we know that change is inevitable we are going to focus on the first 18 months, and even then we really only have control of the plan for the rest of 2014 (8+ months or so). Why? Because this app has the ability to explode, and we are only going to try and control growth for the first 3-5 months of the beta period. After that we have no idea how fast we will grow.\r\n\r\nOne thing we are going to do - try not to lie with numbers, data, and fluffy words.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.quotesvalley.com/images/31/there-are-three-types-of-lies-lies-damn-lies-and-statistics-3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"475\" height=\"203\" />','Plan','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 09:36:29','2014-04-30 09:36:29','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(58,1,'2014-04-30 09:39:07','2014-04-30 09:39:07','','Contact Us','','publish','open','closed','','contact-us','','','2014-10-17 20:26:58','2014-10-17 20:26:58','',0,'http://getadora.com/?page_id=58',8,'page','',0),(59,1,'2014-04-30 09:39:07','2014-04-30 09:39:07','','Contact Us','','inherit','open','open','','58-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 09:39:07','2014-04-30 09:39:07','',58,'http://getadora.com/58-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(60,1,'2014-04-30 09:46:21','2014-04-30 09:46:21','<h3>Adora: A New Option</h3>\r\n<img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" />Advertising funds everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of digital marketing companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, as well as more traditional industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry yet what impact are these platforms making?\r\n\r\nThere is a very important difference between all of these other advertising methods and Adora. We are <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on <strong>doing good</strong> with our advertising revenue, revenue created by our efforts in partnership with you, our users.\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn more about our focus on Charity work, stop reading this page and <strong><a title=\"Charity+\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">PLEASE click here</a>.</strong>  Our message about what drives us is the most important thing we would have you read on our entire site.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>How the Adora App Works</h3>\r\nTraditional advertising, even newer methods like Facebook and Google ads, are not working anymore. Raise your hand if you ignore most every ad around you... You have your hand up don\'t you?\r\n\r\nWe have found an easy way to advertise, a way that is not intrusive, easy to ignore &amp; interact with all at the same time.\r\n\r\nHow you might ask? Through the lockscreen on your mobile device! Take a look at an example of our ad (to the right our just below), yes we know that hulk wouldn\'t really need a band-aid but it is a cool ad. It is a beautiful, full screen ad. It is easy to smile at and simply move on OR it is just as easy to give it a thumbs up and go view the ad.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-641 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LearningSmall.jpg\" alt=\"LearningSmall\" width=\"720\" height=\"400\" />If you\'ve ever used Pandora for music you know how the <strong>thumbs up / thumbs down</strong> interaction works. You get to let us know when you like an ad or when you don\'t.\r\n\r\nIf an ad is just not interesting <strong>simply ignore it, and unlock your device</strong> and we\'ll get that message too.\r\n\r\nBUT what if you <strong><em>do</em></strong> like the ad but don\'t have time to check it out right now? Simply <strong>Save it for later</strong> (see the folders icon) and unlock the device. You can have this option send you and email or it will just be waiting for you when you open the Adora app.\r\n\r\nWhether your interested in an ad or not, you may know someone else who might be. We let you <strong>share that ad</strong> with an individual or with all your social media buddies.\r\n\r\nSoon you\'ll be able to do even more right from the lockscreen, you\'ll love what we have coming!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Adora is More Than Just Ads</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-654 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/MoreThanAdsSmall.jpg\" alt=\"MoreThanAdsSmall\" width=\"400\" height=\"193\" />Adora is still in Beta testing and we are going to be delivering more than just ads to your lockscreen.\r\n\r\nAs we go through testing we\'ll be finding out the best ratio of ads, offers, deals, news, or even personal images. How will we be determining the best ratios? Well that is up to you. How much good do you want to do, how many ads do you want to see vs news, personal images or other content? As you use the app you will tell us with every thumbs up or down.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Adora is easy but we want more from all of you...</h3>\r\nThe Adora app is free to download and use but we want more from everyone. We would love if you would donate out of pocket right now! Don\'t wait to start doing more good. When you download Adora you\'ll start seeing volunteer opportunities but don\'t wait, to find those opportunities.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Donate Now</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h3>\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads, the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way. This is what sets us apart, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','publish','open','closed','','adora-app','','','2014-12-03 09:32:38','2014-12-03 09:32:38','',0,'http://getadora.com/?page_id=60',1,'page','',0),(807,4,'2014-12-02 21:46:38','2014-12-02 21:46:38','<h3>Adora: A New Option</h3>\r\n<img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" />Advertising funds everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of digital marketing companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, as well as more traditional industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry yet what impact are these platforms making?\r\n\r\nThere is a very important difference between all of these other advertising methods and Adora. We are <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on <strong>doing good</strong> with our advertising revenue, revenue created by our efforts in partnership with you, our users.\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn more about our focus on Charity work, stop reading this page and <strong><a title=\"Charity+\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">PLEASE click here</a>.</strong>  Our message about what drives us is the most important thing we would have you read on our entire site.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>How the Adora App Works</h3>\r\nTraditional advertising, even newer methods like Facebook and Google ads, are not working anymore. Raise your hand if you ignore most every ad around you... You have your hand up don\'t you?\r\n\r\nWe have found an easy way to advertise, a way that is not intrusive, easy to ignore &amp; interact with all at the same time.\r\n\r\nHow you might ask? Through the lockscreen on your mobile device! Take a look at an example of our ad (to the right our just below), yes we know that hulk wouldn\'t really need a band-aid but it is a cool ad. It is a beautiful, full screen ad. It is easy to smile at and simply move on OR it is just as easy to give it a thumbs up and go view the ad.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-641 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LearningSmall.jpg\" alt=\"LearningSmall\" width=\"720\" height=\"400\" />If you\'ve ever used Pandora for music you know how the <strong>thumbs up / thumbs down</strong> interaction works. You get to let us know when you like an ad or when you don\'t.\r\n\r\nIf an ad is just not interesting <strong>simply ignore it, and unlock your device</strong> and we\'ll get that message too.\r\n\r\nBUT what if you <strong><em>do</em></strong> like the ad but don\'t have time to check it out right now? Simply <strong>Save it for later</strong> (see the folders icon) and unlock the device. You can have this option send you and email or it will just be waiting for you when you open the Adora app.\r\n\r\nWhether your interested in an ad or not, you may know someone else who might be. We let you <strong>share that ad</strong> with an individual or with all your social media buddies.\r\n\r\nSoon you\'ll be able to do even more right from the lockscreen, you\'ll love what we have coming!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Adora is More Than Just Ads</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-654 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/MoreThanAdsSmall.jpg\" alt=\"MoreThanAdsSmall\" width=\"400\" height=\"193\" />Adora is still in Beta testing and we are going to be delivering more than just ads to your lockscreen.\r\n\r\nAs we go through testing we\'ll be finding out the best ratio of ads, offers, deals, news, or even personal images. How will we be determining the best ratios? Well that is up to you. How much good do you wan tot do, how many ads do you want to see vs news, personal images or other content? As you use the app you will tell us with every thumbs up or down.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Adora is easy but we want more from all of you...</h3>\r\nThe Adora app is free to download and use but we want more from everyone. We would love if you would donate out of pocket right now! Don\'t wait to start doing more good. When you download Adora you\'ll start seeing volunteer opportunities but don\'t wait, to find those opportunities.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Donate Now</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h3>\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads, the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way. This is what sets us apart, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-12-02 21:46:38','2014-12-02 21:46:38','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(61,1,'2014-04-30 09:46:21','2014-04-30 09:46:21','','Adora app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 09:46:21','2014-04-30 09:46:21','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(62,1,'2014-04-30 09:48:31','2014-04-30 09:48:31','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why isn\'t more getting done?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Many of us believe that unless our donation is large, it doesn\'t make a difference. Or that unless we spend hours or days volunteering, then it\'s not worth the small impact.\r\n\r\nAt Adora we are not asking our users to change their mobile device use. Our users don\'t even have to open our app or take any more time out of their busy days to do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur app gives our users a choice they have never had before--to choose where their advertising earnings go. We make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-652\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice.jpg\" alt=\"Choice\" width=\"884\" height=\"498\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">The Adora app is simple--the advertising pays for charity work, but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Adora app will also make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference, but if 1 million or 10 million users all donate, then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"CrowdCellLights\" width=\"421\" height=\"258\" /> Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see  us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible. And oh the good that could be done with that  kind  of donation every month!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"> Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company  in the world.</strong></p>\r\n But once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish. We must change the way we look at charitable  organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"> Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses. Be it a hashtag trending on twitter, a viral video, or dumping ice water on our heads. We know there are few better ways to move mountains than through the power of numbers. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below. Better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/bfAzi6D5FpM\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our Vision</h3>\r\nWe see a world where <strong>everyone is doing good every day. </strong>\r\n<h3><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a></strong></h3>\r\n<strong> It is our vision to lead a change in private &amp; corporate social activity by becoming the most charitable company in  the world by 2020.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such a lofty goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-  tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Even the most charitable companies never donate more  than 15% of their pre-tax profits. Walmart has been at the top of the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo leading the way in 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account, Pfizer has taken the top spot for the  last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know these are very large companies, but one of our goals is to reach the point where we are <strong>donating more than 51% of  our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to that point, but how fast  and how much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>If you want help out, read more about <a title=\"How You Can Help\" href=\"http://getadora.com/can-help/\">how you can be more involved</a>, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong></p>','Charity+','','publish','open','closed','','charity','','','2014-12-03 08:17:14','2014-12-03 08:17:14','',0,'http://getadora.com/?page_id=62',0,'page','',0),(609,1,'2014-10-04 19:05:20','2014-10-04 19:05:20','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we all actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference, that unless they spend hours or days volunteering anything less is not worth the small impact.\r\n\r\nWe are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app, they do not need to take any more time out of their busy days to do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. We make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our app will also make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 10 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"CrowdCellLights\" width=\"421\" height=\"258\" />Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good that could be done with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a hashtag trending on twitter, a viral video, or dumping ice on our heads, we know that there are few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/bfAzi6D5FpM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n<strong>If you want help out read more about how you can be more involved, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 19:05:20','2014-10-04 19:05:20','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(267,1,'2014-05-09 08:06:08','2014-05-09 08:06:08','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do they/we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">By creating strategic relationships we can hit our first goal of 1% of the 200 million smartphone user market by the middle of 2015. The math plays that 1% out to equal 2 million users, when compared to the 100 million Candy Crush users we would hope that at least 2% would be willing to support such a charitable cause. If you want to find out more about how we are going to gather these users, about our marketing plan, <a href=\"info@lscapp.com\">email us</a>. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want to become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 08:06:08','2014-05-09 08:06:08','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(253,1,'2014-05-09 07:28:46','2014-05-09 07:28:46','<img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />There are so many who need help.\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\nWhy do they/we not do more?\r\n<h2>Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">By creating strategic relationships we can hit our first goal of 1% of the 200 million smartphone user market by the middle of 2015. The math plays that 1% out to equal 2 million users, when compared to the 100 million Candy Crush users we would hope that at least 2% would be willing to support such a charitable cause. If you want to find out more about how we are going to gather these users, about our marketing plan, <a href=\"info@lscapp.com\">email us</a>. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our requirements for the charities before getting money from us will be:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 24px;\">No less than 85% of all funds donated must go directly to the key activities of the cause, now this does not mean that no more than 15% can go to \'overhead\' only that it must be an activity that can benefit the cause. We want to work with these charities and make sure that most of their efforts are productive. Fundraising can be productive, getting great talent can be productive, marketing can be productive, tech investments can be productive yet these are all considered traditionally overhead in the non-profit world.</span></li>\r\n	<li>Legal work using donated funds will be heavily scrutinized. We love the legal system but we would rather feed children than pay lawyers.</li>\r\n	<li>Organizations run by religious groups will be heavily scrutinized. We want to make sure everyone is served; not just individuals who share a faith or ideology.</li>\r\n	<li>Medical research will be vetted heavily to make sure funds are going to research that is making strides not spinning wheels. We would love to see families who are struggling with heavily researched medical issues be supported.</li>\r\n	<li>We will not support organizations which participate heavily in political donations, activity, or lobbying. If there is a cause that needs representation at state and federal levels then let us know and we will work together on how to address that.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe bottom line: we want our donations to get to people who need it.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here are some numbers on how we can impact our communities:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>First off let\'s assume our app is awesome, and it gains great market acceptance and we grow like crazy. But let\'s just start at that 1% (1.5 million) of the market. Good, now that we have that out of the way.</li>\r\n	<li>We would love to have all of our users donate their entire $15 max, then we match that, which equals $30 total. But to be realistic that group might make up around 10% (150,000) of our total active users, giving us a potential total of $4.5 million a month from these users.</li>\r\n	<li>If the rest of the 1.35 million users donate $1, and we match that, then it equals $2. We get monthly donation funds of... $2.7 million plus the users\' donations from point number 2, then we get <strong>$7.2 million a month.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<a href=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\"><img class=\"alignright\" src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"288\" /></a>Sounds crazy right... Well Candy Crush Saga, yes we just referenced that game, has over 100 million active users!\r\n\r\nIt makes over $600,000 a day, and over $230 million a year <strong>AND</strong> our app has the potential to blow that away!\r\n\r\nIf we can donate $7.2 million a month, here is just a glimpse at some of the things we can do with that:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>@ $200 per child = 36,000 kids <strong>clothing &amp; school supplies</strong> for a year</li>\r\n	<li>@ $3.50 per meal = over 2.0 million <strong>meals</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per procedure = 72,000<strong> dental procedures</strong> for underprivileged families</li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per month = 72,000 <strong>Public Transit passes</strong> for a month to un/under employed</li>\r\n	<li>@$2,000 per month = 3,600 families <strong>sheltered and given job training</strong> per month</li>\r\n	<li>@ $5,000 per semester = 1440 <strong>scholarships</strong> to under-funded college students</li>\r\n	<li>@ $25,000 per child = 288 families <strong>supported during life threatening medical issues</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100,000 per unit = We can deliver a self-sustaining water solution to 72 locations, and <strong>provide clean water</strong> where thousands die every year from unclean water...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf we donated all but a fraction of our revenues to efforts like this we would find joy and satisfaction in our existence and our app. But we can have both an amazing impact through our donations <strong>and</strong> have a healthy profit margin; this is a \"win/win\" opportunity.\r\n\r\nWe also want to help small businesses by providing them with free help when it comes to learning how to advertise and how to get results.\r\n\r\nWe want to give large brands the reach and impact they are looking for every day.\r\n\r\nWe want to provide an amazing return for our investors so they can go out and invest more in companies that do good.\r\n\r\nWe want to talk to you.\r\n<h3>If you want to become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h3>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 07:28:46','2014-05-09 07:28:46','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(252,1,'2014-05-09 07:24:36','2014-05-09 07:24:36','<img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />There are so many who need help.\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\nWhy do they/we not do more?\r\n<h2>Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">It is simple: the advertising pays for charity work.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">By creating strategic relationships we can hit our first goal of 1% of the 200 million smartphone user market by the middle of 2015. The math plays that 1% out to equal 2 million users, when compared to the 100 million Candy Crush users we would hope that at least 2% would be willing to support such a charitable cause. This will help us donate up to 3 million dollars <strong>per month</strong> to charities that we vet. If you want to find out more about our marketing plan, <a href=\"info@lscapp.com\">email us</a>. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our requirements for the charities before getting money from us will be:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 24px;\">No less than 85% of all funds donated must go directly to the key activities of the cause, now this does not mean that no more than 15% can go to \'overhead\' only that it must be an activity that can benefit the cause. We want to work with these charities and make sure that most of their efforts are productive. Fundraising can be productive, getting great talent can be productive, marketing can be productive, tech investments can be productive yet these are all considered traditionally overhead in the non-profit world.</span></li>\r\n	<li>Legal work using donated funds will be heavily scrutinized. We love the legal system but we would rather feed children than pay lawyers.</li>\r\n	<li>Organizations run by religious groups will be heavily scrutinized. We want to make sure everyone is served; not just individuals who share a faith or ideology.</li>\r\n	<li>Medical research will be vetted heavily to make sure funds are going to research that is making strides not spinning wheels. We would love to see families who are struggling with heavily researched medical issues be supported.</li>\r\n	<li>We will not support organizations which participate heavily in political donations, activity, or lobbying. If there is a cause that needs representation at state and federal levels then let us know and we will work together on how to address that.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe bottom line: we want our donations to get to people who need it.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here are some numbers on how we can impact our communities:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>First off let\'s assume our app is awesome, and it gains great market acceptance and we grow like crazy. But let\'s just start at that 1% (1.5 million) of the market. Good, now that we have that out of the way.</li>\r\n	<li>We would love to have all of our users donate their entire $15 max, then we match that, which equals $30 total. But to be realistic that group might make up around 10% (150,000) of our total active users, giving us a potential total of $4.5 million a month from these users.</li>\r\n	<li>If the rest of the 1.35 million users donate $1, and we match that, then it equals $2. We get monthly donation funds of... $2.7 million plus the users\' donations from point number 2, then we get <strong>$7.2 million a month.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<a href=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\"><img class=\"alignright\" src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"288\" /></a>Sounds crazy right... Well Candy Crush Saga, yes we just referenced that game, has over 100 million active users!\r\n\r\nIt makes over $600,000 a day, and over $230 million a year <strong>AND</strong> our app has the potential to blow that away!\r\n\r\nIf we can donate $7.2 million a month, here is just a glimpse at some of the things we can do with that:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>@ $200 per child = 36,000 kids <strong>clothing &amp; school supplies</strong> for a year</li>\r\n	<li>@ $3.50 per meal = over 2.0 million <strong>meals</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per procedure = 72,000<strong> dental procedures</strong> for underprivileged families</li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per month = 72,000 <strong>Public Transit passes</strong> for a month to un/under employed</li>\r\n	<li>@$2,000 per month = 3,600 families <strong>sheltered and given job training</strong> per month</li>\r\n	<li>@ $5,000 per semester = 1440 <strong>scholarships</strong> to under-funded college students</li>\r\n	<li>@ $25,000 per child = 288 families <strong>supported during life threatening medical issues</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100,000 per unit = We can deliver a self-sustaining water solution to 72 locations, and <strong>provide clean water</strong> where thousands die every year from unclean water...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf we donated all but a fraction of our revenues to efforts like this we would find joy and satisfaction in our existence and our app. But we can have both an amazing impact through our donations <strong>and</strong> have a healthy profit margin; this is a \"win/win\" opportunity.\r\n\r\nWe also want to help small businesses by providing them with free help when it comes to learning how to advertise and how to get results.\r\n\r\nWe want to give large brands the reach and impact they are looking for every day.\r\n\r\nWe want to provide an amazing return for our investors so they can go out and invest more in companies that do good.\r\n\r\nWe want to talk to you.\r\n<h3>If you want to become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h3>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 07:24:36','2014-05-09 07:24:36','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(63,1,'2014-04-30 09:48:31','2014-04-30 09:48:31','','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 09:48:31','2014-04-30 09:48:31','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(64,1,'2014-04-30 09:49:38','2014-04-30 09:49:38','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">In the start-up world we have what would be considered a Dream Team. Click on any of us to learn more.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/BenFaanunuSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-299 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/KyleThomasSmall.jpg\" alt=\"KyleThomasSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-297 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/BenFaanunuSmall.jpg\" alt=\"BenFa\'anunuSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/MarkFeriante2Small.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-300 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/MarkFeriante2Small.jpg\" alt=\"MarkFeriante2Small\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/JoeMichelsSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-298 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/JoeMichelsSmall.jpg\" alt=\"JoeMichelsSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/SebasteanLoschSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-302 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/SebasteanLoschSmall.jpg\" alt=\"SebasteanLoschSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/ChristianSampsonSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-366 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/ChristianSampsonSmall.jpg\" alt=\"ChristianSampsonSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/DevinThorpeSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-425\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/DevinThorpeSmall.jpg\" alt=\"DevinThorpeSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/WayneCarrollSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-426\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/WayneCarrollSmall.jpg\" alt=\"WayneCarrollSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/JoshShapiroSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-427\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/JoshShapiroSmall.jpg\" alt=\"JoshShapiroSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Man-WomanAvatar.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-304 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Man-WomanAvatar.jpg\" alt=\"Man-WomanAvatar\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are looking for a few good men and women. Are you interested in a challenging, exciting, fulfilling daily struggle? Hard work, humility, creativity, and passion are part of the culture here at Adora.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are looking for the following individuals:</p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\" aligncenter\" style=\"height: 27px; width: 657px;\" width=\"569\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Digital Advertising Guru</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Mobile Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Charity Relationship Manager</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you think you would not just fit in, but flourish and you could see yourself in a leadership position as we grow, then by all means <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\">send us an email</a>.</p>\r\n<iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/zrHlkHdPF4U\" width=\"932\" height=\"524\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>','Team','','draft','open','closed','','team','','','2014-10-10 22:20:46','2014-10-10 22:20:46','',2,'http://getadora.com/?page_id=64',2,'page','',0),(65,1,'2014-04-30 09:49:38','2014-04-30 09:49:38','','Team','','inherit','open','open','','64-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 09:49:38','2014-04-30 09:49:38','',64,'http://getadora.com/64-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(68,1,'2014-04-30 09:54:05','2014-04-30 09:54:05','Adora exists to help you do more good.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-208 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\" alt=\"Charity\" width=\"401\" height=\"244\" /></a>Through Adora we hope to help all of our charitable partners do more good through better exposure, more consistent funding, and increased volunteer involvement.\r\n\r\nHere is how it works:\r\n\r\nThe Program is FREE, you will never pay for our services.\r\n\r\nThe Adora Charity Funding Program requires a very simple formal agreement, Adora doesn\'t even need your donor list to engage your supporters, we trust you to do that. When you become a Charity Partner you will be part of our <a title=\"Adora Affiliate Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\">Affiliate Program</a> but with some amazing advantages:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Your users will bring you funding for as long as they use the app, no expiration.</li>\r\n	<li>You will receive free advertising on the network that grows with your Adora user base (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Direct Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate to you via our app, and we will pay the transaction fees.</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)<img class=\"alignright wp-image-652 size-medium\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"Choice\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" /></li>\r\n	<li>You may be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving (coming in 2016).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe key to your funding and the scope of all of these benefits will be based on your effort in promoting your Charity on the Adora App.\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Program','','publish','open','closed','','charityprogram','','','2015-02-11 22:38:24','2015-02-11 22:38:24','',0,'http://getadora.com/?page_id=68',4,'page','',0),(897,1,'2015-02-11 22:38:24','2015-02-11 22:38:24','Adora exists to help you do more good.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-208 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\" alt=\"Charity\" width=\"401\" height=\"244\" /></a>Through Adora we hope to help all of our charitable partners do more good through better exposure, more consistent funding, and increased volunteer involvement.\r\n\r\nHere is how it works:\r\n\r\nThe Program is FREE, you will never pay for our services.\r\n\r\nThe Adora Charity Funding Program requires a very simple formal agreement, Adora doesn\'t even need your donor list to engage your supporters, we trust you to do that. When you become a Charity Partner you will be part of our <a title=\"Adora Affiliate Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\">Affiliate Program</a> but with some amazing advantages:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Your users will bring you funding for as long as they use the app, no expiration.</li>\r\n	<li>You will receive free advertising on the network that grows with your Adora user base (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Direct Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate to you via our app, and we will pay the transaction fees.</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)<img class=\"alignright wp-image-652 size-medium\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"Choice\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" /></li>\r\n	<li>You may be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving (coming in 2016).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe key to your funding and the scope of all of these benefits will be based on your effort in promoting your Charity on the Adora App.\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2015-02-11 22:38:24','2015-02-11 22:38:24','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(814,4,'2014-12-02 22:13:21','2014-12-02 22:13:21','Adora exists to help you do more good.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-208 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\" alt=\"Charity\" width=\"401\" height=\"244\" /></a>Through Adora we hope to help all of our charitable partners do more good through better exposure, more consistent funding, and increased volunteer involvement.\r\n\r\nHere is how it works:\r\n\r\nThe Program is FREE, you will never pay for our services.\r\n\r\nThe Adora Charity Funding Program requires a very simple formal agreement, Adora doesn\'t even need your donor list to engage your supporters, we trust you to do that. When you become a Charity Partner you will be part of our <a title=\"Adora Affiliate Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\">Affiliate Program</a> but with some amazing advantages:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Your users will bring you funding for as long as they use the app, no 12-6 month expiration.</li>\r\n	<li>You will receive free advertising on the network that grows with your Adora user base (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Direct Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate to you via our app, and we will pay the transaction fees.</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You may be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving (coming in 2016).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe key to your funding and the scope of all of these benefits will be based on your effort in promoting your Charity on the Adora App.\r\n\r\n<strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-652 size-medium\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"Choice\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" /></a>Special Crowdfunding Opportunity</strong>\r\n\r\nOn December 2nd, we will be lunching a crowdfunding campaign. In this campaign we will raising money to complete the app and feed people and pets. This campaign will focus on fighting holiday hunger and be a great way to acquire users of our app who will fund you monthly once the app begins delivering ads.  The more users that download our app from your partner link, the less that is spent on non-charity affiliate costs be cause those affiliate fees go to your charity. We\'ll tell you more once you are on board.\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be free for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This exposure will encourage others to go out and do more good.\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-12-02 22:13:21','2014-12-02 22:13:21','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(547,1,'2014-10-02 22:16:50','2014-10-02 22:16:50','Adora Helps Charities Do More\r\n\r\nAt Adora we love the good our partner charities are doing, our goal is to help them to execute their charitable missions through providing access to additional funding and outreach to volunteers to the communities they serve.\r\n\r\nPhilanthropy 2.0\r\n\r\nAdora was created as a way to allow everyone to become a philanthropist.  Through the Adora Charity App,  everyone can participate in charitable giving, even those with no money to give.   In this new paradigm of giving, all forms of support for a charitable cause are of worth and the cost of developing support from the lowest tier of the funding pyramid goes away.\r\n\r\nAdora Provides the Platform &amp; the Technology\r\n\r\nAdora creates a consistent and dependable revenue stream for charities to or replace other more costly streams.  Advertisers provide the money and Adora turns anyone with a mobile device who supports your cause into a donor.  The same social media, newsletter, mail, radio, and TV development efforts attract a new bottom tier to your funding pyramid with no extra costs or efforts.\r\n\r\nGood Works Beget More Good Works\r\n\r\nFor those who already donate and volunteer, Adora is an easy way to give more and evangelize for your cause with Adora\'s sharing features.   For the new donors that give only through the ad-view funding they generate it is the first step to engagement and involvement with your charity.  Doing good feels good - each individual will give up as much time and money as they are willing to trade to be a part of your mission and to experience the joy of doing good and helping others.  Adora lowers the bar for giving and opens the door to charity involvement and active volunteer participation.\r\n\r\nMoving Forward Together\r\n\r\nThe impact we can make together can change the face of charitable giving forever. This is no small promise or opportunity, nor is this a one time thing. Every day you can add users and grow your funding and volunteer engagement.  Your social supports can now all be donors and as they recruit others for your cause, they will expand that base to achieve the goals for funding and serving others.\r\n\r\nHow it works\r\n\r\nThere are two different types of relationships a charity can have with our app: Basic or Partner.  We hope to have every charity as a Partner, but we canl still help those who want a more casual Basic Relationship\r\n\r\nBasic Relationship\r\n\r\nThis is the simple way to work with us. All you will need to do is indicate that you are interested in signup form and we will provide an affiliate code and link to share with your social followers and place on your direct donation page.\r\n\r\nFeatures of the basic relationship:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Quarterly (all transaction costs will be paid out of the donation total)</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be limited (Capped at $2.50 right now but that may go up in the future)</li>\r\n	<li>Users will need to specify your charity by name or with a code to donate though the app.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPartnership\r\n\r\nThis is the most productive relationship for everyone and in technical terms it is only an ongoing joint venture. By committing to work with us on the launch and continual promotion of the app we can have a closer relationship with you. General features of the joint venture:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Free advertising on the network (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You will be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This will encourage others to do more good.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe will be selecting a precious few to be in on our secret regarding how we will be delivering our ads. We want you to be able to tell others, including those you promote our app to, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-02 22:16:50','2014-10-02 22:16:50','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(69,1,'2014-04-30 09:54:05','2014-04-30 09:54:05','','The Marketing','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 09:54:05','2014-04-30 09:54:05','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(72,1,'2014-10-05 02:12:23','2014-10-05 02:12:23','<h3>Adora: A New Option</h3>\n<img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" />Advertising funds everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of digital marketing companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, as well as more traditional industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry yet what impact are these platforms making?\n\nThere is a very important difference between all of these other advertising methods and Adora. We are <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on <strong>doing good</strong> with our advertising revenue, revenue created by our efforts in partnership with you, our users.\n\nIf you want to learn more about our focus on Charity work, stop reading this page and <a title=\"Charity+\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\"><strong>PLEASE</strong> </a><strong><a title=\"Charity+\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">click here</a>.</strong>  Our message about what drives us is the most important thing we would have you read on our entire site.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3>How the Adora App Works</h3>\nTraditional advertising, even newer methods like Facebook and Google ads, are not working anymore. Raise your hand if you ignore most every ad around you... You have your hand up don\'t you?\n\nWe have found an easy way to advertise, a way that is not intrusive, easy to ignore &amp; interact with all at the same time.\n\nHow you might ask? Through the lockscreen on your mobile device! Take a look at an example of our ad (to the right our just below), yes we know that hulk wouldn\'t really need a band-aid but it is a cool ad. It is a beautiful, full screen ad. It is easy to smile at and simply move on OR it is just as easy to give it a thumbs up and go view the ad.\n\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-641 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LearningSmall.jpg\" alt=\"LearningSmall\" width=\"720\" height=\"400\" />If you\'ve ever used Pandora for music you know how the <strong>thumbs up / thumbs down</strong> interaction works. You get to let us know when you like an ad or when you don\'t.\n\nIf an ad is just not interesting <strong>simply ignore it, and unlock your device</strong> and we\'ll get that message too.\n\nBUT what if you <strong><em>do</em></strong> like the ad but don\'t have time to check it out right now? Simply <strong>Save it for later</strong> (see the folders icon) and unlock the device. You can have this option send you and email or it will just be waiting for you when you open the Adora app.\n\nWhether you are of aren\'t interested in an ad you may know someone else who might be interested, so we let you <strong>share an ad</strong> with an individual or with all your social media buddies.\n\nSoon you\'ll be able to do even more right from the lockscreen, you\'ll love what we have coming!\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3>Adora is More Than Just Ads</h3>\n<img class=\" wp-image-654 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/MoreThanAdsSmall.jpg\" alt=\"MoreThanAdsSmall\" width=\"400\" height=\"193\" />Adora is still in Beta testing and we are going to be delivering more than just ads to your lockscreen.\n\nAs we go through testing we\'ll be finding out the best ratio of ads, offers, deals, news, or even personal images. How will we be determining the best ratios? Well that is up to you. How much good do you wan tot do, how many ads do you want to see vs news, personal images or other content? As you use the app you will tell us with every thumbs up or down.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3>Adora is easy but we want more from all of you...</h3>\nThe Adora app is free to download and use but we want more from everyone. We would love if you would donate out of pocket right now! Don\'t wait to start doing more good. We also want you to go out and find a way to volunteer, when you download Adora you will start seeing volunteer opportunities but we don\'t want you to wait for those either.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3>Donate Now</h3>\n&nbsp;\n<h3>Our Vision</h3>\nWe see a world where <strong>everyone is doing good every day. </strong>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a></strong></h3>\n<strong>It is our vision to lead a change in private &amp; corporate social activity by becoming the most charitable company in the world by 2020.</strong>\n\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Even the most charitable companies never donate more than 15% of their pre-tax profits. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\n\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are <strong>donating more than 51% of our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h3>\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\n\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','inherit','open','open','','60-autosave-v1','','','2014-10-05 02:12:23','2014-10-05 02:12:23','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(293,1,'2014-05-09 11:03:55','2014-05-09 11:03:55','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The Adora project uses the power of Ad Revenue + User Engagement to = Charitable giving.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Our passion is to do as much good as we possibly can.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This is what drives our every move, what make our hearts burn to work harder, longer, and smarter.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We then want our example to start a movement, a change in not just corporate giving but private giving too. Make the point that even a dollar here or $5 there can make a difference, that you don\'t have to be wealthy to give and you don\'t have to give money to make an impact.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/RXMnDG3QzxE\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a title=\"The app\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/adora-app/\">Read more about our app</a></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>If you want more info <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\">contact us</a>.</strong></p>','About Us','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 11:03:55','2014-05-09 11:03:55','',2,'http://getadora.com/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(76,1,'2014-04-30 15:48:43','2014-04-30 15:48:43','Without spilling the beans - here is a little info on what we are building. Right now many of us are doing one specific thing over and over again, and more than likely you will do this one thing a few times as you read this. We want to take that one action and turn it into a way for businesses, large and small, to reach you and everyone else in the world.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\"><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"338\" height=\"166\" /></a>\r\n\r\nWhat we know:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our economy is not growing as it could/should be.</li>\r\n	<li>The key to any real recovery is going to be the small and medium sized businesses driving the local economies.</li>\r\n	<li>In this age of Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, and all the other digital resources we use every day, a business MUST utilize some amount of digital marketing if they want to be successful.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe problem is... They don\'t know where or how to utilize their small but important budgets.\r\n\r\nWe want to create an easy-to-use ad marketplace, delivery network, and support team where a Mom &amp; Pop business can get advice on how to create an ad, geo-target that ad, set times, add special discount codes, and most importantly: <strong>get results.</strong>\r\n\r\nWe also want to have this same network serve our large corporate clients -- they create value too. There are huge regional,  national, and international brands that would love a more successful way to reach their consumers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Google, Facebook, Twitter and all the rest.</strong>\r\n\r\nRight now the top online advertising outlets are all trying to capture their piece of the pie, but they do it by offering something else. That something else comes with a lot of distractions, content, and anywhere from 5-12 or even more advertisements--competition. They want to provide value to increase user engagement, but they also want users to interact with the advertising. It is a difficult balance.\r\n\r\nWe want to help fill a void that has little to no competition, does not have distracting content, and is straightforward. We are going to deliver ads to you, and you are going to love it, use it all the time and soon life won\'t be the same with out us.\r\n\r\nHere are some important stats:\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"411\"]<a href=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\"><img src=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\" alt=\"US Smartphone Growth Projections\" width=\"411\" height=\"351\" /></a> Smartphone Growth[/caption]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The US alone will be rapidly approaching 200 million smartphones in use by the 2014 holiday season</li>\r\n	<li>Users wake up their phones over <a title=\"HTC One M8 Review and Research\" href=\"https://www.yahoo.com/tech/heres-why-people-are-so-excited-about-the-new-htc-one-80913367177.html\" target=\"_blank\">150 times a day</a> - 4,500 times a month - 54,000 times a year.</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Advertising revenue is going to continue to grow as more and more time is spent on mobile platforms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobile Ad Revenue (Billions):\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2012 - $8.76</li>\r\n	<li>2013 - $17.96</li>\r\n	<li>2014 - $<em>31.45 (estimate)</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you could create an app which takes advantage of all of these factors, you could deliver ads to users in a way which creates great value to everyone involved.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe have an app in development that does just this.\r\n\r\nThe focus of the app is to deliver ads to mobile users, to pay those users up to $15 a month for letting us deliver ads to them, then ask those users to donate at least $1 per month of their earnings to their favorite charity.<strong> We then match these donations dollar for dollar.</strong> These users are worth, at the low end averages, $36 per month.\r\n\r\nOur marketing plan will allow us to gain significant user acceptance. By partnering with strategic organizations, charities, carriers, and other large companies we can hit our first goal of 1% of the smartphone users (1.75 million users) by the end of 2014.\r\n\r\nThat would bring in a mind blowing $54 million per month in revenues.\r\n<h4>And this is not even the best part of the app - the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side can work.</a></h4>\r\n<h4>If you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h4>','Adora app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 15:48:43','2014-04-30 15:48:43','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(74,1,'2014-04-30 15:45:16','2014-04-30 15:45:16','Without spilling the beans - here is a little info on what we are building. Right now many of us are doing one specific thing over and over again, and more than likely you will do this o