012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\"><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"338\" height=\"166\" /></a>\r\n\r\nWhat we know:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our economy is not growing as it could/should be.</li>\r\n	<li>The key to any real recovery is going to be the small and medium sized businesses driving the local economies.</li>\r\n	<li>In this age of Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, and all the other digital resources we use every day, a business MUST utilize some amount of digital marketing if they want to be successful.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe problem is... They don\'t know where or how to utilize their small but important budgets.\r\n\r\nWe want to create an easy-to-use ad marketplace, delivery network, and support team where a Mom &amp; Pop business can get advice on how to create an ad, geo-target that ad, set times, add special discount codes, and most importantly: <strong>get results.</strong>\r\n\r\nWe also want to have this same network serve our large corporate clients -- they create value too. There are huge regional,  national, and international brands that would love a more successful way to reach their consumers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Google, Facebook, Twitter and all the rest.</strong>\r\n\r\nRight now the top online advertising outlets are all trying to capture their piece of the pie, but they do it by offering something else. That something else comes with a lot of distractions, content, and anywhere from 5-12 or even more advertisements--competition. They want to provide value to increase user engagement, but they also want users to interact with the advertising. It is a difficult balance.\r\n\r\nWe want to help fill a void that has little to no competition, does not have distracting content, and is straightforward. We are going to deliver ads to you, and you are going to love it, use it all the time and soon life won\'t be the same with out us.\r\n\r\nHere are some important stats:\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"411\"]<a href=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\"><img src=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\" alt=\"US Smartphone Growth Projections\" width=\"411\" height=\"351\" /></a> Smartphone Growth[/caption]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The US alone will be rapidly approaching 200 million smartphones in use by the 2014 holiday season</li>\r\n	<li>Users wake up their phones over <a title=\"HTC One M8 Review and Research\" href=\"https://www.yahoo.com/tech/heres-why-people-are-so-excited-about-the-new-htc-one-80913367177.html\" target=\"_blank\">150 times a day</a> - 4,500 times a month - 54,000 times a year.</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Advertising revenue is going to continue to grow as more and more time is spent on mobile platforms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"325\"]<a href=\"https://ci6.googleusercontent.com/proxy/EOhaossDsKn5mKqDwCksO5uloDJUUtTrWRFmiOS1bwjgXPpf5CiROGpW-wuHbvAx916BNTdOQGj6cGjtQVadE6egXeCQLFNcYjLmtS05vbzYevOPPyjhXao=s0-d-e1-ft#http://www.emarketer.com/images/chart_gifs/170001-171000/170637.gif\"><img src=\"https://ci6.googleusercontent.com/proxy/EOhaossDsKn5mKqDwCksO5uloDJUUtTrWRFmiOS1bwjgXPpf5CiROGpW-wuHbvAx916BNTdOQGj6cGjtQVadE6egXeCQLFNcYjLmtS05vbzYevOPPyjhXao=s0-d-e1-ft#http://www.emarketer.com/images/chart_gifs/170001-171000/170637.gif\" alt=\"Mobile Ad Revenue \" width=\"325\" height=\"254\" /></a> Mobile Ad Revenue[/caption]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobile Ad Revenue (Billions):\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2012 - $8.76</li>\r\n	<li>2013 - $17.96</li>\r\n	<li>2014 - $<em>31.45 (estimate)</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you could create an app which takes advantage of all of these factors, you could deliver ads to users in a way which creates great value to everyone involved.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe have an app in development that does just this.\r\n\r\nThe focus of the app is to deliver ads to mobile users, to pay those users up to $15 a month for letting us deliver ads to them, then ask those users to donate at least $1 per month of their earnings to their favorite charity.<strong> We then match these donations dollar for dollar.</strong> These users are worth, at the low end averages, $36 per month.\r\n\r\nOur marketing plan will allow us to gain significant user acceptance. By partnering with strategic organizations, charities, carriers, and other large companies we can hit our first goal of 1% of the smartphone users (1.75 million users) by mid-2015.\r\n\r\nThat would bring in a mind blowing $54 million per month in revenues - at just 1% of the market.\r\n<h4>And this is not even the best part of the app - the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side can work.</a></h4>\r\n<h4>If you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h4>','Adora app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 15:46:20','2014-04-30 15:46:20','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(77,1,'2014-04-30 15:49:05','2014-04-30 15:49:05','Without spilling the beans - here is a little info on what we are building. Right now many of us are doing one specific thing over and over again, and more than likely you will do this one thing a few times as you read this. We want to take that one action and turn it into a way for businesses, large and small, to reach you and everyone else in the world.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\"><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"338\" height=\"166\" /></a>\r\n\r\nWhat we know:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our economy is not growing as it could/should be.</li>\r\n	<li>The key to any real recovery is going to be the small and medium sized businesses driving the local economies.</li>\r\n	<li>In this age of Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, and all the other digital resources we use every day, a business MUST utilize some amount of digital marketing if they want to be successful.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe problem is... They don\'t know where or how to utilize their small but important budgets.\r\n\r\nWe want to create an easy-to-use ad marketplace, delivery network, and support team where a Mom &amp; Pop business can get advice on how to create an ad, geo-target that ad, set times, add special discount codes, and most importantly: <strong>get results.</strong>\r\n\r\nWe also want to have this same network serve our large corporate clients -- they create value too. There are huge regional,  national, and international brands that would love a more successful way to reach their consumers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Google, Facebook, Twitter and all the rest.</strong>\r\n\r\nRight now the top online advertising outlets are all trying to capture their piece of the pie, but they do it by offering something else. That something else comes with a lot of distractions, content, and anywhere from 5-12 or even more advertisements--competition. They want to provide value to increase user engagement, but they also want users to interact with the advertising. It is a difficult balance.\r\n\r\nWe want to help fill a void that has little to no competition, does not have distracting content, and is straightforward. We are going to deliver ads to you, and you are going to love it, use it all the time and soon life won\'t be the same with out us.\r\n\r\nHere are some important stats:\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"547\"]<a href=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\"><img src=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\" alt=\"US Smartphone Growth Projections\" width=\"547\" height=\"467\" /></a> Smartphone Growth[/caption]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The US alone will be rapidly approaching 200 million smartphones in use by the 2014 holiday season</li>\r\n	<li>Users wake up their phones over <a title=\"HTC One M8 Review and Research\" href=\"https://www.yahoo.com/tech/heres-why-people-are-so-excited-about-the-new-htc-one-80913367177.html\" target=\"_blank\">150 times a day</a> - 4,500 times a month - 54,000 times a year.</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Advertising revenue is going to continue to grow as more and more time is spent on mobile platforms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobile Ad Revenue (Billions):\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2012 - $8.76</li>\r\n	<li>2013 - $17.96</li>\r\n	<li>2014 - $<em>31.45 (estimate)</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you could create an app which takes advantage of all of these factors, you could deliver ads to users in a way which creates great value to everyone involved.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe have an app in development that does just this.\r\n\r\nThe focus of the app is to deliver ads to mobile users, to pay those users up to $15 a month for letting us deliver ads to them, then ask those users to donate at least $1 per month of their earnings to their favorite charity.<strong> We then match these donations dollar for dollar.</strong> These users are worth, at the low end averages, $36 per month.\r\n\r\nOur marketing plan will allow us to gain significant user acceptance. By partnering with strategic organizations, charities, carriers, and other large companies we can hit our first goal of 1% of the smartphone users (1.75 million users) by the end of 2014.\r\n\r\nThat would bring in a mind blowing $54 million per month in revenues.\r\n<h4>And this is not even the best part of the app - the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side can work.</a></h4>\r\n<h4>If you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h4>','Adora app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 15:49:05','2014-04-30 15:49:05','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(81,1,'2014-04-30 16:00:25','2014-04-30 16:00:25','<img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Many could use a little help.\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">Many more people would love to help.</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have an app in development to make all of this easier. The focus of the app is to deliver ads to users, to pay those users up to $15 a month for letting us deliver ads to them, then ask those users to donate at least $1 per month of their earnings. <strong>We then match these donations, dollar for dollar. </strong><em>\r\n</em></span>\r\n\r\nOur app will be attractive to those who want to save a buck or 15, but what about those who do not care about the cost of their cell phone plan?\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />This is where we really push the fact that we are willing to match their full potential of $15 per month, dollar for dollar. Just to make it easy on everyone--<em>that is up to $30 per cell phone</em> user donated to charity. We know that $30 per month is nothing to get too excited about, but if you multiply that by thousands of people every month we could be donating $30,000 - $300,000 or even $3,000,000<em> per month</em> to a charity of our users\' choice.\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">It is simple: the advertising pays for charity work.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">By partnering with strategic organizations, charities, carriers, and other large companies, we can hit our first goal of 1% of the 150 million smartphone user market by the middle of 2015. Yes that is 1.5 million users, and yes we know that is crazy user engagement in a short time. This will help us donate up to 3 million dollars <strong>per month</strong> to charities that we vet. If you want to find out more about our marketing plan, <a href=\"info@lscapp.com\">email us</a>. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our requirements for the charities before getting money from us will be:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 24px;\">No less than 85% of all funds donated must go directly to the key activities of the cause, now this does not mean that no more than 15% can go to \'overhead\' only that it must be an activity that can benefit the cause. We want to work with these charities and make sure that most of their efforts are productive. Fundraising can be productive, getting great talent can be productive, marketing can be productive, tech investments can be productive yet these are all considered traditionally overhead in the non-profit world.</span></li>\r\n	<li>Legal work using donated funds will be heavily scrutinized. We love the legal system but we would rather feed children than pay lawyers.</li>\r\n	<li>Organizations run by religious groups will be heavily scrutinized. We want to make sure everyone is served; not just individuals who share a faith or ideology.</li>\r\n	<li>Medical research will be vetted heavily to make sure funds are going to research that is making strides not spinning wheels. We would love to see families who are struggling with heavily researched medical issues be supported.</li>\r\n	<li>We will not support organizations which participate heavily in political donations, activity, or lobbying. If there is a cause that needs representation at state and federal levels then let us know and we will work together on how to address that.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe bottom line: we want our donations to get to people who need it.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here are some numbers on how we can impact our communities:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>First off let\'s assume our app is awesome, and it gains great market acceptance and we grow like crazy. But let\'s just start at that 1% (1.5 million) of the market. Good, now that we have that out of the way.</li>\r\n	<li>We would love to have all of our users donate their entire $15 max, then we match that, which equals $30 total. But to be realistic that group might make up around 10% (150,000) of our total active users, giving us a potential total of $4.5 million a month from these users.</li>\r\n	<li>If the rest of the 1.35 million users donate $1, and we match that, then it equals $2. We get monthly donation funds of... $2.7 million plus the users\' donations from point number 2, then we get <strong>$7.2 million a month.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<a href=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\"><img class=\"alignright\" src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"288\" /></a>Sounds crazy right... Well Candy Crush Saga, yes we just referenced that game, has over 100 million active users!\r\n\r\nIt makes over $600,000 a day, and over $230 million a year <strong>AND</strong> our app has the potential to blow that away!\r\n\r\nIf we can donate $7.2 million a month, here is just a glimpse at some of the things we can do with that:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>@ $200 per child = 36,000 kids <strong>clothing &amp; school supplies</strong> for a year</li>\r\n	<li>@ $3.50 per meal = over 2.0 million <strong>meals</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per procedure = 72,000<strong> dental procedures</strong> for underprivileged families</li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per month = 72,000 <strong>Public Transit passes</strong> for a month to un/under employed</li>\r\n	<li>@$2,000 per month = 3,600 families <strong>sheltered and given job training</strong> per month</li>\r\n	<li>@ $5,000 per semester = 1440 <strong>scholarships</strong> to under-funded college students</li>\r\n	<li>@ $25,000 per child = 288 families <strong>supported during life threatening medical issues</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100,000 per unit = We can deliver a self-sustaining water solution to 72 locations, and <strong>provide clean water</strong> where thousands die every year from unclean water...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf we donated all but a fraction of our revenues to efforts like this we would find joy and satisfaction in our existence and our app. But we can have both an amazing impact through our donations <strong>and</strong> have a healthy profit margin; this is a \"win/win\" opportunity.\r\n\r\nWe also want to help small businesses by providing them with free help when it comes to learning how to advertise and how to get results.\r\n\r\nWe want to give large brands the reach and impact they are looking for every day.\r\n\r\nWe want to provide an amazing return for our investors so they can go out and invest more in companies that do good.\r\n\r\nWe want to talk to you.\r\n<h3>If you want to become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h3>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-04-30 16:00:25','2014-04-30 16:00:25','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(78,1,'2014-04-30 15:55:26','2014-04-30 15:55:26','<a href=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-252 alignright\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" /></a>Many could use a little help.\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">Many more people would love to help.</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have an app in development to make all of this easier. The focus of the app is to deliver ads to users, to pay those users up to $15 a month for letting us deliver ads to them, then ask those users to donate at least $1 per month of their earnings. <strong>We then match these donations, dollar for dollar. </strong><em>\r\n</em></span>\r\n\r\nOur app will be attractive to those who want to save a buck or 15, but what about those who do not care about the cost of their cell phone plan?\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" /></a>This is where we really push the fact that we are willing to match their full potential of $15 per month, dollar for dollar. Just to make it easy on everyone--<em>that is up to $30 per cell phone</em> user donated to charity. We know that $30 per month is nothing to get too excited about, but if you multiply that by thousands of people every month we could be donating $30,000 - $300,000 or even $3,000,000<em> per month</em> to a charity of our users\' choice.\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">It is simple: the advertising pays for charity work.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-heigh