','open','','152-revision-v1','','','2014-05-06 01:38:43','2014-05-06 01:38:43','',152,'http://getadora.com/152-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(160,5,'2014-03-11 01:41:39','2014-03-11 01:41:39','<img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/52177dd269bedd547d000000/an-architecture-student-transformed-a-school-bus-into-a-mobile-home-and-is-taking-it-on-a-cross-country-tour.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"386\" height=\"290\" /><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://cocktailmixing.junio.vistec.net/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/shipsunset1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"289\" height=\"290\" />\r\n\r\nJim Collins talks about this concept in terms of a bus but I actually like to change it up and make it a big sail boat. Not a modern sailing ship but one that takes a team to sail, one that pushes the crew to make it through a storm.\r\n\r\nThe point to Jim\'s Bus concept is to think about who you\'d want on that bus or ship. Who could you sail for a year with in tight quarters, through easy and especially the hard times?\r\n\r\nWhen you think about this from a team building perspective I think we would all look a little more closely at who we pick to be a part of what we are building - I know we are.','The Bus','','publish','open','open','','bus','','','2014-05-08 00:33:23','2014-05-08 00:33:23','',0,'http://getadora.com/?p=160',0,'post','',0),(161,1,'2014-05-06 01:41:39','2014-05-06 01:41:39','<img class=\"alignright\" src=\"http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/52177dd269bedd547d000000/an-architecture-student-transformed-a-school-bus-into-a-mobile-home-and-is-taking-it-on-a-cross-country-tour.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"391\" height=\"294\" />Jim Collins talks about this concept in terms of a bus but I actually like to change it up and make it a big sail boat, like','The Bus','','inherit','open','open','','160-revision-v1','','','2014-05-06 01:41:39','2014-05-06 01:41:39','',160,'http://getadora.com/160-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(162,1,'2014-05-06 01:57:03',