l be:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 24px;\">No less than 85% of all funds donated must go directly to the key activities of the cause, now this does not mean that no more than 15% can go to \'overhead\' only that it must be an activity that can benefit the cause. We want to work with these charities and make sure that most of their efforts are productive. Fundraising can be productive, getting great talent can be productive, marketing can be productive, tech investments can be productive yet these are all considered traditionally overhead in the non-profit world.</span></li>\r\n	<li>Legal work using donated funds will be heavily scrutinized. We love the legal system but we would rather feed children than pay lawyers.</li>\r\n	<li>Organizations run by religious groups will be heavily scrutinized. We want to make sure everyone is served; not just individuals who share a faith or ideology.</li>\r\n	<li>Medical research will be vetted heavily to make sure funds are going to research that is making strides not spinning wheels. We would love to see families who are struggling with heavily researched medical issues be supported.</li>\r\n	<li>We will not support organizations which participate heavily in political donations, activity, or lobbying. If there is a cause that needs representation at state and federal levels then let us know and we will work together on how to address that.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe bottom line: we want our donations to get to people who need it.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here are some numbers on how we can impact our communities:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>First off let\'s assume our app is awesome, and it gains great market acceptance and we grow like crazy. But let\'s just start at that 1% (1.5 million) of the market. Good, now that we have that out of the way.</li>\r\n	<li>We would love to have all of our users donate their entire $15 max, then we match that, which equals $30 total. But to be realistic that group might make up around 10% (150,000) of our total active users, giving us a potential total of $4.5 million a month from these users.</li>\r\n	<li>If the rest of the 1.35 million users donate $1, and we match that, then it equals $2. We get monthly donation funds of... $2.7 million plus the users\' donations from point number 2, then we get <strong>$7.2 million a month.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<a href=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\"><img class=\"alignright\" src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"288\" /></a>Sounds crazy right... Well Candy Crush Saga, yes we just referenced that game, has over 100 million active users!\r\n\r\nIt makes over $600,000 a day, and over $230 million a year <strong>AND</strong> our app has the potential to blow that away!\r\n\r\nIf we can donate $7.2 million a month, here is just a glimpse at some of the things we can do with that:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>@ $200 per child = 36,000 kids <strong>clothing &amp; school supplies</strong> for a year</li>\r\n	<li>@ $3.50 per meal = over 2.0 million <strong>meals</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per procedure = 72,000<strong> dental procedures</strong> for underprivileged families</li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per month = 72,000 <strong>Public Transit passes</strong> for a month to un/under employed</li>\r\n	<li>@$2,000 per month = 3,600 families <strong>sheltered and given job training</strong> per month</li>\r\n	<li>@ $5,000 per semester = 1440 <strong>scholarships</strong> to under-funded college students</li>\r\n	<li>@ $25,000 per child = 288 families <strong>supported during life threatening medical issues</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100,000 per unit = We can deliver a self-sustaining water solution to 72 locations, and <strong>provide clean water</strong> where thousands die every year from unclean water...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf we donated all but a fraction of our revenues to efforts like this we would find joy and satisfaction in our existence and our app. But we can have both an amazing impact through our donations <strong>and</strong> have a healthy profit margin; this is a \"win/win\" opportunity.\r\n\r\nWe also want to help small businesses by providing them with free help when it comes to learning how to advertise and how to get results.\r\n\r\nWe want to give large brands the reach and impact they are looking for every day.\r\n\r\nWe want to provide an amazing return for our investors so they can go out and invest more in companies that do good.\r\n\r\nWe want to talk to you.\r\n<h3>If you want to become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h3>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 07:39:57','2014-05-09 07:39:57','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(263,1,'2014-05-09 07:52:47','2014-05-09 07:52:47','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do they/we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">By creating strategic relationships we can hit our first goal of 1% of the 200 million smartphone user market by the middle of 2015. The math plays that 1% out to equal 2 million users, when compared to the 100 million Candy Crush users we would hope that at least 2% would be willing to support such a charitable cause. If you want to find out more about how we are going to gather these users, about our marketing plan, <a href=\"info@lscapp.com\">email us</a>. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our requirements for the charities before getting money from us will be:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 24px;\">No less than 85% of all funds donated must go directly to the key activities of the cause, now this does not mean that no more than 15% can go to \'overhead\' only that it must be an activity that can benefit the cause. We want to work with these charities and make sure that most of their efforts are productive. Fundraising can be productive, getting great talent can be productive, marketing can be productive, tech investments can be productive yet these are all considered traditionally overhead in the non-profit world.</span></li>\r\n	<li>Legal work using donated funds will be heavily scrutinized. We love the legal system but we would rather feed children than pay lawyers.</li>\r\n	<li>Organizations run by religious groups will be heavily scrutinized. We want to make sure everyone is served; not just individuals who share a faith or ideology.</li>\r\n	<li>Medical research will be vetted heavily to make sure funds are going to research that is making strides not spinning wheels. We would love to see families who are struggling with heavily researched medical issues be supported.</li>\r\n	<li>We will not support organizations which participate heavily in political donations, activity, or lobbying. If there is a cause that needs representation at state and federal levels then let us know and we will work together on how to address that.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe bottom line: we want our donations to get to people who need it.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here are some numbers on how we can impact our communities:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>First off let\'s assume our app is awesome, and it gains great market acceptance and we grow like crazy. But let\'s just start at that 1% (1.5 million) of the market. Good, now that we have that out of the way.</li>\r\n	<li>We would love to have all of our users donate their entire $15 max, then we match that, which equals $30 total. But to be realistic that group might make up around 10% (150,000) of our total active users, giving us a potential total of $4.5 million a month from these users.</li>\r\n	<li>If the rest of the 1.35 million users donate $1, and we match that, then it equals $2. We get monthly donation funds of... $2.7 million plus the users\' donations from point number 2, then we get <strong>$7.2 million a month.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<a href=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\"><img class=\"alignright\" src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"288\" /></a>Sounds crazy right... Well Candy Crush Saga, yes we just referenced that game, has over 100 million active users!\r\n\r\nIt makes over $600,000 a day, and over $230 million a year <strong>AND</strong> our app has the potential to blow that away!\r\n\r\nIf we can donate $7.2 million a month, here is just a glimpse at some of the things we can do with that:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>@ $200 per child = 36,000 kids <strong>clothing &amp; school supplies</strong> for a year</li>\r\n	<li>@ $3.50 per meal = over 2.0 million <strong>meals</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per procedure = 72,000<strong> dental procedures</strong> for underprivileged families</li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per month = 72,000 <strong>Public Transit passes</strong> for a month to un/under employed</li>\r\n	<li>@$2,000 per month = 3,600 families <strong>sheltered and given job training</strong> per month</li>\r\n	<li>@ $5,000 per semester = 1440 <strong>scholarships</strong> to under-funded college students</li>\r\n	<li>@ $25,000 per child = 288 families <strong>supported during life threatening medical issues</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100,000 per unit = We can deliver a self-sustaining water solution to 72 locations, and <strong>provide clean water</strong> where thousands die every year from unclean water...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf we donated all but a fraction of our revenues to efforts like this we would find joy and satisfaction in our existence and our app. But we can have both an amazing impact through our donations <strong>and</strong> have a healthy profit margin; this is a \"win/win\" opportunity.\r\n\r\nWe also want to help small businesses by providing them with free help when it comes to learning how to advertise and how to get results.\r\n\r\nWe want to give large brands the reach and impact they are looking for every day.\r\n\r\nWe want to provide an amazing return for our investors so they can go out and invest more in companies that do good.\r\n\r\nWe want to talk to you.\r\n<h3>If you want to become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h3>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 07:52:47','2014-05-09 07:52:47','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(264,1,'2014-05-09 07:56:12','2014-05-09 07:56:12','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do they/we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">By creating strategic relationships we can hit our first goal of 1% of the 200 million smartphone user market by the middle of 2015. The math plays that 1% out to equal 2 million users, when compared to the 100 million Candy Crush users we would hope that at least 2% would be willing to support such a charitable cause. If you want to find out more about how we are going to gather these users, about our marketing plan, <a href=\"info@lscapp.com\">email us</a>. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our requirements for the charities before getting money from us will be:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 24px;\">No less than 85% of all funds donated must go directly to the key activities of the cause, now this does not mean that no more than 15% can go to \'overhead\' only that it must be an activity that can benefit the cause. We want to work with these charities and make sure that most of their efforts are productive. Fundraising can be productive, getting great talent can be productive, marketing can be productive, tech investments can be productive yet these are all considered traditionally overhead in the non-profit world.</span></li>\r\n	<li>Legal work using donated funds will be heavily scrutinized. We love the legal system but we would rather feed children than pay lawyers.</li>\r\n	<li>Organizations run by religious groups will be heavily scrutinized. We want to make sure everyone is served; not just individuals who share a faith or ideology.</li>\r\n	<li>Medical research will be vetted heavily to make sure funds are going to research that is making strides not spinning wheels. We would love to see families who are struggling with heavily researched medical issues be supported.</li>\r\n	<li>We will not support organizations which participate heavily in political donations, activity, or lobbying. If there is a cause that needs representation at state and federal levels then let us know and we will work together on how to address that.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe bottom line: we want our donations to get to people who need it.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here are some numbers on how we can impact our communities:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>First off let\'s assume our app is awesome, and it gains great market acceptance and we grow like crazy. But let\'s just start at that 1% (1.5 million) of the market. Good, now that we have that out of the way.</li>\r\n	<li>We would love to have all of our users donate their entire $15 max, then we match that, which equals $30 total. But to be realistic that group might make up around 10% (150,000) of our total active users, giving us a potential total of $4.5 million a month from these users.</li>\r\n	<li>If the rest of the 1.35 million users donate $1, and we match that, then it equals $2. We get monthly donation funds of... $2.7 million plus the users\' donations from point number 2, then we get <strong>$7.2 million a month.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<a href=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\"><img class=\"alignright\" src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"288\" /></a>Sounds crazy right... Well Candy Crush Saga, yes we just referenced that game, has over 100 million active users!\r\n\r\nIt makes over $600,000 a day, and over $230 million a year <strong>AND</strong> our app has the potential to blow that away!\r\n\r\nIf we can donate $7.2 million a month, here is just a glimpse at some of the things we can do with that:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>@ $200 per child = 36,000 kids <strong>clothing &amp; school supplies</strong> for a year</li>\r\n	<li>@ $3.50 per meal = over 2.0 million <strong>meals</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per procedure = 72,000<strong> dental procedures</strong> for underprivileged families</li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per month = 72,000 <strong>Public Transit passes</strong> for a month to un/under employed</li>\r\n	<li>@$2,000 per month = 3,600 families <strong>sheltered and given job training</strong> per month</li>\r\n	<li>@ $5,000 per semester = 1440 <strong>scholarships</strong> to under-funded college students</li>\r\n	<li>@ $25,000 per child = 288 families <strong>supported during life threatening medical issues</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100,000 per unit = We can deliver a self-sustaining water solution to 72 locations, and <strong>provide clean water</strong> where thousands die every year from unclean water...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf we donated all but a fraction of our revenues to efforts like this we would find joy and satisfaction in our existence and our app. But we can have both an amazing impact through our donations <strong>and</strong> have a healthy profit margin; this is a \"win/win\" opportunity.\r\n\r\nWe also want to help small businesses by providing them with free help when it comes to learning how to advertise and how to get results.\r\n\r\nWe want to give large brands the reach and impact they are looking for every day.\r\n\r\nWe want to provide an amazing return for our investors so they can go out and invest more in companies that do good.\r\n\r\nWe want to talk to you.\r\n<h3>If you want to become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h3>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 07:56:12','2014-05-09 07:56:12','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(268,1,'2014-05-09 08:09:05','2014-05-09 08:09:05','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do they/we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">By creating strategic relationships we can hit our first goal of 1% of the 200 million smartphone user market by the middle of 2015. The math plays that 1% out to equal 2 million users, when compared to the 100 million Candy Crush users we would hope that at least 2% would be willing to support such a charitable cause. If you want to find out more about how we are going to gather these users, about our marketing plan, <a href=\"info@lscapp.com\">email us</a>. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want to become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 08:09:05','2014-05-09 08:09:05','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(266,1,'2014-05-09 08:02:34','2014-05-09 08:02:34','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do they/we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">By creating strategic relationships we can hit our first goal of 1% of the 200 million smartphone user market by the middle of 2015. The math plays that 1% out to equal 2 million users, when compared to the 100 million Candy Crush users we would hope that at least 2% would be willing to support such a charitable cause. If you want to find out more about how we are going to gather these users, about our marketing plan, <a href=\"info@lscapp.com\">email us</a>. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\r\n<strong>If you want to become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 08:02:34','2014-05-09 08:02:34','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(265,1,'2014-05-09 08:01:31','2014-05-09 08:01:31','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do they/we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">By creating strategic relationships we can hit our first goal of 1% of the 200 million smartphone user market by the middle of 2015. The math plays that 1% out to equal 2 million users, when compared to the 100 million Candy Crush users we would hope that at least 2% would be willing to support such a charitable cause. If you want to find out more about how we are going to gather these users, about our marketing plan, <a href=\"info@lscapp.com\">email us</a>. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our requirements for the charities before getting money from us will be:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 24px;\">No less than 85% of all funds donated must go directly to the key activities of the cause, now this does not mean that no more than 15% can go to \'overhead\' only that it must be an activity that can benefit the cause. We want to work with these charities and make sure that most of their efforts are productive. Fundraising can be productive, getting great talent can be productive, marketing can be productive, tech investments can be productive yet these are all considered traditionally overhead in the non-profit world.</span></li>\r\n	<li>Legal work using donated funds will be heavily scrutinized. We love the legal system but we would rather feed children than pay lawyers.</li>\r\n	<li>Organizations run by religious groups will be heavily scrutinized. We want to make sure everyone is served; not just individuals who share a faith or ideology.</li>\r\n	<li>Medical research will be vetted heavily to make sure funds are going to research that is making strides not spinning wheels. We would love to see families who are struggling with heavily researched medical issues be supported.</li>\r\n	<li>We will not support organizations which participate heavily in political donations, activity, or lobbying. If there is a cause that needs representation at state and federal levels then let us know and we will work together on how to address that.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe bottom line: we want our donations to get to people who need it.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here are some numbers on how we can impact our communities:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>First off let\'s assume our app is awesome, and it gains great market acceptance and we grow like crazy. But let\'s just start at that 1% (1.5 million) of the market. Good, now that we have that out of the way.</li>\r\n	<li>We would love to have all of our users donate their entire $15 max, then we match that, which equals $30 total. But to be realistic that group might make up around 10% (150,000) of our total active users, giving us a potential total of $4.5 million a month from these users.</li>\r\n	<li>If the rest of the 1.35 million users donate $1, and we match that, then it equals $2. We get monthly donation funds of... $2.7 million plus the users\' donations from point number 2, then we get <strong>$7.2 million a month.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<a href=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\"><img class=\"alignright\" src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/DLDifF6R6ETGoHBPAfEDcwbRnZiTvty074hd0WQuRJug7RbfR7ihrkZXgt5zACKejbL6=h900\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"288\" /></a>Sounds crazy right... Well Candy Crush Saga, yes we just referenced that game, has over 100 million active users!\r\n\r\nIt makes over $600,000 a day, and over $230 million a year <strong>AND</strong> our app has the potential to blow that away!\r\n\r\nIf we can donate $7.2 million a month, here is just a glimpse at some of the things we can do with that:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>@ $200 per child = 36,000 kids <strong>clothing &amp; school supplies</strong> for a year</li>\r\n	<li>@ $3.50 per meal = over 2.0 million <strong>meals</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per procedure = 72,000<strong> dental procedures</strong> for underprivileged families</li>\r\n	<li>@ $100 per month = 72,000 <strong>Public Transit passes</strong> for a month to un/under employed</li>\r\n	<li>@$2,000 per month = 3,600 families <strong>sheltered and given job training</strong> per month</li>\r\n	<li>@ $5,000 per semester = 1440 <strong>scholarships</strong> to under-funded college students</li>\r\n	<li>@ $25,000 per child = 288 families <strong>supported during life threatening medical issues</strong></li>\r\n	<li>@ $100,000 per unit = We can deliver a self-sustaining water solution to 72 locations, and <strong>provide clean water</strong> where thousands die every year from unclean water...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf we donated all but a fraction of our revenues to efforts like this we would find joy and satisfaction in our existence and our app. But we can have both an amazing impact through our donations <strong>and</strong> have a healthy profit margin; this is a \"win/win\" opportunity.\r\n\r\nWe also want to help small businesses by providing them with free help when it comes to learning how to advertise and how to get results.\r\n\r\nWe want to give large brands the reach and impact they are looking for every day.\r\n\r\nWe want to provide an amazing return for our investors so they can go out and invest more in companies that do good.\r\n\r\nWe want to talk to you.\r\n<h3>If you want to become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h3>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 08:01:31','2014-05-09 08:01:31','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(271,1,'2014-05-09 08:27:41','2014-05-09 08:27:41','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do they/we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a moving hashtag spreading via twitter or a viral video, we know that there are a few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 08:27:41','2014-05-09 08:27:41','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(270,1,'2014-05-09 08:21:35','2014-05-09 08:21:35','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do they/we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a moving hashtag spreading via twitter or a viral video we know that there are a few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">By creating strategic relationships we can hit our first goal of 1% of the 200 million smartphone user market by the middle of 2015. The math plays that 1% out to equal 2 million users, when compared to the 100 million Candy Crush users we would hope that at least 2% would be willing to support such a charitable cause. If you want to find out more about how we are going to gather these users, about our marketing plan, <a href=\"info@lscapp.com\">email us</a>. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want to become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 08:21:35','2014-05-09 08:21:35','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(273,1,'2014-05-09 08:43:48','2014-05-09 08:43:48','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a moving hashtag spreading via twitter or a viral video, we know that there are a few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 08:43:48','2014-05-09 08:43:48','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(272,1,'2014-05-09 08:40:28','2014-05-09 08:40:28','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a moving hashtag spreading via twitter or a viral video, we know that there are a few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 08:40:28','2014-05-09 08:40:28','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(274,1,'2014-05-09 08:47:05','2014-05-09 08:47:05','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good we could do with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a moving hashtag spreading via twitter or a viral video, we know that there are a few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 08:47:05','2014-05-09 08:47:05','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(275,1,'2014-05-09 08:48:20','2014-05-09 08:48:20','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 150px;\">So many people would love to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why do we not do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves both of those problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good we could do with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But even once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a moving hashtag spreading via twitter or a viral video, we know that there are a few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 08:48:20','2014-05-09 08:48:20','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(276,1,'2014-05-09 10:10:04','2014-05-09 10:10:04','<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"338\" height=\"166\" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically increase user engagement with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus increasing our value to advertisers and therefore increasing our ability to contribute to organizations who do good.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\nThis brings us to <strong>Our Vision:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>It is our goal to be the most charitable company in the world within then next 5 years.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of 0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits to good causes. We get to this point and how much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n<h2>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that set us apart. Over then next few months we will present a mystery to the world. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this mystery and we will share how with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nRight now many of us are doing one specific thing over and over again, and more than likely you will do this one thing a few times as you read this. We want to take that one action and turn it into a way for businesses, large and small, to reach you and everyone else in the world.\r\n<h2><strong>Google, Facebook, Twitter and all the rest.</strong></h2>\r\nRight now the top online advertising outlets are all trying to capture their piece of the pie, but they do it by offering something else. That something else comes with a lot of distractions, content, and anywhere from 5-12 or even more advertisements--competition. They want to provide value to increase user engagement, but they also want users to interact with the advertising. It is a difficult balance.\r\n\r\nWe want to help fill a void that has little to no competition, does not have distracting content, and is straightforward. We are going to deliver ads to you, and you are going to love it, use it all the time and soon life won\'t be the same with out us.\r\n\r\nHere are some important stats:\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"547\"]<a href=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\"><img src=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\" alt=\"US Smartphone Growth Projections\" width=\"547\" height=\"467\" /></a> Smartphone Growth[/caption]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The US alone will be rapidly approaching 200 million smartphones in use by the 2014 holiday season</li>\r\n	<li>Users wake up their phones over <a title=\"HTC One M8 Review and Research\" href=\"https://www.yahoo.com/tech/heres-why-people-are-so-excited-about-the-new-htc-one-80913367177.html\" target=\"_blank\">150 times a day</a> - We are using our phones for everything now.</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Advertising revenue is going to continue to grow as more and more time is spent on mobile platforms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobile Ad Revenue (Billions):\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2012 - $8.76</li>\r\n	<li>2013 - $17.96</li>\r\n	<li>2014 - $<em>31.45 (estimate)</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you could create an app which takes advantage of all of these factors, you could deliver ads to users in a way which creates great value to everyone involved.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur app does just this.\r\n\r\nOur marketing plan will allow us to gain significant user acceptance. By partnering with strategic organizations, charities, carriers, and other large companies we can hit our first goal of 1% of the smartphone users (1.75 million users) by the end of 2014.\r\n\r\nThat would bring in a mind blowing $54 million per month in revenues.\r\n<h4>And this is not even the best part of the app - the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side can work.</a></h4>\r\n<h4>If you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h4>','The app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 10:10:04','2014-05-09 10:10:04','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(280,1,'2014-05-09 10:13:56','2014-05-09 10:13:56','<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"481\" height=\"236\" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically increase user engagement with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus increasing our value to advertisers and therefore increasing our ability to contribute to organizations who do good.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n<h2><strong>Our Vision</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to be the most charitable company in the world within then next 5 years.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of 0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits to good causes. We get to this point and how much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n<h2>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that set us apart. Over then next few months we will present a mystery to the world. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this mystery and we will share how with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nRight now many of us are doing one specific thing over and over again, and more than likely you will do this one thing a few times as you read this. We want to take that one action and turn it into a way for businesses, large and small, to reach you and everyone else in the world.\r\n<h2><strong>Google, Facebook, Twitter and all the rest.</strong></h2>\r\nRight now the top online advertising outlets are all trying to capture their piece of the pie, but they do it by offering something else. That something else comes with a lot of distractions, content, and anywhere from 5-12 or even more advertisements--competition. They want to provide value to increase user engagement, but they also want users to interact with the advertising. It is a difficult balance.\r\n\r\nWe want to help fill a void that has little to no competition, does not have distracting content, and is straightforward. We are going to deliver ads to you, and you are going to love it, use it all the time and soon life won\'t be the same with out us.\r\n\r\nHere are some important stats:\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"547\"]<a href=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\"><img src=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\" alt=\"US Smartphone Growth Projections\" width=\"547\" height=\"467\" /></a> Smartphone Growth[/caption]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The US alone will be rapidly approaching 200 million smartphones in use by the 2014 holiday season</li>\r\n	<li>Users wake up their phones over <a title=\"HTC One M8 Review and Research\" href=\"https://www.yahoo.com/tech/heres-why-people-are-so-excited-about-the-new-htc-one-80913367177.html\" target=\"_blank\">150 times a day</a> - We are using our phones for everything now.</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Advertising revenue is going to continue to grow as more and more time is spent on mobile platforms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobile Ad Revenue (Billions):\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2012 - $8.76</li>\r\n	<li>2013 - $17.96</li>\r\n	<li>2014 - $<em>31.45 (estimate)</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you could create an app which takes advantage of all of these factors, you could deliver ads to users in a way which creates great value to everyone involved.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur app does just this.\r\n\r\nOur marketing plan will allow us to gain significant user acceptance. By partnering with strategic organizations, charities, carriers, and other large companies we can hit our first goal of 1% of the smartphone users (1.75 million users) by the end of 2014.\r\n\r\nThat would bring in a mind blowing $54 million per month in revenues.\r\n<h4>And this is not even the best part of the app - the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side can work.</a></h4>\r\n<h4>If you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h4>','The app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 10:13:56','2014-05-09 10:13:56','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(277,1,'2014-05-09 10:11:19','2014-05-09 10:11:19','<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"566\" height=\"278\" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically increase user engagement with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus increasing our value to advertisers and therefore increasing our ability to contribute to organizations who do good.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\nThis brings us to <strong>Our Vision:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>It is our goal to be the most charitable company in the world within then next 5 years.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of 0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits to good causes. We get to this point and how much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n<h2>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that set us apart. Over then next few months we will present a mystery to the world. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this mystery and we will share how with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nRight now many of us are doing one specific thing over and over again, and more than likely you will do this one thing a few times as you read this. We want to take that one action and turn it into a way for businesses, large and small, to reach you and everyone else in the world.\r\n<h2><strong>Google, Facebook, Twitter and all the rest.</strong></h2>\r\nRight now the top online advertising outlets are all trying to capture their piece of the pie, but they do it by offering something else. That something else comes with a lot of distractions, content, and anywhere from 5-12 or even more advertisements--competition. They want to provide value to increase user engagement, but they also want users to interact with the advertising. It is a difficult balance.\r\n\r\nWe want to help fill a void that has little to no competition, does not have distracting content, and is straightforward. We are going to deliver ads to you, and you are going to love it, use it all the time and soon life won\'t be the same with out us.\r\n\r\nHere are some important stats:\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"547\"]<a href=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\"><img src=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\" alt=\"US Smartphone Growth Projections\" width=\"547\" height=\"467\" /></a> Smartphone Growth[/caption]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The US alone will be rapidly approaching 200 million smartphones in use by the 2014 holiday season</li>\r\n	<li>Users wake up their phones over <a title=\"HTC One M8 Review and Research\" href=\"https://www.yahoo.com/tech/heres-why-people-are-so-excited-about-the-new-htc-one-80913367177.html\" target=\"_blank\">150 times a day</a> - We are using our phones for everything now.</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Advertising revenue is going to continue to grow as more and more time is spent on mobile platforms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobile Ad Revenue (Billions):\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2012 - $8.76</li>\r\n	<li>2013 - $17.96</li>\r\n	<li>2014 - $<em>31.45 (estimate)</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you could create an app which takes advantage of all of these factors, you could deliver ads to users in a way which creates great value to everyone involved.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur app does just this.\r\n\r\nOur marketing plan will allow us to gain significant user acceptance. By partnering with strategic organizations, charities, carriers, and other large companies we can hit our first goal of 1% of the smartphone users (1.75 million users) by the end of 2014.\r\n\r\nThat would bring in a mind blowing $54 million per month in revenues.\r\n<h4>And this is not even the best part of the app - the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side can work.</a></h4>\r\n<h4>If you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h4>','The app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 10:11:19','2014-05-09 10:11:19','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(278,1,'2014-05-09 10:11:41','2014-05-09 10:11:41','<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Dig