.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/SebasteanLoschSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-302 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/SebasteanLoschSmall.jpg\" alt=\"SebasteanLoschSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/ChristianSampsonSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-366 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/ChristianSampsonSmall.jpg\" alt=\"ChristianSampsonSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/DevinThorpeSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-425\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/DevinThorpeSmall.jpg\" alt=\"DevinThorpeSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/WayneCarrollSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-426\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/WayneCarrollSmall.jpg\" alt=\"WayneCarrollSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Man-WomanAvatar.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-304 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Man-WomanAvatar.jpg\" alt=\"Man-WomanAvatar\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are looking for a few good men and women. Are you interested in a challenging, exciting, fulfilling daily struggle? Hard work, humility, creativity, and passion are part of the culture here at Adora.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are looking for the following individuals:</p>\n\n<table class=\" aligncenter\" style=\"height: 27px; width: 657px;\" width=\"569\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Digital Advertising Guru</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Mobile Software Engineer</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Charity Relationship Manager</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you think you would not just fit in but flourish and could see yourself in a leadership position as we grow then by all means <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\">send us an email</a>.</p>\n<iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/zrHlkHdPF4U\" width=\"932\" height=\"524\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>','Team','','inherit','open','open','','64-autosave-v1','','','2014-05-30 16:03:12','2014-05-30 16:03:12','',64,'http://getadora.com/64-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(292,1,'2014-05-09 11:00:59','2014-05-09 11:00:59','&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically increase user engagement with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus increasing our value to advertisers and therefore increasing our ability to contribute to organizations who do good.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to be the most charitable company in the world within the next 5 years.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of 0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits to good causes. We get to this point and how much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that set us apart. Over then next few months we will present a mystery to the world. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this mystery and we will share how with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nRight now many of us are doing one specific thing over and over again, and more than likely you will do this one thing a few times as you read this. We want to take that one action and turn it into a way for businesses, large and small, to reach you and everyone else in the world.\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side can work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 11:00:59','2014-05-09 11:00:59','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(291,1,'2014-05-09 10:48:00','2014-05-09 10:48:00','&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically increase user engagement with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus increasing our value to advertisers and therefore increasing our ability to contribute to organizations who do good.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to be the most charitable company in the world within the next 5 years.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of 0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits to good causes. We get to this point and how much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that set us apart. Over then next few months we will present a mystery to the world. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this mystery and we will share how with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nRight now many of us are doing one specific thing over and over again, and more than likely you will do this one thing a few times as you read this. We want to take that one action and turn it into a way for businesses, large and small, to reach you and everyone else in the world.\r\n<h2><strong>Google, Facebook, Twitter and all the rest.</strong></h2>\r\nRight now the top online advertising outlets are all trying to capture their piece of the pie, but they do it by offering something else. That something else comes with a lot of distractions, content, and anywhere from 5-12 or even more advertisements--competition. They want to provide value to increase user engagement, but they also want users to interact with the advertising. It is a difficult balance.\r\n\r\nWe want to help fill a void that has little to no competition, does not have distracting content, and is straightforward. We are going to deliver ads to you, and you are going to love it, use it all the time and soon life won\'t be the same with out us.\r\n\r\nHere are some important stats:\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"547\"]<a href=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\"><img src=\"http://83-136-248-155.uk-lon1.host.upcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Screen-Shot-2013-10-08-at-10-8-9.41.00-PM.png\" alt=\"US Smartphone Growth Projections\" width=\"547\" height=\"467\" /></a> Smartphone Growth[/caption]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The US alone will be rapidly approaching 200 million smartphones in use by the 2014 holiday season</li>\r\n	<li>Users wake up their phones over <a title=\"HTC One M8 Review and Research\" href=\"https://www.yahoo.com/tech/heres-why-people-are-so-excited-about-the-new-htc-one-80913367177.html\" target=\"_blank\">150 times a day</a> - We are using our phones for everything now.</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Advertising revenue is going to continue to grow as more and more time is spent on mobile platforms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobile Ad Revenue (Billions):\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2012 - $8.76</li>\r\n	<li>2013 - $17.96</li>\r\n	<li>2014 - $<em>31.45 (estimate)</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you could create an app which takes advantage of all of these factors, you could deliver ads to users in a way which creates great value to everyone involved.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur app does just this.\r\n\r\nOur marketing plan will allow us to gain significant user acceptance. By partnering with strategic organizations, charities, carriers, and other large companies we can hit our first goal of 1% of the smartphone users (1.75 million users) by the end of 2014.\r\n\r\nThat would bring in a mind blowing $54 million per month in revenues.\r\n<h4>And this is not even the best part of the app - the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side can work.</a></h4>\r\n<h4>If you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></h4>','The app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 10:48:00','2014-05-09 10:48:00','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(295,1,'2014-05-09 12:38:58','2014-05-09 12:38:58','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">In the start-up world we have what would be considered a Dream Team. Click on any of us to learn more.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>','Team','','inherit','open','open','','64-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 12:38:58','2014-05-09 12:38:58','',64,'http://getadora.com/64-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(296,1,'2014-05-09 12:46:23','2014-05-09 12:46:23','','WayneCarrollSmall','','inherit','open','open','','waynecarrollsmall','','','2014-05-09 12:46:23','2014-05-09 12:46:23','',64,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/WayneCarrollSmall.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(297,1,'2014-05-09 12:46:24','2014-05-09 12:46:24','','BenFa\'anunuSmall','','inherit','open','open','','benfaanunusmall','','','2014-05-09 12:46:24','2014-05-09 12:46:24','',64,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/BenFaanunuSmall.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(298,1,'2014-05-09 12:46:25','2014-05-09 12:46:25','','JoeMichelsSmall','Joe Michels - CTO','inherit','open','open','','joemichelssmall','','','2014-05-09 12:46:25','2014-05-09 12:46:25','',64,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/JoeMichelsSmall.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(299,1,'2014-05-09 12:46:26','2014-05-09 12:46:26','','KyleThomasSmall','Kyle Thomas - Founder / CEO','inherit','open','open','','kylethomassmall','','','2014-05-09 12:46:26','2014-05-09 12:46:26','',64,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/KyleThomasSmall.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(300,1,'2014-05-09 12:46:27','2014-05-09 12:46:27','','MarkFeriante2Small','','inherit','open','open','','markferiante2small','','','2014-05-09 12:46:27','2014-05-09 12:46:27','',64,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/MarkFeriante2Small.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(301,1,'2014-05-09 12:46:28','2014-05-09 12:46:28','','MarkFerianteSmall','','inherit','open','open','','markferiantesmall','','','2014-05-09 12:46:28','2014-05-09 12:46:28','',0,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/MarkFerianteSmall.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(302,1,'2014-05-09 12:46:29','2014-05-09 12:46:29','','Seba