etadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/BenFaanunuSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-299 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/KyleThomasSmall.jpg\" alt=\"KyleThomasSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-297 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/BenFaanunuSmall.jpg\" alt=\"BenFa\'anunuSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/MarkFeriante2Small.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-300 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/MarkFeriante2Small.jpg\" alt=\"MarkFeriante2Small\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/JoeMichelsSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-298 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/JoeMichelsSmall.jpg\" alt=\"JoeMichelsSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/SebasteanLoschSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-302 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/SebasteanLoschSmall.jpg\" alt=\"SebasteanLoschSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/WayneCarrollSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-296 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/WayneCarrollSmall.jpg\" alt=\"WayneCarrollSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Man-WomanAvatar.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-304 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Man-WomanAvatar.jpg\" alt=\"Man-WomanAvatar\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are looking for a few good men and women. Are you interested in a challenging, exciting, fulfilling daily struggle? Hard work, humility, creativity, and passion are part of the culture here at Adora.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are looking for individuals with:</p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\" aligncenter\" style=\"height: 109px;\" width=\"672\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Digital Advertising Guru</strong>\r\n\r\nMobile experience is great but not a requirement.</td>\r\n<td><strong>Mobile Software Engineer</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are looking for both iOS and Android Developers.</td>\r\n<td><strong>Charity Relationship Manager</strong>\r\n\r\nWe need amazing people to manage these important relationships</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you think you would not just fit in but flourish and could see yourself in a leadership position as we grow then by all means send us an email.</p>','Team','','inherit','open','open','','64-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 13:45:44','2014-05-09 13:45:44','',64,'http://getadora.com/64-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(309,1,'2014-05-09 13:53:03','2014-05-09 13:53:03','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">In the start-up world we have what would be considered a Dream Team. Click on any of us to learn more.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/BenFaanunuSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-299 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/KyleThomasSmall.jpg\" alt=\"KyleThomasSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-297 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/BenFaanunuSmall.jpg\" alt=\"BenFa\'anunuSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/MarkFeriante2Small.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-300 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/MarkFeriante2Small.jpg\" alt=\"MarkFeriante2Small\" width=\"200\" he