g.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of our team, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 13:58:39','2014-05-09 13:58:39','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(316,1,'2014-05-09 14:17:50','2014-05-09 14:17:50','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">In the start-up world we have what would be considered a Dream Team. Click on any of us to learn more.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/BenFaanunuSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-299 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/KyleThomasSmall.jpg\" alt=\"KyleThomasSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-297 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/BenFaanunuSmall.jpg\" alt=\"BenFa\'anunuSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/MarkFeriante2Small.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-300 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/MarkFeriante2Small.jpg\" alt=\"MarkFeriante2Small\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/JoeMichelsSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-298 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/JoeMichelsSmall.jpg\" alt=\"JoeMichelsSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/SebasteanLoschSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-302 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/SebasteanLoschSmall.jpg\" alt=\"SebasteanLoschSmall\" width=\"2