" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/WayneCarrollSmall.jpg\" alt=\"WayneCarrollSmall\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Man-WomanAvatar.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-304 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Man-WomanAvatar.jpg\" alt=\"Man-WomanAvatar\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are looking for a few good men and women. Are you interested in a challenging, exciting, fulfilling daily struggle? Hard work, humility, creativity, and passion are part of the culture here at Adora.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are looking for the following individuals:</p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\" aligncenter\" style=\"height: 27px; width: 657px;\" width=\"569\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Digital Advertising Guru</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Mobile Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Charity Relationship Manager</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you think you would not just fit in but flourish and could see yourself in a leadership position as we grow then by all means <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\">send us an email</a>.</p>\r\n<iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/zrHlkHdPF4U\" width=\"932\" height=\"524\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>','Team','','inherit','open','open','','64-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 14:19:46','2014-05-09 14:19:46','',64,'http://getadora.com/64-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(323,1,'2014-05-09 23:08:51','2014-05-09 23:08:51','I\'ve always been of two minds when it comes to my being a leader. One side of the conversation realizes just how unprepared I am when I look at my ambitions and where I want to go. The other reminds me that every leader has been required to go through the same stages of growth that I have, and so many that I will still need to go through.\r\n\r\nI am an interesting case when it comes to leadership.\r\n\r\nI come from a humble background and it is, without a doubt, one of my greatest points of development. I\'m a forth generation Farmer/Rancher and while my father and I have not been full time in the fields we\'ve both spent enough time to keep up with the best out there. My father was a general contractor and I can\'t remember when I first started swinging a hammer on a job site, no not in fun but as a smaller but still productive part of the crew. Both my father and grandfather dabbled in entrepreneurial efforts and some panned out while most didn\'t.\r\n\r\nThis background doesn\'t stack up to so many others when I look at the history of leadership, but it does with a few.\r\n\r\nI have a bit of a chip on my shoulder because I don\'t have a college degree. At the same time when I talk to many who do I realize that the paper on the wall doesn\'t make them any more educated than I am. Many kids go through college trying to learn just enough to pass a test or a class while my education has been carefully and deliberately sought out.','An Interesting Leadership Conversation','','draft','open','open','','interesting-leadership-conversation','','','2014-05-10 03:23:32','2014-05-10 03:23:32','',0,'http://getadora.com/?p=323',0,'post','',0),(324,1,'2014-05-09 15:03:25','2014-05-09 15:03:25','I\'ve always been of two minds when it comes to my being a leader. One side of the conversation realizes just how unprepared I am when I look at my ambitions and where I want to go. The other reminds me that every leader has been required to go through the same stages of growth that I have, and will still need to go through.\r\n\r\nI am an interesting case when it comes to leadership.\r\n\r\nI come from a humble background and it is, without a doubt, one of my greatest points of development. I\'m a forth generation Farmer/Rancher and while my father and I have not been full time in the fields we\'ve both spent enough time to keep up with the best out there. My father was a general contractor and I can\'t remember when I first started swinging a hammer on a job site, no not in fun but as a smaller but still productive part of the crew. Both my father and grandfather dabbled in entrepreneurial efforts and some panned out while most didn\'t.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nI have a bit of a chip on my shoulder because I don\'t have a college degree. At the same time when I talk to many who do I realize that the paper on the wall doesn\'t make them any more educated than I am. Many kids go through college trying to learn just enough to pass a test or a class while my education has been carefully and deliberately sought out.','An Interesting Leadership Conversation','','inherit','open','open','','323-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 15:03:25','2014-05-09 15:03:25','',323,'http://getadora.com/323-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(325,1,'2014-05-09 23:08:51','2014-05-09 23:08:51','I\'ve always been of two minds when it comes to my being a leader. One side of the conversation realizes just how unprepared I am when I look at my ambitions and where I want to go. The other reminds me that every leader has been required to go through the same stages of growth that I have, and so many that I will still need to go through.\r\n\r\nI am an interesting case when it comes to leadership.\r\n\r\nI come from a humble background and it is, without a doubt, one of my greatest points of development. I\'m a forth generation Farmer/Rancher and while my father and I have not been full time in the fields we\'ve both spent enough time to keep up with the best out there. My father was a general contractor and I can\'t remember when I first started swinging a hammer on a job site, no not in fun but as a smaller but still productive part of the crew. Both my father and grandfather dabbled in entrepreneurial efforts and some panned out while most didn\'t.\r\n\r\nThis background doesn\'t stack up to so many others when I look at the history of leadership, but it does with a few.\r\n\r\nI have a bit of a chip on my shoulder because I don\'t have a college degree. At the same time when I talk to many who do I realize that the paper on the wall doesn\'t make them any more educated than I am. Many kids go through college trying to learn just enough to pass a test or a class while my education has been carefully and deliberately sought out.','An Interesting Leadership Conversation','','inherit','open','open','','323-revision-v1','','','2014-05-09 23:08:51','2014-05-09 23:08:51','',323,'http://getadora.com/323-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(326,1,'2014-05-09 23:09:12','2014-05-09 23:09:12','','LogoLarge','','inherit','open','open','','logo','','','2014-05-09 23:09:12','2014-05-09 23:09:12','',51,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Logo.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(327,1,'2014-05-09 23:09:35','2014-05-09 23:09:35','','AppIcon_01','','inherit','open','open','','appicon_01','','','2014-05-09 23:09:35','2014-05-09 23:09:35','',0,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/AppIcon_01.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(333,1,'2014-05-10 04:00:43','2014-05-10 04:00:43','','ReachingToHelp','','inherit','open','open','','reachingtohelp','','','2014-05-10 04:00:43','2014-05-10 04:00:43','',0,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/ReachingToHelp.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(336,1,'2014-05-11 04:25:01','2014-05-11 04:25:01','&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically increase user engagement with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus increasing our value to advertisers and therefore increasing our ability to contribute to organizations who do good.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to be the most charitable company in the world within the next 5 years.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of 0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that set us apart. Over then next few months we will present a mystery to the world. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this mystery and we will share how with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nRight now many of us are doing one specific thing over and over again, and more than likely you will do this one thing a few times as you read this. We want to take that one action and turn it into a way for businesses, large and small, to reach you and everyone else in the world.\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side can work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-05-11 04:25:01','2014-05-11 04:25:01','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(338,1,'2014-05-11 04:34:41','2014-05-11 04:34:41','&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically increase user engagement with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus increasing our value to advertisers and therefore increasing our ability to contribute to organizations who do good.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to be the most charitable company in the world within the next 5 years.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are <strong>donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that set us apart. Over then next few months we will present a mystery to the world. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this problem and we will share <strong>how we solve it</strong> with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side can work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-05-11 04:34:41','2014-05-11 04:34:41','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(337,1,'2014-05-11 04:25:24','2014-05-11 04:25:24','&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically increase user engagement with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus increasing our value to advertisers and therefore increasing our ability to contribute to organizations who do good.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to be the most charitable company in the world within the next 5 years.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are <strong>donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that set us apart. Over then next few months we will present a mystery to the world. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this mystery and we will share how with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nRight now many of us are doing one specific thing over and over again, and more than likely you will do this one thing a few times as you read this. We want to take that one action and turn it into a way for businesses, large and small, to reach you and everyone else in the world.\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side can work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The app','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-05-11 04:25:24','2014-05-11 04:25:24','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(339,1,'2014-05-11 04:37:13','2014-05-11 04:37:13','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 180px;\">So many people would love to do more but...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So don\'t we do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves all of these problems. First we are not asking for our users to spend any more time than they already do. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. And Third - we make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-96\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Crowd.jpg\" alt=\"Crowd\" width=\"388\" height=\"255\" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For those who would like to donate from their own pockets we hope to help this process be easier. Our app will make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good we could do with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But even once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a moving hashtag spreading via twitter or a viral video, we know that there are a few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of <a title=\"Team\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/team/\">our team</a>, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-05-11 04:37:13','2014-05-11 04:37:13','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(340,1,'2014-05-11 05:02:03','2014-05-11 05:02:03','','CrowdCellLights','','inherit','open','open','','crowdcelllights','','','2014-05-11 05:02:03','2014-05-11 05:02:03','',62,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(344,1,'2014-05-11 05:03:58','2014-05-11 05:03:58','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text