ividuals wish to recommend a charity and pledge to support that charity through installing the Adora Charity App,  they may submit those <a title=\"Nominate and pledge support for your charity\" href=\"http://goo.gl/60LSzX\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.','Philanthropy in Vogue - Charitable Giving Approaches Pre Recession Levels','','inherit','open','open','','484-revision-v1','','','2014-09-09 22:04:14','2014-09-09 22:04:14','',484,'http://getadora.com/484-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(498,1,'2014-09-20 00:11:13','2014-09-20 00:11:13','','PhonesOnTheMount','','inherit','open','open','','phonesonthemount','','','2014-09-20 00:11:13','2014-09-20 00:11:13','',0,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/PhonesOnTheMount.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(503,1,'2014-09-21 05:22:36','2014-09-21 05:22:36','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Doing good all by yourself can be rewarding, but doing good makes an even greater impact when we get everyone involved.\r\nThe more you share the more good we all can do</p>','Share Adora with your friends','','publish','closed','closed','','share-adora-friends','','','2014-09-23 02:27:22','2014-09-23 02:27:22','',0,'http://getadora.com/?post_type=slide&#038;p=503',0,'slide','',0),(653,1,'2014-10-05 01:43:11','2014-10-05 01:43:11','','MoreThanAds','','inherit','open','open','','morethanads','','','2014-10-05 01:43:11','2014-10-05 01:43:11','',0,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/MoreThanAds.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(504,1,'2014-09-21 05:23:31','2014-09-21 05:23:31','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We not only help you fund causes but we help causes reach you.\r\nSo you’ll know when and where you and your friends can help.</p>','Doing More for Causes','','publish','closed','closed','','causes','','','2014-10-03 18:43:10','2014-10-03 18:43:10','',0,'http://getadora.com/?post_type=slide&#038;p=504',0,'slide','',0),(505,1,'2014-09-21 05:24:32','2014-09-21 05:24:32','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">No one wants to see ads all the time.\r\nAdora delivers deals, offers, recommendations from friends, breaking news, alerts, and more...</p>','More than Just Ads','','publish','closed','closed','','just-ads','','','2014-10-05 02:00:36','2014-10-05 02:00:36','',0,'http://getadora.com/?post_type=slide&#038;p=505',0,'slide','',0),(506,1,'2014-09-21 05:27:04','2014-09-21 05:27:04','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">You get to tell Adora the kinds of content you like in your profile and by interacting with the content that is delivered to your lock screen.  When you interact positively with content you will see more offers like that and if there is content that doesn\'t interest you, you will see less of those kinds of offers going forward.  The longer you use the app, the more personalized the experience.<strong>\r\n</strong></p>','Personalized','','pending','closed','closed','','learning-2','','','2014-12-02 21:22:59','2014-12-02 21:22:59','',0,'http://getadora.com/?post_type=slide&#038;p=506',0,'slide','',0),(507,1,'2014-09-21 05:29:17','2014-09-21 05:29:17','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Unlike everyone else online, you get to take some of the ad revenue you generate and give it to a cause you support.\r\nWith Adora this is not where your choices end…</p>','Choice','','publish','closed','closed','','choice','','','2014-10-05 01:59:36','2014-10-05 01:59:36','',0,'http://getadora.com/?post_type=slide&#038;p=507',0,'slide','',0),(508,1,'2014-09-21 05:29:49','2014-09-21 05:29:49','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Through Adora,\r\nEvery time you look at your phone you are doing good, helping a cause, possibly saving lives</p>','Not Just Another App','','publish','closed','closed','','just-another-app','','','2014-09-21 23:22:10','2014-09-21 23:22:10','',0,'http://getadora.com/?post_type=slide&#038;p=508',0,'slide','',0),(519,1,'2014-09-23 02:27:15','2014-09-23 02:27:15','','Share','','inherit','open','open','','share','','','2014-09-23 02:27:15','2014-09-23 02:27:15','',503,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Share.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(638,1,'2014-10-05 00:49:47','2014-10-05 00:49:47','','Learning','','inherit','open','open','','learning-3','','','2014-10-05 00:49:47','2014-10-05 00:49:47','',506,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Learning.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(652,1,'2014-10-05 01:42:54','2014-10-05 01:42:54','','Choice','','inherit','open','open','','choice-2','','','2014-10-05 01:43:57','2014-10-05 01:43:57','',62,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(512,1,'2014-09-21 23:24:07','2014-09-21 23:24:07','','DonateNow','','inherit','open','open','','donatenow','','','2014-09-21 23:24:07','2014-09-21 23:24:07','',504,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/DonateNow.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(513,1,'2014-09-22 01:30:56','2014-09-22 01:30:56','','Chalkboard','','inherit','open','open','','chalkboard','','','2014-09-22 01:30:56','2014-09-22 01:30:56','',1,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Chalkboard.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(514,1,'2014-09-22 21:57:35','2014-09-22 21:57:35','','OnePageWebsitebanner','','inherit','open','open','','onepagewebsitebanner','','','2014-09-22 21:57:35','2014-09-22 21:57:35','',1,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/OnePageWebsitebanner.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(540,1,'2014-10-01 17:41:26','2014-10-01 17:41:26','','OnePageWebsiteLogo','','inherit','open','open','','onepagewebsitelogo','','','2014-10-01 17:41:26','2014-10-01 17:41:26','',1,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/OnePageWebsiteLogo.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(516,1,'2014-09-22 22:06:40','2014-09-22 22:06:40','','OnePageWebsitebanner','','inherit','open','open','','onepagewebsitebanner-2','','','2014-09-22 22:06:40','2014-09-22 22:06:40','',1,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/OnePageWebsitebanner1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(518,1,'2014-09-22 22:22:54','2014-09-22 22:22:54','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 180px;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves all of these problems. First we are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. And Third - we make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"CrowdCellLights\" width=\"421\" height=\"258\" /></a>Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our app will also make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good we could do with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a hashtag trending on twitter or a viral video, we know that there are few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of <a title=\"Team\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/team/\">our team</a>, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-09-22 22:22:54','2014-09-22 22:22:54','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(517,1,'2014-09-22 22:20:24','2014-09-22 22:20:24','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 180px;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Add money to the mix and many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference.\r\n\r\nOur app solves all of these problems. First we are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app. Second our app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. And Third - we make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"CrowdCellLights\" width=\"426\" height=\"261\" /></a>Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our app will also make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good we could do with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a moving hashtag spreading via twitter or a viral video, we know that there are a few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of <a title=\"Team\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/team/\">our team</a>, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-09-22 22:20:24','2014-09-22 22:20:24','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(521,6,'2014-09-25 23:49:44','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','About Adora','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-09-25 23:49:44','2014-09-25 23:49:44','',0,'http://getadora.com/?page_id=521',0,'page','',0),(730,1,'2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://getadora.com/?p=730',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(729,1,'2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://getadora.com/?p=729',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(728,1,'2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://getadora.com/?p=728',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(727,1,'2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://getadora.com/?p=727',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(726,1,'2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://getadora.com/?p=726',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(725,1,'2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://getadora.com/?p=725',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(724,1,'2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Home','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-12-01 16:53:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://getadora.com/?p=724',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(532,6,'2014-10-03 03:14:57','2014-10-03 03:14:57','Doing good. That is what drives us. Every decision we make must be guided by the question - does it help us do more good?\n\nIf you represent the executive team or development team of a 501c3 nonprofit, <a title=\"Adora Charity Funding Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/charityprogram/\" target=\"_blank\">click here</a> to learn how Adora can help you do more good.','Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','185-autosave-v1','','','2014-10-03 03:14:57','2014-10-03 03:14:57','',185,'http://getadora.com/185-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(534,6,'2014-09-30 20:22:16','2014-09-30 20:22:16','','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-09-30 20:22:16','2014-09-30 20:22:16','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(533,6,'2014-11-21 01:28:24','2014-11-21 01:28:24','Adora exists to help you do more good.\n\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-208 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\" alt=\"Charity\" width=\"401\" height=\"244\" /></a>Through Adora we hope to help all of our charitable partners do more good through better exposure, more consistent funding, and increased volunteer involvement.\n\nHere is how it works:\n\nThe program is FREE, you will never pay for our services.\n\nThe Adora Charity Funding Program requires a very simple formal agreement, Adora doesn\'t even need your donor list to engage your supporters, we trust you to do that. When you become a Charity Partner you will be part of our <a title=\"Adora Affiliate Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\">Affiliate Program</a> but with some amazing advantages:\n<ul>\n	<li>Your users will bring you funding for as long as they use the app, no 12-6 month expiration.</li>\n	<li>You will receive free advertising on the network that grows with your Adora user base (Ask us about this)</li>\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\n	<li>Direct Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate to you via our app, and we will pay the transaction fees.</li>\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\n	<li>You may be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving (coming in 2016).</li>\n</ul>\nThe key to your funding and the scope of all of these benefits will be based on your effort in promoting your Charity on the Adora App.\n\n<strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-652 size-medium\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"Choice\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" /></a>Special Crowdfunding Opportunity</strong>\n\nOn November 25th, we will be lunching a crowdfunding campaign. In this campaign we will be giving 30-50% of our total raised to charities that help us promote the campaign. This campaign will focus on fighting holiday hunger and be a great way to acquire users of our app who will fund you monthly once the app begins delivering ads in mid December.  The more users that download our app from your partner link, the less that is spent on non-charity affiliate costs be cause those affiliate fees go to your charity. We\'ll tell you more once you are on board.\n\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be free for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This exposure will encourage others to go out and do more good.\n\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\n\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner.\n\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-autosave-v1','','','2014-11-21 01:28:24','2014-11-21 01:28:24','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(567,1,'2014-10-03 20:45:05','2014-10-03 20:45:05','Donations will be made Quarterly (all transaction costs will be paid out of the donation total)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Donations will be limited (Capped at $2.50 right now but that may go up in the future)</li>\r\n	<li>Users will need to specify your charity by name or with a code to donate though the app.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPartnership\r\n\r\nThis is the most productive relationship for everyone and in technical terms it is only an ongoing joint venture. By committing to work with us on the launch and continual promotion of the app we can have a closer relationship with you. General features of the joint venture:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Free advertising on the network (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You will be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This will encourage others to do more good.\r\n\r\nWe will be selecting a precious few to be in on our secret regarding how we will be delivering our ads. We want you to be able to tell others, including those you promote our app to, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 20:45:05','2014-10-03 20:45:05','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(538,6,'2014-09-30 22:25:59','2014-09-30 22:25:59','<strong>Adora Helps Charities Do More</strong>\r\n\r\nAt Adora we love the good our partner charities are doing, our goal is to help them to execute their charitable missions through providing access to additional funding and outreach to volunteers to the communities they serve.\r\n\r\n<strong>Philanthropy 2.0</strong>\r\n\r\nAdora was created as a way to allow everyone to become a philanthropist.  Through the Adora Charity App,  everyone can participate in charitable giving, even those with no money to give.   In this new paradigm of giving, all forms of support for a charitable cause are of worth and the cost of developing support from the lowest tier of the funding pyramid goes away.\r\n\r\n<strong>Adora Provides the Platform &amp; the Technology</strong>\r\n\r\nAdora creates a consistent and dependable revenue stream for charities to or replace other more costly streams.  Advertisers provide the money and Adora turns anyone with a mobile device who supports your cause into a donor.  The same social media, newsletter, mail, radio, and TV development efforts attract a new bottom tier to your funding pyramid with no extra costs or efforts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Good Works Beget More Good Works</strong>\r\n\r\nFor those who already donate and volunteer, Adora is an easy way to give more and evangelize for your cause with Adora\'s sharing features.   For the new donors that give only through the ad-view funding they generate it is the first step to engagement and involvement with your charity.  Doing good feels good - each individual will give up as much time and money as they are willing to trade to be a part of your mission and to experience the joy of doing good and helping others.  Adora lowers the bar for giving and opens the door to charity involvement and active volunteer participation.\r\n\r\n<strong>Moving Forward Together</strong>\r\n\r\nThe impact we can make together can change the face of charitable giving forever. This is no small promise or opportunity, nor is this a one time thing. Every day you can add users and grow your funding and volunteer engagement.  Your social supports can now all be donors and as they recruit others for your cause, they will expand that base to achieve the goals for funding and serving others.\r\n\r\n<strong>How it works</strong>\r\n\r\nThere are two different types of relationships a charity can have with our app: Basic or Partner.  We hope to have every charity as a Partner, but we canl still help those who want a more casual Basic Relationship\r\n\r\nBasic Relationship\r\n\r\nThis is the simple way to work with us. All you will need to do is indicate that you are interested in signup form and we will provide an affiliate code and link to share with your social followers and place on your direct donation page.\r\n\r\nFeatures of the basic relationship:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Quarterly (all transaction costs will be paid out of the donation total)</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be limited (Capped at $2.50 right now but that may go up in the future)</li>\r\n	<li>Users will need to specify your charity by name or with a code to donate though the app.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPartnership\r\n\r\nThis is the most productive relationship for everyone and in technical terms it is only an ongoing joint venture. By committing to work with us on the launch and continual promotion of the app we can have a closer relationship with you. General features of the joint venture:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Free advertising on the network (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You will be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This will encourage others to do more good.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe will be selecting a precious few to be in on our secret regarding how we will be delivering our ads. We want you to be able to tell others, including those you promote our app to, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-09-30 22:25:59','2014-09-30 22:25:59','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(539,1,'2014-09-30 22:49:02','2014-09-30 22:49:02','Doing good isn\'t easy. It isn\'t cheap. It takes time and resources. For businesses who want to support charities with their ad budgets Adora is here to give you this choice. When you advertise with Adora you form a charitable partnership with our users, to get started <a href=\"http://getadora.com/ads/\">click here</a>.','Adora Advertising','','inherit','open','open','','190-autosave-v1','','','2014-09-30 22:49:02','2014-09-30 22:49:02','',190,'http://getadora.com/190-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(541,1,'2014-10-04 17:55:32','2014-10-04 17:55:32','There are many ways to be a part of the Adora Partnership Team. If you are a blogger, a business owner (large or small), an artist or anyone with a following you might be perfect for our Adora Affiliate Program, and the extra income should help you out too. <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">To learn more contact us</a>.','Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','191-autosave-v1','','','2014-10-04 17:55:32','2014-10-04 17:55:32','',191,'http://getadora.com/191-autosave-v1/',0,'r