only an ongoing joint venture. By committing to work with us on the launch and continual promotion of the app we can have a closer relationship with you. General features of the joint venture:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Free advertising on the network (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You will be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This will encourage others to do more good.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe will be selecting a precious few to be in on our secret regarding how we will be delivering our ads. We want you to be able to tell others, including those you promote our app to, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-02 22:17:43','2014-10-02 22:17:43','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(688,1,'2014-10-10 22:33:40','2014-10-10 22:33:40','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Adora Mobile App on the Apple App Store\" href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/adora-charity/id930725815?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-707\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/AppStore.png\" alt=\"Adora Mobile App on the Apple App Store\" width=\"270\" height=\"80\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Adora Mobile App on the Google Play Store\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.adoracharity\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-708\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/PlayStore.png\" alt=\"Adora Mobile App on the Google Play Store\" width=\"270\" height=\"80\" /></a></p>','Download Adora','','publish','open','closed','','download','','','2014-10-21 15:06:33','2014-10-21 15:06:33','',0,'http://getadora.com/?page_id=688',6,'page','',0),(550,6,'2014-12-02 20:36:05','2014-12-02 20:36:05','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/AffiliateProgram.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-595 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/AffiliateProgram.jpg\" alt=\"AffiliateProgram\" width=\"470\" height=\"394\" /></a>Hi, welcome to our info page on the Adora Affiliate Program.\n\nWe want you to promote our app along with causes and charities that are important to you, to your customers, lists, blog readers, social networking followers, and anyone else or through any other avenue where you have a voice. In return for this you have two amazing rewards:\n\nYou\'ll feel great knowing you\'ve helped do more good through Adora and that is a great feeling, but...\nWe all know that an Affiliate Program needs to help you in return financially so...\n\nWe have one of, if not the best, affiliate programs available:\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">You get <em>up to*</em> <strong>$2.50 </strong>per user per month for up to 12 months--how long depends on how soon you become an affiliate.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Those who sign up before Dec 3rd will keep their reward bonuses for 12 months</li>\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Those who sign up on December 4th or later will keep their reward bonuses for 6 months</li>\n</ul>\nYour users will need to download the Adora App. It\'s free. And as long as they keep using the app, you can earn your reward bonuses. Our Affiliate Program is expected to change dramatically in 2015, but any affiliate who signs up before the December 17th deadline will be able to continue adding users through 2015.\n\n<em>*up to $2.50 means that how much you make per user depends on how often your customers use their phone.</em>\n\nOur app is coming out soon, but our advertising will not begin until <em>late October / early November</em>. We pay our affiliates after we get paid by the advertisers, so you can expect your first payment from Adora to come around the 15th of January 2015.\n\nTo get started fill out this form and we\'ll register you into our affiliate program.\n\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRW5XG6L3866\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','536-autosave-v1','','','2014-12-02 20:36:05','2014-12-02 20:36:05','',536,'http://getadora.com/536-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(551,6,'2014-10-02 22:44:51','2014-10-02 22:44:51','<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRW5XG6L3866\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','536-revision-v1','','','2014-10-02 22:44:51',