promote our app to, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 20:41:57','2014-10-03 20:41:57','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(554,6,'2014-10-03 00:14:04','2014-10-03 00:14:04','Adora Helps Charities Do More\r\n\r\nAt Adora we love the good our partner charities are doing, our goal is to help them to execute their charitable missions through providing access to additional funding and outreach to volunteers to the communities they serve.\r\n\r\nPhilanthropy 2.0\r\n\r\nAdora was created as a way to allow everyone to become a philanthropist.  Through the Adora Charity App,  everyone can participate in charitable giving, even those with no money to give.   In this new paradigm of giving, all forms of support for a charitable cause are of worth and the cost of developing support from the lowest tier of the funding pyramid goes away.\r\n\r\nAdora Provides the Platform &amp; the Technology\r\n\r\nAdora creates a consistent and dependable revenue stream for charities to or replace other more costly streams.  Advertisers provide the money and Adora turns anyone with a mobile device who supports your cause into a donor.  The same social media, newsletter, mail, radio, and TV development efforts attract a new bottom tier to your funding pyramid with no extra costs or efforts.\r\n\r\nGood Works Beget More Good Works\r\n\r\nFor those who already donate and volunteer, Adora is an easy way to give more and evangelize for your cause with Adora\'s sharing features.   For the new donors that give only through the ad-view funding they generate it is the first step to engagement and involvement with your charity.  Doing good feels good - each individual will give up as much time and money as they are willing to trade to be a part of your mission and to experience the joy of doing good and helping others.  Adora lowers the bar for giving and opens the door to charity involvement and active volunteer participation.\r\n\r\nMoving Forward Together\r\n\r\nThe impact we can make together can change the face of charitable giving forever. This is no small promise or opportunity, nor is this a one time thing. Every day you can add users and grow your funding and volunteer engagement.  Your social supports can now all be donors and as they recruit others for your cause, they will expand that base to achieve the goals for funding and serving others.\r\n\r\nHow it works\r\n\r\nThere are two different types of relationships a charity can have with our app: Basic or Partner.  We hope to have every charity as a Partner, but we canl still help those who want a more casual Basic Relationship\r\n\r\nBasic Relationship\r\n\r\nThis is the simple way to work with us. All you will need to do is indicate that you are interested in signup form and we will provide an affiliate code and link to share with your social followers and place on your direct donation page.\r\n\r\nFeatures of the basic relationship:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Quarterly (all transaction costs will be paid out of the donation total)</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be limited (Capped at $2.50 right now but that may go up in the future)</li>\r\n	<li>Users will need to specify your charity by name or with a code to donate though the app.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPartnership\r\n\r\nThis is the most productive relationship for everyone and in technical terms it is only an ongoing joint venture. By committing to work with us on the launch and continual promotion of the app we can have a closer relationship with you. General features of the joint venture:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Free advertising on the network (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You will be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This will encourage others to do more good.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe will be selecting a precious few to be in on our secret regarding how we will be delivering our ads. We want you to be able to tell others, including those you promote our app to, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 00:14:04','2014-10-03 00:14:04','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(555,1,'2015-02-11 22:34:01','2015-02-11 22:34:01','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/AffiliateProgram.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-595 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/AffiliateProgram.jpg\" alt=\"AffiliateProgram\" width=\"470\" height=\"394\" /></a>Hi, welcome to our info page on the Adora Affiliate Program.\n\nWe want you to promote our app along with causes and charities that are important to you, to your customers, lists, blog readers, social networking followers, and anyone else or through any other avenue where you have a voice. In return for this you have two amazing rewards:\n\nYou\'ll feel great knowing you\'ve helped do more good through Adora and that is a great feeling, but...\nWe all know that an Affiliate Program needs to help you in return financially so...\n\nWe have one of, if not the best, affiliate programs available: Depending on your reach and how you come to us you can get <em>up to*</em> <strong>$2.00 </strong>per user per month for up to 6 months--how long depends on how soon you become an affiliate.\n\nYour users will need to download the Adora App. It\'s free. And as long as they keep using the app, you can earn your reward bonuses. Our Affiliate Program is expected to change dramatically as we go through 2015, so partner with us now.\n\n<em>*up to $2.00 means that the amount made per user depends on how often your referrals (the people you get to download the app) use their phone.</em>\n\nOur app is coming soon. We will begin advertising through the notifications system paired with full-page, in-app ads. We pay our affiliates after we get paid by the advertisers.\n\nTo get started fill out this form and we\'ll register you into our affiliate program.\n\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRW5XG6L3866\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','536-autosave-v1','','','2015-02-11 22:34:01','2015-02-11 22:34:01','',536,'http://getadora.com/536-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(894,1,'2015-02-11 22:34:55','2015-02-11 22:34:55','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/AffiliateProgram.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-595 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/AffiliateProgram.jpg\" alt=\"AffiliateProgram\" width=\"470\" height=\"394\" /></a>Hi, welcome to our info page on the Adora Affiliate Program.\r\n\r\nWe want you to promote our app along with causes and charities that are important to you, to your customers, lists, blog readers, social networking followers, and anyone else or through any other avenue where you have a voice. In return for this you have two amazing rewards:\r\n\r\nYou\'ll feel great knowing you\'ve helped do more good through Adora and that is a great feeling, but...\r\nWe all know that an Affiliate Program needs to help you in return financially so...\r\n\r\nWe have one of, if not the best, affiliate programs available: Depending on your reach and how you come to us you can get <em>up to*</em> <strong>$2.00 </strong>per user per month for up to 6 months--how long depends on how soon you become an affiliate.\r\n\r\nYour users will need to download the Adora App. It\'s free. And as long as they keep using the app, you can earn your reward bonuses. Our Affiliate Program is expected to change dramatically as we go through 2015, so partner with us now.\r\n\r\n<em>*up to $2.00 means that the amount made per user depends on how often your referrals (the people you get to download the app) use their phone.</em>\r\n\r\nWe will begin advertising through the notifications system paired with full-page, in-app ads. We pay our affiliates after we get paid by the advertisers so while you get more from our program you don\'t get it right after the download, they have to keep the app on their phone for at least a month.\r\n\r\nTo get started fill out this form and we\'ll register you into our affiliate program.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRW5XG6L3866\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','536-revision-v1','','','2015-02-11 22:34:55','2015-02-11 22:34:55','',536,'http://getadora.com/536-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(556,1,'2014-10-03 02:12:00','2014-10-03 02:12:00','Hi, welcome to our info page on the Adora Affiliate Program.\r\n\r\nWe want you to promote our app to your customers, lists, blog readers, social networking followers, and anyone else or through any other avenue where you have a voice. In return for this you have two amazing rewards:\r\n\r\nYou\'ll feel great knowing that you\'ve helped do more good through Adora (that is a great feeling but...)\r\n\r\nIf you are one of the first 100 affiliates you will have\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRW5XG6L3866\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','536-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 02:12:00','2014-10-03 02:12:00','',536,'http://getadora.com/536-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(557,1,'2014-10-03 02:16:46','2014-10-03 02:16:46','Hi, welcome to our info page on the Adora Affiliate Program.\r\n\r\nWe want you to promote our app to your customers, lists, blog readers, social networking followers, and anyone else or through any other avenue where you have a voice. In return for this you have two amazing rewards:\r\n\r\nYou\'ll feel great knowing that you\'ve helped do more good through Adora and that is a great feeling but...\r\nWe all know that an Affiliate Program needs to help you out financially so...\r\n\r\nWe have one of, if not the best, affiliate programs around: you get <em>up to*</em> <strong>$2.50</strong>/user/month for up to 12 months.\r\n\r\nIf you are one of the first 100 affiliates you will get the full 12 months, if you are 101-200 you can get your residual income for 9 months, and any affiliates ofter that will get their residual income for 6 months.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRW5XG6L3866\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','536-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 02:16:46','2014-10-03 02:16:46','',536,'http://getadora.com/536-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES (558,1,'2014-10-03 02:38:24','2014-10-03 02:38:24','Hi, welcome to our info page on the Adora Affiliate Program.\r\n\r\nWe want you to promote our app to your customers, lists, blog readers, social networking followers, and anyone else or through any other avenue where you have a voice. In return for this you have two amazing rewards:\r\n\r\nYou\'ll feel great knowing that you\'ve helped do more good through Adora and that is a great feeling but...\r\nWe all know that an Affiliate Program needs to help you out financially so...\r\n\r\nWe have one of, if not the best, affiliate programs around: you get <em>up to*</em> <strong>$2.50</strong>/user/month for up to 12 months.\r\n\r\nYour users will need to download the Adora App, it\'s free, and for every month they keep using the app you can earn your referral fee. If you are one of the first 100 affiliates you will get the full 12 months, if you are 101-200 you can get your residual income for 9 months, and any affiliates after that will get their residual income for 6 months.\r\n\r\n<em>*up to $2.50 means that how much you make per user depends on how often your customers user their phone.</em>\r\n\r\nOur app is coming out soon, but our advertising will not begin until late October. We pay our affiliates after we get paid by the advertisers, so you can expect your first payment from Adora to come around the 15th of December, just in to for the holidays.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRW5XG6L3866\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','536-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 02:38:24','2014-10-03 02:38:24','',536,'http://getadora.com/536-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(559,1,'2014-10-03 02:39:23','2014-10-03 02:39:23','Hi, welcome to our info page on the Adora Affiliate Program.\r\n\r\nWe want you to promote our app to your customers, lists, blog readers, social networking followers, and anyone else or through any other avenue where you have a voice. In return for this you have two amazing rewards:\r\n\r\nYou\'ll feel great knowing that you\'ve helped do more good through Adora and that is a great feeling but...\r\nWe all know that an Affiliate Program needs to help you out financially so...\r\n\r\nWe have one of, if not the best, affiliate programs around: you get <em>up to*</em> <strong>$2.50</strong>/user/month for up to 12 months.\r\n\r\nYour users will need to download the Adora App, it\'s free, and for every month they keep using the app you can earn your referral fee. If you are one of the first 100 affiliates you will get the full 12 months, if you are 101-200 you can get your residual income for 9 months, and any affiliates after that will get their residual income for 6 months.\r\n\r\n<em>*up to $2.50 means that how much you make per user depends on how often your customers user their phone.</em>\r\n\r\nOur app is coming out soon, but our advertising will not begin until late October. We pay our affiliates after we get paid by the advertisers, so you can expect your first payment from Adora to come around the 15th of December, just in to for the holidays.\r\n\r\nTo get started fill out this form and we\'ll get you into our affiliate program.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRW5XG6L3866\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','536-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 02:39:23','2014-10-03 02:39:23','',536,'http://getadora.com/536-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(560,6,'2014-10-08 02:48:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Adora Helps Charities Do More\r\n\r\nAt Adora we love the good our partner charities are doing. Our goal is to help them execute their charitable missions through providing access to additional funding and outreach to volunteers in the communities they serve.\r\n\r\nPhilanthropy 2.0\r\n\r\nAdora was created as a way to allow everyone to become a philanthropist.  Through the Adora Charity App,  everyone can participate in charitable giving, even those with no money to give. In this new paradigm of giving, all forms of support for a charitable cause are of worth and the cost of developing support from the lowest tier of the funding pyramid goes away.\r\n\r\nAdora Provides the Platform &amp; Technology\r\n\r\nAdora creates a consistent and dependable revenue stream for charities to augment the current streams or replace other more costly streams.  Advertisers provide the money and Adora turns anyone with a mobile device who supports your cause into a donor. The same social media, newsletter, mail, radio, and TV development efforts attract a new bottom tier to your funding pyramid with no extra costs or efforts.\r\n\r\nGood Works Beget More Good Works\r\n\r\nFor those who already donate and volunteer, Adora is an easy way to give more and evangelize for your cause with Adora\'s sharing features. For the new donors that give only through the ad-view funding they generate, it is the first step to engagement and involvement with your charity.  Doing good feels good - each individual will give up as much time and money as they are willing to invest to be a part of your mission and to experience the joy of doing good and helping others.  Adora lowers the bar for giving and opens the door to charity involvement and active volunteer participation.\r\n\r\nMoving Forward Together\r\n\r\nThe impact we can make together can change the face of charitable giving forever. This is no small promise or opportunity, nor is this a one time event. Every day you can add users and grow your funding and volunteer engagement.  Your social support network can now all be donors and as they recruit others for your cause, they will expand that base to achieve the goals for funding and serving others.\r\n\r\nHow it works\r\n\r\nThe Adora Charity Funding Program requires a very simple formal agreement. Adora doesn\'t even need your donor list to engage your supporters.  As far as funding programs go, it is more of a fundraising tool than a formal program.  We like to think of it as a partnership where Adora takes all the economic risks, bears all the overhead, pays all the transaction costs, generates the revenue and leaves our partner charities free to focus on their organizational missions.\r\n\r\nAll a charity needs to do is to indicate an interest in participating by completing the <a title=\"Adora Charity Funding Program Sign-up\" href=\"http://getadora.com/charityprogram\">sign-up form</a>.  Adora will provide an affiliate code and link to share with social media followers and place on the charities direct donation page or other media that reaches their supporters.  Charities benefit proportionally to the degree with which they promote participation.\r\n\r\nCharities Gives Much More Than Just Funding\r\n\r\nThe funds generated by supporters through their ad view revenue and direct donation is only part 1 of a package intended to change the world, one charity and one mobile user at a time.  With exposure and through the time and resources of Adora  k with us on the launch and continual promotion of the app we can have a closer relationship with you. General features of the joint venture:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Free advertising on the network (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You will be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up to and through the holiday season. During this period we will visit some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds donated through Adora. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as for Adora’s use. This will encourage others to do more good.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe will choose a select few to be in on our secret regarding how we will be delivering our ads. We want you to be able to tell others, including those you promote our app to, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner','Adora Helps Charities Do More Good','','draft','open','open','','adora-helps-charities-good','','','2014-10-08 02:48:40','2014-10-08 02:48:40','',0,'http://getadora.com/?page_id=560',0,'page','',0),(561,6,'2014-10-03 03:18:17','2014-10-03 03:18:17','Adora Helps Charities Do More\r\n\r\nAt Adora we love the good our partner charities are doing, our goal is to help them to execute their charitable missions through providing access to additional funding and outreach to volunteers to the communities they serve.\r\n\r\nPhilanthropy 2.0\r\n\r\nAdora was created as a way to allow everyone to become a philanthropist.  Through the Adora Charity App,  everyone can participate in charitable giving, even those with no money to give.   In this new paradigm of giving, all forms of support for a charitable cause are of worth and the cost of developing support from the lowest tier of the funding pyramid goes away.\r\n\r\nAdora Provides the Platform &amp; the Technology\r\n\r\nAdora creates a consistent and dependable revenue stream for charities to or replace other more costly streams.  Advertisers provide the money and Adora turns anyone with a mobile device who supports your cause into a donor.  The same social media, newsletter, mail, radio, and TV development efforts attract a new bottom tier to your funding pyramid with no extra costs or efforts.\r\n\r\nGood Works Beget More Good Works\r\n\r\nFor those who already donate and volunteer, Adora is an easy way to give more and evangelize for your cause with Adora\'s sharing features.   For the new donors that give only through the ad-view funding they generate it is the first step to engagement and involvement with your charity.  Doing good feels good - each individual will give up as much time and money as they are willing to trade to be a part of your mission and to experience the joy of doing good and helping others.  Adora lowers the bar for giving and opens the door to charity involvement and active volunteer participation.\r\n\r\nMoving Forward Together\r\n\r\nThe impact we can make together can change the face of charitable giving forever. This is no small promise or opportunity, nor is this a one time thing. Every day you can add users and grow your funding and volunteer engagement.  Your social supports can now all be donors and as they recruit others for your cause, they will expand that base to achieve the goals for funding and serving others.\r\n\r\nHow it works\r\n\r\nThere are two different types of relationships a charity can have with our app: Basic or Partner.  We hope to have every charity as a Partner, but we canl still help those who want a more casual Basic Relationship\r\n\r\nBasic Relationship\r\n\r\nThis is the simple way to work with us. All you will need to do is indicate that you are interested in signup form and we will provide an affiliate code and link to share with your social followers and place on your direct donation page.\r\n\r\nFeatures of the basic relationship:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Quarterly (all transaction costs will be paid out of the donation total)</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be limited (Capped at $2.50 right now but that may go up in the future)</li>\r\n	<li>Users will need to specify your charity by name or with a code to donate though the app.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPartnership\r\n\r\nThis is the most productive relationship for everyone and in technical terms it is only an ongoing joint venture. By committing to work with us on the launch and continual promotion of the app we can have a closer relationship with you. General features of the joint venture:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Free advertising on the network (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You will be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This will encourage others to do more good.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe will be selecting a precious few to be in on our secret regarding how we will be delivering our ads. We want you to be able to tell others, including those you promote our app to, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner','','','inherit','open','open','','560-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 03:18:17','2014-10-03 03:18:17','',560,'http://getadora.com/560-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(563,6,'2014-10-03 03:33:02','2014-10-03 03:33:02','<strong>Adora Helps Charities Do More</strong>\r\n\r\nAt Adora we love the good our partner charities are doing, our goal is to help them to execute their charitable missions through providing access to additional funding and outreach to volunteers to the communities they serve.\r\n\r\n<strong>Philanthropy 2.0</strong>\r\n\r\nAdora was created as a way to allow everyone to become a philanthropist.  Through the Adora Charity App,  everyone can participate in charitable giving, even those with no money to give.   In this new paradigm of giving, all forms of support for a charitable cause are of worth and the cost of developing support from the lowest tier of the funding pyramid goes away.\r\n\r\n<strong>Adora Provides the Platform &amp; Technology</strong>\r\n\r\nAdora creates a consistent and dependable revenue stream for charities to or replace other more costly streams.  Advertisers provide the money and Adora turns anyone with a mobile device who supports your cause into a donor.  The same social media, newsletter, mail, radio, and TV development efforts attract a new bottom tier to your funding pyramid with no extra costs or efforts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Good Works Beget More Good Works</strong>\r\n\r\nFor those who already donate and volunteer, Adora is an easy way to give more and evangelize for your cause with Adora\'s sharing features.   For the new donors that give only through the ad-view funding they generate it is the first step to engagement and involvement with your charity.  Doing good feels good - each individual will give up as much time and money as they are willing to trade to be a part of your mission and to experience the joy of doing good and helping others.  Adora lowers the bar for giving and opens the door to charity involvement and active volunteer participation.\r\n\r\n<strong>Moving Forward Together</strong>\r\n\r\nThe impact we can make together can change the face of charitable giving forever. This is no small promise or opportunity, nor is this a one time thing. Every day you can add users and grow your funding and volunteer engagement.  Your social supports can now all be donors and as they recruit others for your cause, they will expand that base to achieve the goals for funding and serving others.\r\n\r\n<strong>How it works</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Adora Charity Funding Program requires no formal contract, or legal relationship.  Adora doesn\'t even need your donor list to engage your supporters.  As far a funding programs go, it is more or a fundraising tool than a formal program.  We like to think of it as a partnership where Adora takes all the economic risks, bares all the overhead, pays all the transaction costs, generates the revenue and leaves our partner charities free to focus on their organizational missions.\r\n\r\nThis is the simple way to work with us. All you will need to do is indicate that you are interested in signup form and we will provide an affiliate code and link to share with your social followers and place on your direct donation page.\r\n\r\nFeatures of the basic relationship:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Quarterly (all transaction costs will be paid out of the donation total)</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be limited (Capped at $2.50 right now but that may go up in the future)</li>\r\n	<li>Users will need to specify your charity by name or with a code to donate though the app.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPartnership\r\n\r\nThis is the most productive relationship for everyone and in technical terms it is only an ongoing joint venture. By committing to work with us on the launch and continual promotion of the app we can have a closer relationship with you. General features of the joint venture:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Free advertising on the network (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You will be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This will encourage others to do more good.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe will be selecting a precious few to be in on our secret regarding how we will be delivering our ads. We want you to be able to tell others, including those you promote our app to, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner','Adora Helps Charities Do More Good','','inherit','open','open','','560-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 03:33:02','2014-10-03 03:33:02','',560,'http://getadora.com/560-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(562,6,'2014-10-03 03:19:44','2014-10-03 03:19:44','Adora Helps Charities Do More\r\n\r\nAt Adora we love the good our partner charities are doing, our goal is to help them to execute their charitable missions through providing access to additional funding and outreach to volunteers to the communities they serve.\r\n\r\nPhilanthropy 2.0\r\n\r\nAdora was created as a way to allow everyone to become a philanthropist.  Through the Adora Charity App,  everyone can participate in charitable giving, even those with no money to give.   In this new paradigm of giving, all forms of support for a charitable cause are of worth and the cost of developing support from the lowest tier of the funding pyramid goes away.\r\n\r\nAdora Provides the Platform &amp; the Technology\r\n\r\nAdora creates a consistent and dependable revenue stream for charities to or replace other more costly streams.  Advertisers provide the money and Adora turns anyone with a mobile device who supports your cause into a donor.  The same social media, newslett