o, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 20:49:17','2014-10-03 20:49:17','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(572,1,'2014-10-03 20:52:00','2014-10-03 20:52:00','Adora exists to help you do more good.\r\n\r\nThrough Adora we hope to help all of our charitable partners do more good through better exposure, more consistent funding, and increased volunteer involvement.\r\n\r\nHere is how it works:\r\n\r\nDonations will be made Quarterly (all transaction costs will be paid out of the donation total)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Donations will be limited (Capped at $2.50 right now but that may go up in the future)</li>\r\n	<li>Users will need to specify your charity by name or with a code to donate though the app.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPartnership\r\n\r\nThis is the most productive relationship for everyone and in technical terms it is only an ongoing joint venture. By committing to work with us on the launch and continual promotion of the app we can have a closer relationship with you. General features of the joint venture:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Free advertising on the network (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You will be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This will encourage others to do more good.\r\n\r\nWe will be selecting a precious few to be in on our secret regarding how we will be delivering our ads. We want you to be able to tell others, including those you promote our app to, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 20:52:00','2014-10-03 20:52:00','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(571,1,'2014-10-03 20:51:07','2014-10-03 20:51:07','Adora exists to help you do more good.\r\n\r\nOur charitable partners are the key to our success and words cannot express how excited we are to partner with o