n.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 21:25:24','2014-10-03 21:25:24','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(584,1,'2014-10-03 21:26:30','2014-10-03 21:26:30','Adora exists to help you do more good.\r\n\r\nThrough Adora we hope to help all of our charitable partners do more good through better exposure, more consistent funding, and increased volunteer involvement.\r\n\r\nHere is how it works:\r\n\r\nThe Adora Charity Funding Program requires a very simple formal agreement, Adora doesn\'t even need your donor list to engage your supporters, we trust you to do that. When you become a Charity Partner you will be part of our <a title=\"Adora Affiliate Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\">Affiliate Program</a> but with some amazing advantages.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Your users will bring you funding for as long as they use the app, no 12-6 month expiration.</li>\r\n	<li>You will receive free advertising on the network that grows with your Adora user base (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You may be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving (coming in 2016).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe key to your funding and the scope of all of these benefits will be based on your effort in promoting your Charity on the Adora App.\r\n\r\n<strong>Special Crowdfunding Opportunity</strong>\r\n\r\nHere in October, in the next few weeks, we will be lunching a crowdfuning campaign. In this campaign we will be giving 30-50% of our total raised to charities that help us promote the campaign. We\'ll tell you more once you are on board.\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This exposure will encourage others to go out and do more good.\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner\r\n\r\n<i>*Note: This offer is subject to change at any time, and may no longer be available after October 23rd.</i>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 21:26:30','2014-10-03 21:26:30','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(586,1,'2014-10-03 21:29:35','2014-10-03 21:29:35','Hi, welcome to our info page on the Adora Affiliate Program.\r\n\r\nWe want you to promote our app to your customers, lists, blog readers, social networking followers, and anyone else or through any other avenue where you have a voice. In return for this you have two amazing rewards:\r\n\r\nYou\'ll feel great knowing that you\'ve helped do more good through Ador