ages:\r\n\r\nSmall Biz Pack -        10,000 impressions\r\nMedium Biz Pack -   100,000 impressions\r\n\r\n<strong>Fill out the interest form below and we\'ll contact you to start the process.</strong>\r\n\r\nEXTRA: Starting in November we are going to be Featuring a new business every week, and those businesses will get unlimited* advertising through the end of the year.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWL6X2G4C68\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Advertising','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 23:01:58','2014-10-03 23:01:58','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(594,1,'2014-10-03 23:04:32','2014-10-03 23:04:32','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-591  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a> <a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-592  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a>Adora Advertising is different for one HUGE reason... When anyone looks at our ads they KNOW that they are doing good.\r\n\r\nWith ever other ad platform - Facebook, Google, Twitter, Yahoo, you name it - people are turned off by advertising, they don\'t want it, they didn\'t say yes to the ads even if they said yes to the product.\r\n\r\nRight now we are looking to populate our app with ads. Most large brands and ad agencies need us to have a large user base before they will even consider advertising with us, so like many organizations we have the \"Chicken or the egg\" dilemma.\r\n\r\nThis is where you get the deal...! We are offering small and medium sized B2C startups/businesses the opportunity to secure some great advertising at a great price.\r\n\r\nRight now, <em>for a limited time,</em> you can test our platform out for <strong>FREE</strong>. We are giving away two different ad packages:\r\n\r\nSmall Biz Pack -        10,000 impressions\r\nMedium Biz Pack -   100,000 impressions\r\n\r\n<strong>Fill out the interest form below and we\'ll contact you to start the process.</strong>\r\n\r\nEXTRA: Starting in November we are going to be Featuring a new business every week, and those businesses will get unlimited* advertising through the end of the year.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWL6X2G4C68\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Advertising','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-10-03 23:04:32','2014-10-03 23:04:32','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(595,1,'2014-10-04 04:46:26','2014-10-04 04:46:26','','AffiliateProgram','','inherit','open','open','','affiliateprogram','','','2014-10-04 04:46:26','2014-10-04 04:46:26','',536,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/AffiliateProgram.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(596,1,'2014-10-04 04:46:44','2014-10-04 04:46:44','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/AffiliateProgram.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-595 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/AffiliateProgram.jpg\" alt=\"AffiliateProgram\" width=\"470\" height=\"394\" /></a>Hi, welcome to our info page on the Adora Affiliate Program.\r\n\r\nWe want you to promote our app to your customers, lists, blog readers, social networking followers, and anyone else or through any other avenue where you have a voice. In return for this you have two amazing rewards:\r\n\r\nYou\'ll feel great knowing that you\'ve helped do more good through Adora and that is a great feeling but...\r\nWe all know that an Affiliate Program needs to help you out financially so...\r\n\r\nWe have one of, if not the best, affiliate programs around:\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">You get <em>up to*</em> <strong>$2.50</strong>/user/month for up to 12 months - how long depends on how soon you become an affiliate.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Those who sign up before October 23rd will keep their revenue for 12 months</li>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Those who sign up before November 19th will keep their revenue for 9 months</li>\r\n	<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Those who sign up before December 17th will keep their revenue for 6 months</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYour users will need to download the Adora App, it\'s free, and as long as they keep using the app you can earn your referral fee. Our Affiliate Program is expected to change dramatically in 2015, but any affiliate who signs up before the December 17th deadline will be able to continue adding users through 2015.\r\n\r\n<em>*up to $2.50 means that how much you make per user depends on how often your customers user their phone.</em>\r\n\r\nOur app is coming out soon, but our advertising will not begin until <em>late October / early November</em>. We pay our affiliates after we get paid by the advertisers, so you can expect your first payment from Adora to come around the 15th of December, just in to for the holidays.\r\n\r\nTo get started fill out this form and we\'ll get you into our affiliate program.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRW5XG6L3866\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Affiliate Program','','inherit','open','open','','536-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 04:46:44','2014-10-04 04:46:44','',536,'http://getadora.com/536-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(598,1,'2014-10-04 17:07:34','2014-10-04 17:07:34','Adora exists to help you do more good.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-208 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\" alt=\"Charity\" width=\"401\" height=\"244\" /></a>Through Adora we hope to help all of our charitable partners do more good through better exposure, more consistent funding, and increased volunteer involvement.\r\n\r\nHere is how it works:\r\n\r\nThe Adora Charity Funding Program requires a very simple formal agreement, Adora doesn\'t even need your donor list to engage your supporters, we trust you to do that. When you become a Charity Partner you will be part of our <a title=\"Adora Affiliate Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\">Affiliate Program</a> but with some amazing advantages.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Your users will bring you funding for as long as they use the app, no 12-6 month expiration.</li>\r\n	<li>You will receive free advertising on the network that grows with your Adora user base (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You may be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving (coming in 2016).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe key to your funding and the scope of all of these benefits will be based on your effort in promoting your Charity on the Adora App.\r\n\r\n<strong>Special Crowdfunding Opportunity</strong>\r\n\r\nHere in October, in the next few weeks, we will be lunching a crowdfuning campaign. In this campaign we will be giving 30-50% of our total raised to charities that help us promote the campaign. We\'ll tell you more once you are on board.\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This exposure will encourage others to go out and do more good.\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner\r\n\r\n<i>*Note: This offer is subject to change at any time, and may no longer be available after October 23rd.</i>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 17:07:34','2014-10-04 17:07:34','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(599,1,'2014-10-04 17:46:35','2014-10-04 17:46:35','Adora exists to help you do more good.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-208 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\" alt=\"Charity\" width=\"401\" height=\"244\" /></a>Through Adora we hope to help all of our charitable partners do more good through better exposure, more consistent funding, and increased volunteer involvement.\r\n\r\nHere is how it works:\r\n\r\nThe Adora Charity Funding Program requires a very simple formal agreement, Adora doesn\'t even need your donor list to engage your supporters, we trust you to do that. When you become a Charity Partner you will be part of our <a title=\"Adora Affiliate Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\">Affiliate Program</a> but with some amazing advantages.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Your users will bring you funding for as long as they use the app, no 12-6 month expiration.</li>\r\n	<li>You will receive free advertising on the network that grows with your Adora user base (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You may be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving (coming in 2016).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe key to your funding and the scope of all of these benefits will be based on your effort in promoting your Charity on the Adora App.\r\n\r\n<strong><img class=\"wp-image-500 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Choice.jpg\" alt=\"Choice\" width=\"499\" height=\"281\" />Special Crowdfunding Opportunity</strong>\r\n\r\nHere in October, in the next few weeks, we will be lunching a crowdfuning campaign. In this campaign we will be giving 30-50% of our total raised to charities that help us promote the campaign. We\'ll tell you more once you are on board.\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This exposure will encourage others to go out and do more good.\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner\r\n\r\n<i>*Note: This offer is subject to change at any time, and may no longer be available after October 23rd.</i>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 17:46:35','2014-10-04 17:46:35','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(601,1,'2014-10-04 18:27:50','2014-10-04 18:27:50','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Our passion is to do as much good as we possibly can.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This is what drives our every move, what makes our hearts burn to work harder, longer, and smarter.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We then will use our example to start a movement, a change in not just corporate giving but in private giving too. We stand for the principle that even a dollar here or $5 there can make a difference--that you don\'t have to be wealthy to give and you don\'t have to give money to make an impact.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/RXMnDG3QzxE\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Read more <a title=\"Charity+\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">about Adora</a> or find out more <a title=\"The app\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/adora-app/\">about the Adora app</a></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>If you want to talk more info <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\">contact us</a>.</strong></p>','About','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 18:27:50','2014-10-04 18:27:50','',2,'http://getadora.com/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(605,1,'2014-10-04 18:45:17','2014-10-04 18:45:17','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we all actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference, that unless they spend hours or days volunteering anything less is not worth the small impact.\r\n\r\nWe are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app, they do not need to take any more time out of their busy days to do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. We make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"CrowdCellLights\" width=\"421\" height=\"258\" /></a>Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our app will also make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 10 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good that could be done with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a hashtag trending on twitter or a viral video, we know that there are few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of <a title=\"Team\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/team/\">our team</a>, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 18:45:17','2014-10-04 18:45:17','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(604,1,'2014-10-04 18:42:37','2014-10-04 18:42:37','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we all actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference, that unless they spend hours or days volunteering anything less is not worth the small impact.\r\n\r\nWe are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app, they do not need to take any more time out of their busy days to do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. We make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"CrowdCellLights\" width=\"421\" height=\"258\" /></a>Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our app will also make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good we could do with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a hashtag trending on twitter or a viral video, we know that there are few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of <a title=\"Team\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/team/\">our team</a>, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 18:42:37','2014-10-04 18:42:37','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(602,1,'2014-10-04 18:40:19','2014-10-04 18:40:19','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 60px;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 180px;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we all actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference, that unless they spend hours or days volunteering anything less is not worth the small impact.\r\n\r\nWe are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app, they do not need to take any more time out of their busy days to do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. We make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"CrowdCellLights\" width=\"421\" height=\"258\" /></a>Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our app will also make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 100 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good we could do with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a hashtag trending on twitter or a viral video, we know that there are few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of <a title=\"Team\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/team/\">our team</a>, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 18:40:19','2014-10-04 18:40:19','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(603,1,'2014-10-04 18:41:23','2014-10-04 18:41:23','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we all actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference, that unless they spend hours or days volunteering anything less is not worth the small impact.\r\n\r\nWe are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app, they do not need to take any more time out of their busy days to do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. We make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.c