_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of <a title=\"Team\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/team/\">our team</a>, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 18:41:23','2014-10-04 18:41:23','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(607,1,'2014-10-04 18:49:25','2014-10-04 18:49:25','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we all actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference, that unless they spend hours or days volunteering anything less is not worth the small impact.\r\n\r\nWe are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app, they do not need to take any more time out of their busy days to do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. We make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but t