pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of <a title=\"Team\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/team/\">our team</a>, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 18:49:25','2014-10-04 18:49:25','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(606,1,'2014-10-04 18:46:47','2014-10-04 18:46:47','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we all actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference, that unless they spend hours or days volunteering anything less is not worth the small impact.\r\n\r\nWe are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app, they do not need to take any more time out of their busy days to do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. We make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"CrowdCellLights\" width=\"421\" height=\"258\" /></a>Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our app will also make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 10 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good that could be done with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a hashtag trending on twitter or a viral video, we know that there are few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out and become part of <a title=\"Team\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/team/\">our team</a>, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 18:46:47','2014-10-04 18:46:47','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(608,1,'2014-10-04 18:58:49','2014-10-04 18:58:49','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we all actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference, that unless they spend hours or days volunteering anything less is not worth the small impact.\r\n\r\nWe are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app, they do not need to take any more time out of their busy days to do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. We make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our app will also make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 10 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"CrowdCellLights\" width=\"421\" height=\"258\" />Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good that could be done with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a hashtag trending on twitter, a viral video, or dumping ice on our heads, we know that there are few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://embed.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong.html\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<strong>If you want help out read more about how you can be more involved, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 18:58:49','2014-10-04 18:58:49','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(610,1,'2014-10-04 19:05:38','2014-10-04 19:05:38','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we all actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference, that unless they spend hours or days volunteering anything less is not worth the small impact.\r\n\r\nWe are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app, they do not need to take any more time out of their busy days to do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. We make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our app will also make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 10 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"CrowdCellLights\" width=\"421\" height=\"258\" />Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good that could be done with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a hashtag trending on twitter, a viral video, or dumping ice on our heads, we know that there are few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/bfAzi6D5FpM\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\r\n<strong>If you want help out read more about how you can be more involved, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong></p>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 19:05:38','2014-10-04 19:05:38','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(611,1,'2014-10-04 20:16:37','2014-10-04 20:16:37','No matter who you are you can do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur apps will be launching soon, and as an individual you can download the app and do good by installing it and sharing the app with your friends.  You may have a few hundred friends between your email contacts and social networks who would help you support the cause you feel most passionately about - <a title=\"The app\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/adora-app/\">Learn more about how our app works</a>.\r\n\r\nIf you are a charity you are already doing good and <strong>we thank you so much</strong> for being ready to do even more through Adora! <a title=\"Adora Charity Funding Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/charityprogram/\">Learn more about our Charity Program</a>.\r\n\r\nIf you are a business, blogger, artist, or anyone with a following you can promote Adora and <a title=\"Adora Affiliate Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/affiliate/\">take part in one of the best Affiliate Programs around</a>.\r\n\r\nIf you advertise, even if you have a small budget, who would you rather advertise with? Facebook, Google, Twitter, even TV &amp; Radio are great advertising outlets BUT what if you could get the same results AND do good with each ad dollar you spend. This is what you do when you advertise through Adora. <a tit