ora, and do as much good as you can.\n\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/GoodTogether.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-614\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/GoodTogether.jpg\" alt=\"GoodTogether\" width=\"884\" height=\"363\" /></a>','How You Can Help','','inherit','open','open','','611-autosave-v1','','','2014-10-04 20:21:10','2014-10-04 20:21:10','',611,'http://getadora.com/611-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(618,1,'2014-10-04 20:21:36','2014-10-04 20:21:36','No matter who you are you can do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur apps will be launching soon, and as an individual you can download the app and do good in that way. <a title=\"The app\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/adora-app/\">Learn more about how our app works</a>.\r\n\r\nIf you are a charity you are already doing good and <strong>we thank you so much</strong> for being ready to do even more through Adora! <a title=\"Adora Charity Funding Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/charityprogram/\">Learn more about or Charity Program</a>.\r\n\r\nIf you are a business, blogger, artist, or anyone with a following you can promote Adora and <a title=\"Adora Affiliate Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/affiliate/\">take part in one of the best Affiliate Programs around</a>.\r\n\r\nIf you advertise, even if you have a small budget, who would you rather advertise with? Facebook, Google, Twitter, even TV &amp; Radio are great advertising outlets BUT what if you could get the same results AND do good with each ad dollar you spend. This is what you do when you advertise through Adora. <a title=\"Adora Advertising\" href=\"http://getadora.com/ads/\">Learn more about how to start advertising with Adora</a>.\r\n\r\nWe want to give everyone a way to make an impact, we know that the only way we can really change the world, to really do good on a scale that makes noise, is to get everyone involved. Come join us here at Adora, and do as much good as you can.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/GoodTogether.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-614\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/GoodTogether.jpg\" alt=\"GoodTogether\" width=\"884\" height=\"363\" /></a>','How You Can Help','','inherit','open','open','','611-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 20:21:36','2014-10-04 20:21:36','',611,'http://getadora.com/611-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(619,1,'2014-10-04 20:26:03','2014-10-04 20:26:03','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are so many who need help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Many charities are trying to help.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">So many people would love to do more...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>So why don\'t we all actually do more?</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignright wp-image-252\" src=\"http://lscapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Charity1.jpg\" alt=\"CharityWordle1\" width=\"478\" height=\"291\" />Time &amp; Money</h2>\r\nThis is what stops most of us from doing more. We have enough trouble balancing our lives as it is. Many believe that unless their donation is large it doesn\'t make a difference, that unless they spend hours or days volunteering anything less is not worth the small impact.\r\n\r\nWe are not asking for our users to change their mobile device use, they don\'t even have to open our app, they do not need to take any more time out of their busy days to do good through Adora.\r\n\r\nOur app gives our users a choice they have never had before, to choose where their advertising earnings go. We make it clear that no donation is too small to make a difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">Our app is simple: the advertising pays for charity work but the users determine where the funds go.</span></strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our app will also make it easy to donate as little as $1 a month and make that seemingly insignificant sum hold the weight of our entire user base. $1 alone makes little difference but if 1 million or 10 million users all donate then those dollars add up!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"alignleft  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/CrowdCellLights-300x184.jpg\" alt=\"CrowdCellLights\" width=\"421\" height=\"258\" />Imagine if we could be as well supported as a game like Candy Crush and its 100 million users. That would see us donating over $100 million every month! That is possible and oh the good that could be done with that kind of donation every month.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Every effort we make is guided by the goal voiced in our vision: <strong>To become the most charitable company in the world</strong></p>\r\n But once we reach that lofty goal there is more to accomplish, we must change the way we look at charitable organizations.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Charity+ = The next evolution of charitable funding</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">We have seen the strength of the masses, be it a hashtag trending on twitter, a viral video, or dumping ice on our heads, we know that there are few better ways to move mountains. If real good is to be done it must be done by everyone and it must be seen as possible.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For this to be possible we must look at the business of charity work in a much different way. We resonate with Dan in his TED Talk below, better support for great leadership, management, marketing, and business principals is essential to success in the world of doing good. We cannot expect great performance without great support.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/bfAzi6D5FpM\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\r\n<strong>If you want help out read more about <a title=\"How You Can Help\" href=\"http://getadora.com/can-help/\">how you can be more involved</a>, or if you are just interested in learning more, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a></strong></p>','Charity+','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 20:26:03','2014-10-04 20:26:03','',62,'http://getadora.com/62-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(620,1,'2014-10-04 20:26:37','2014-10-04 20:26:37','&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically <strong>increase user engagement</strong> with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus <strong>increasing our value to advertisers &amp; brands</strong> and therefore<strong> increasing our ability to</strong> <strong>contribute to organizations who do good</strong>.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to lead a change in corporate social activity by becoming the most charitable company in the world by 2020.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are <strong>donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that sets us apart. Over the next few months <strong>we will present this mystery to the world</strong>. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this problem and we will share <strong>how we solve it</strong> with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 20:26:37','2014-10-04 20:26:37','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(621,1,'2014-10-04 20:43:40','2014-10-04 20:43:40','<h2>Adora is an Advertising App</h2>\r\nAdvertising is how we fund everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry.\r\n\r\nAdora is <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on doing good with our advertising revenue, revenue created by our efforts in partnership with our users.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically <strong>increase user engagement</strong> with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus <strong>increasing our value to advertisers &amp; brands</strong> and therefore<strong> increasing our ability to</strong> <strong>contribute to organizations who do good</strong>.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to lead a change in corporate social activity by becoming the most charitable company in the world by 2020.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are <strong>donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that sets us apart. Over the next few months <strong>we will present this mystery to the world</strong>. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this problem and we will share <strong>how we solve it</strong> with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 20:43:40','2014-10-04 20:43:40','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(622,1,'2014-10-04 20:52:59','2014-10-04 20:52:59','<h2>Adora is an Advertising App</h2>\r\nAdvertising is how we fund everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry.\r\n\r\nThere is a very important difference between all of these other advertising methods. Adora is <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on <strong>doing good</strong> with our advertising revenue, revenue created by our efforts in partnership with our users.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" /></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically <strong>increase user engagement</strong> with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus <strong>increasing our value to advertisers &amp; brands</strong> and therefore<strong> increasing our ability to</strong> <strong>contribute to organizations who do good</strong>.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to lead a change in corporate social activity by becoming the most charitable company in the world by 2020.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are <strong>donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that sets us apart. Over the next few months <strong>we will present this mystery to the world</strong>. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this problem and we will share <strong>how we solve it</strong> with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 20:52:59','2014-10-04 20:52:59','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(624,1,'2014-10-04 21:46:33','2014-10-04 21:46:33','<h2>Adora is an Advertising App</h2>\r\n<img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" />Advertising is how we fund everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of digital marketing companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, as well as more traditional industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry yet what impact are these platforms making?\r\n\r\nThere is a very important difference between all of these other advertising methods and Adora. We are <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on <strong>doing good</strong> with our advertising revenue, revenue created by our efforts in partnership with our users.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>How the Adora App works</h2>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-591 alignleft\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"246\" height=\"515\" />Traditional advertising, even newer methods like Facebook and Google ads, are not working anymore. Raise your hand if you ignore most every ad around you... You have your hand up don\'t you?\r\n\r\nWe have found an easy way to advertise, a way that is not intrusive, easy to ignore &amp; interact with all at the same time.\r\n\r\nHow you might ask? Well take a look at an example of our ad to the left, yes we know that hulk wouldn\'t really need a band-aid but it is a cool ad. It is a beautiful, full screen ad. It is easy to smile at and simply move on OR it is just as easy to give it a thumbs up and go view the ad.\r\n\r\nIf you\'ve ever used Pandora for music you know how the thumbs up / thumbs down interaction works. You get to let us know when you like an ad or when you don\'t.\r\n\r\nIf an ad is just not interesting simply ignore it and we\'ll get that message too.\r\n\r\nBUT what if you do like the ad but don\'t have time to check it out right now? Simply Save it for later (see the folders icon). You can have this option send you and email or it will just be waiting for you when you open the Adora app.\r\n<h2><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h2>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically <strong>increase user engagement</strong> with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus <strong>increasing our value to advertisers &amp; brands</strong> and therefore<strong> increasing our ability to</strong> <strong>contribute to organizations who do good</strong>.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to lead a change in corporate social activity by becoming the most charitable company in the world by 2020.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are <strong>donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h2>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that sets us apart. Over the next few months <strong>we will present this mystery to the world</strong>. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this problem and we will share <strong>how we solve it</strong> with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-10-04 21:46:33','2014-10-04 21:46:33','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(669,6,'2014-10-05 04:24:13','2014-10-05 04:24:13','<h3>Adora: A New Option</h3>\r\n<img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" />Advertising funds everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of digital marketing companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, as well as more traditional industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry yet what impact are these platforms making?\r\n\r\nThere is a very important difference between all of these other advertising methods and Adora. We are <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on <strong>doing good</strong> with our advertising revenue, revenue created by our efforts in partnership with you, our users.\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn more about our focus on Charity work, stop reading this page and <strong><a title=\"Charity+\" href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">PLEASE click here</a>.</strong>  Our message about what drives us is the most important thing we would have you read on our entire site.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>How the Adora App Works</h3>\r\nTraditional advertising, even newer methods like Facebook and Google ads, are not working anymore. Raise your hand if you ignore most every ad around you... You have your hand up don\'t you?\r\n\r\nWe have found an easy way to advertise, a way that is not intrusive, easy to ignore &amp; interact with all at the same time.\r\n\r\nHow you might ask? Through the lockscreen on your mobile device! Take a look at an example of our ad (to the right our just below), yes we know that hulk wouldn\'t really need a band-aid but it is a cool ad. It is a beautiful, full screen ad. It is easy to smile at and simply move on OR it is just as easy to give it a thumbs up and go view the ad.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-641 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LearningSmall.jpg\" alt=\"LearningSmall\" width=\"720\" height=\"400\" />If you\'ve ever used Pandora for music you know how the <strong>thumbs up / thumbs down</strong> interaction works. You get to let us know when you like an ad or when you don\'t.\r\n\r\nIf an ad is just not interesting <strong>simply ignore it, and unlock your device</strong> and we\'ll get that message too.\r\n\r\nBUT what if you <strong><em>do</em></strong> like the ad but don\'t have time to check it out right now? Simply <strong>Save it for later</strong> (see the folders icon) and unlock the device. You can have this option send you and email or it will just be waiting for you when you open the Adora app.\r\n\r\nWhether you are of aren\'t interested in an ad you may know someone else who might be interested, so we let you <strong>share an ad</strong> with an individual or with all your social media buddies.\r\n\r\nSoon you\'ll be able to do even more right from the lockscreen, you\'ll love what we have coming!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Adora is More Than Just Ads</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-654 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/MoreThanAdsSmall.jpg\" alt=\"MoreThanAdsSmall\" width=\"400\" height=\"193\" />Adora is still in Beta testing and we are going to be delivering more than just ads to your lockscreen.\r\n\r\nAs we go through testing we\'ll be finding out the best ratio of ads, offers, deals, news, or even personal images. How will we be determining the best ratios? Well that is up to you. How much good do you wan tot do, how many ads do you want to see vs news, personal images or other content? As you use the app you will tell us with every thumbs up or down.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Adora is easy but we want more from all of you...</h3>\r\nThe Adora app is free to download and use but we want more from everyone. We would love if you would donate out of pocket right now! Don\'t wait to start doing more good. We also want you to go out and find a way to volunteer, when you download Adora you will start seeing volunteer opportunities but we don\'t want you to wait for those either.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Donate Now</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h3>\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, this is what sets us apart, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-10-05 04:24:13','2014-10-05 04:24:13','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(623,1,'2014-10-04 21:45:27','2014-10-04 21:45:27','<h2><img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" />Adora is an Advertising App</h2>\r\nAdvertising is how we fund everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of digital marketing companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, as well as more traditional industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry yet what impact are these platforms making?\r\n\r\nThere is a very important difference between all of these other advertising methods and Adora. We are <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on <strong>doing good</strong> with our advertising revenue, revenue created by our efforts in partnership with our users.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>How the Adora App works</h2>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-591 alignleft\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"246\" height=\"515\" />Traditional advertising, even newer methods like Facebook and Google ads, are not working anymore. Raise your hand if you ignore most every ad around you... You have your hand up don\'t you?\r\n\r\nWe have found an easy way to advertise, a way that is not intrusive, easy to ignore &amp; interact with all at the same time.\r\n\r\nHow you might ask? Well take a look at an example of our ad to the left, yes we know that hulk wouldn\'t really need a band-aid but it is a cool ad. It is a beautiful, full screen ad. It is easy to smile