eone else who might be interested, so we let you <strong>share an ad</strong> with an individual or with all your social media buddies.\r\n\r\nSoon you\'ll be able to do even more right from the lockscreen, you\'ll love what we have coming!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h3>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically <strong>increase user engagement</strong> with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus <strong>increasing our value to advertisers &amp; brands</strong> and therefore<strong> increasing our ability to</strong> <strong>contribute to organizations who do good</strong>.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h3>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to lead a change in corporate social activity by becoming the most charitable company in the world by 2020.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are <strong>donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h3>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that sets us apart. Over the next few months <strong>we will present this mystery to the world</strong>. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this problem and we will share <strong>how we solve it</strong> with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-10-05 00:57:04','2014-10-05 00:57:04','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(643,1,'2014-10-05 00:57:15','2014-10-05 00:57:15','<h3>Adora: A New Option</h3>\r\n<img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" />Advertising is how we fund everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of digital marketing companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, as well as more traditional industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry yet what impact are these platforms making?\r\n\r\nThere is a very important difference between all of these other advertising methods and Adora. We are <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on <strong>doing good</strong> with our advertising revenue, revenue created by our efforts in partnership with our users.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>How the Adora App Works</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LearningSmall.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-641 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LearningSmall.jpg\" alt=\"LearningSmall\" width=\"720\" height=\"400\" /></a> Traditional advertising, even newer methods like Facebook and Google ads, are not working anymore. Raise your hand if you ignore most every ad around you... You have your hand up don\'t you?\r\n\r\nWe have found an easy way to advertise, a way that is not intrusive, easy to ignore &amp; interact with all at the same time.\r\n\r\nHow you might ask? Through the lockscreen on your mobile device! Take a look at an example of our ad (to the left or above), yes we know that hulk wouldn\'t really need a band-aid but it is a cool ad. It is a beautiful, full screen ad. It is easy to smile at and simply move on OR it is just as easy to give it a thumbs up and go view the ad.\r\n\r\nIf you\'ve ever used Pandora for music you know how the <strong>thumbs up / thumbs down</strong> interaction works. You get to let us know when you like an ad or when you don\'t.\r\n\r\nIf an ad is just not interesting <strong>simply ignore it, and unlock your device</strong> and we\'ll get that message too.\r\n\r\nBUT what if you do like the ad but don\'t have time to check it out right now? Simply <strong>Save it for later</strong> (see the folders icon) and unlock the device. You can have this option send you and email or it will just be waiting for you when you open the Adora app.\r\n\r\nWhether you are of aren\'t interested in an ad you may know someone else who might be interested, so we let you <strong>share an ad</strong> with an individual or with all your social media buddies.\r\n\r\nSoon you\'ll be able to do even more right from the lockscreen, you\'ll love what we have coming!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h3>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically <strong>increase user engagement</strong> with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus <strong>increasing our value to advertisers &amp; brands</strong> and therefore<strong> increasing our ability to</strong> <strong>contribute to organizations who do good</strong>.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h3>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to lead a change in corporate social activity by becoming the most charitable company in the world by 2020.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are <strong>donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h3>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that sets us apart. Over the next few months <strong>we will present this mystery to the world</strong>. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this problem and we will share <strong>how we solve it</strong> with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-10-05 00:57:15','2014-10-05 00:57:15','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(645,1,'2014-10-05 00:59:54','2014-10-05 00:59:54','<h3>Adora: A New Option</h3>\r\n<img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" />Advertising is how we fund everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of digital marketing companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, as well as more traditional industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry yet what impact are these platforms making?\r\n\r\nThere is a very important difference between all of these other advertising methods and Adora. We are <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on <strong>doing good</strong> with our advertising revenue, revenue created by our efforts in partnership with our users.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>How the Adora App Works</h3>\r\nTraditional advertising, even newer methods like Facebook and Google ads, are not working anymore. Raise your hand if you ignore most every ad around you... You have your hand up don\'t you?\r\n\r\nWe have found an easy way to advertise, a way that is not intrusive, easy to ignore &amp; interact with all at the same time.\r\n\r\nHow you might ask? Through the lockscreen on your mobile device! Take a look at an example of our ad (to the left or above), yes we know that hulk wouldn\'t really need a band-aid but it is a cool ad. It is a beautiful, full screen ad. It is easy to smile at and simply move on OR it is just as easy to give it a thumbs up and go view the ad.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-641 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LearningSmall.jpg\" alt=\"LearningSmall\" width=\"720\" height=\"400\" />If you\'ve ever used Pandora for music you know how the <strong>thumbs up / thumbs down</strong> interaction works. You get to let us know when you like an ad or when you don\'t.\r\n\r\nIf an ad is just not interesting <strong>simply ignore it, and unlock your device</strong> and we\'ll get that message too.\r\n\r\nBUT what if you do like the ad but don\'t have time to check it out right now? Simply <strong>Save it for later</strong> (see the folders icon) and unlock the device. You can have this option send you and email or it will just be waiting for you when you open the Adora app.\r\n\r\nWhether you are of aren\'t interested in an ad you may know someone else who might be interested, so we let you <strong>share an ad</strong> with an individual or with all your social media buddies.\r\n\r\nSoon you\'ll be able to do even more right from the lockscreen, you\'ll love what we have coming!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h3>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically <strong>increase user engagement</strong> with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus <strong>increasing our value to advertisers &amp; brands</strong> and therefore<strong> increasing our ability to</strong> <strong>contribute to organizations who do good</strong>.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h3>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to lead a change in corporate social activity by becoming the most charitable company in the world by 2020.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are <strong>donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h3>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that sets us apart. Over the next few months <strong>we will present this mystery to the world</strong>. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this problem and we will share <strong>how we solve it</strong> with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-10-05 00:59:54','2014-10-05 00:59:54','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(646,1,'2014-10-05 01:00:52','2014-10-05 01:00:52','<h3>Adora: A New Option</h3>\r\n<img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" />Advertising is how we fund everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of digital marketing companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, as well as more traditional industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry yet what impact are these platforms making?\r\n\r\nThere is a very important difference between all of these other advertising methods and Adora. We are <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on <strong>doing good</strong> with our advertising revenue, revenue created by our efforts in partnership with our users.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>How the Adora App Works</h3>\r\nTraditional advertising, even newer methods like Facebook and Google ads, are not working anymore. Raise your hand if you ignore most every ad around you... You have your hand up don\'t you?\r\n\r\nWe have found an easy way to advertise, a way that is not intrusive, easy to ignore &amp; interact with all at the same time.\r\n\r\nHow you might ask? Through the lockscreen on your mobile device! Take a look at an example of our ad (to the left or above), yes we know that hulk wouldn\'t really need a band-aid but it is a cool ad. It is a beautiful, full screen ad. It is easy to smile at and simply move on OR it is just as easy to give it a thumbs up and go view the ad.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-641 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LearningSmall.jpg\" alt=\"LearningSmall\" width=\"720\" height=\"400\" />If you\'ve ever used Pandora for music you know how the <strong>thumbs up / thumbs down</strong> interaction works. You get to let us know when you like an ad or when you don\'t.\r\n\r\nIf an ad is just not interesting <strong>simply ignore it, and unlock your device</strong> and we\'ll get that message too.\r\n\r\nBUT what if you <strong><em>do</em></strong> like the ad but don\'t have time to check it out right now? Simply <strong>Save it for later</strong> (see the folders icon) and unlock the device. You can have this option send you and email or it will just be waiting for you when you open the Adora app.\r\n\r\nWhether you are of aren\'t interested in an ad you may know someone else who might be interested, so we let you <strong>share an ad</strong> with an individual or with all your social media buddies.\r\n\r\nSoon you\'ll be able to do even more right from the lockscreen, you\'ll love what we have coming!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>Our mission</strong> is simple</h3>\r\n<strong>↑User Engagement → ↑Ad Revenue→ ↑Charitable Giving</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Translation -</strong> Our mission is to dramatically <strong>increase user engagement</strong> with the messages brands present through our unique ad delivery methods thus <strong>increasing our value to advertisers &amp; brands</strong> and therefore<strong> increasing our ability to</strong> <strong>contribute to organizations who do good</strong>.\r\n\r\nThis is our passion - To do as much good as we possibly can.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/GreenView-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"GreenView\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Our Vision</strong></h3>\r\n<strong>It is our vision to lead a change in corporate social activity by becoming the most charitable company in the world by 2020.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be perfectly honest this is not such an outlandish goal, unfortunately. In 2012 the average company donated a median of <strong>0.8% of pre-tax profits, which is less than the normal range of 1% to 1.4%</strong>. Walmart has lead the list of most charitable companies 7 times over the last 8 years with Wells Fargo taking 2011. When both cash and products are taken into account Pfizer has taken the top spot for the last 4 years.\r\n\r\nWe know that these are very large companies but one of our goals is to get to the point where we are <strong>donating more than 50% of our pre-tax profits</strong> to good causes. We want to be very clear that we know it could take us years to get to this point but how fast and much we donate will really be up to the supportive public and brands who want to reach them.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-285\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/StandingApart-300x248.jpg\" alt=\"StandingApart\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>What sets us apart</h3>\r\nThere is more than just our charitable focus that sets us apart. Over the next few months <strong>we will present this mystery to the world</strong>. The mystery of how we can create the most attractive and productive ad for advertisers and for users alike.\r\n\r\nWe have solved this problem and we will share <strong>how we solve it</strong> with all of you soon...\r\n\r\nNo matter how amazing the performance of our ads the charity work we can do far outweighs the impact of our revenue spent in any other way, so <a href=\"http://getadora.com/about/charity/\">read more about how the charity side will work.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you want to learn in more detail how we do this, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://getadora.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us.</a>','The App','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2014-10-05 01:00:52','2014-10-05 01:00:52','',60,'http://getadora.com/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(647,1,'2014-10-05 01:02:57','2014-10-05 01:02:57','<h3>Adora: A New Option</h3>\r\n<img class=\"   alignright\" src=\"http://increasevisibility.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/digital-marketing-banner1.png\" alt=\"Digital Marketing\" width=\"424\" height=\"208\" />Advertising is how we fund everything we do. We are humbled to follow in the footsteps of digital marketing companies like Google, Facebook, Twitter, Yahoo, as well as more traditional industries like Television, Radio, Newspapers, Magazines and even Billboards. Advertising is all around us and it is a multi-billion dollar industry yet what impact are these platforms making?\r\n\r\nThere is a very important difference between all of these other advertising methods and Adora. We are <strong>THE FIRST</strong> main stream advertising platform that is focused on <strong>doing good</strong> with our adve