nding programs go, it is more of a fundraising tool than a formal program.  We like to think of it as a partnership where Adora takes all the economic risks, bears all the overhead, pays all the transaction costs, generates the revenue and leaves our partner charities free to focus on their organizational missions.\r\n\r\nAll a charity needs to do is to indicate an interest in participating by completing the <a title=\"Adora Charity Funding Program Sign-up\" href=\"http://getadora.com/charityprogram\">sign-up form</a>.  Adora will provide an affiliate code and link to share with social media followers and place on the charities direct donation page or other media that reaches their supporters.  Charities benefit proportionally to the degree with which they promote participation.\r\n\r\nCharities Gives Much More Than Just Funding\r\n\r\nThe funds generated by supporters through their ad view revenue and direct donation is only part 1 of a package intended to change the world, one charity and one mobile user at a time.  With exposure and through the time and resources of Adora  k with us on the launch and continual promotion of the app we can have a closer relationship with you. General features of the joint venture:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Free advertising on the network (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You will be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up to and through the holiday season. During this period we will visit some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds donated through Adora. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as for Adora’s use. This will encourage others to do more good.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe will choose a select few to be in on our secret regarding how we will be delivering our ads. We want you to be able to tell others, including those you promote our app to, that we really do have a top secret, cutting edge way to deliver ads that will make this program revolutionary.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner','Adora Helps Charities Do More Good','','inherit','open','open','','560-revision-v1','','','2014-10-08 02:48:40','2014-10-08 02:48:40','',560,'http://getadora.com/560-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(683,3,'2014-10-08 02:50:17','2014-10-08 02:50:17','Adora exists to help you do more good.\n\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-208 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\" alt=\"Charity\" width=\"401\" height=\"244\" /></a>Through Adora we hope to help all of our charitable partners do more good through better exposure, more consistent funding, and increased volunteer involvement.\n\nHere is how it works:\n\nThe Adora Charity Funding Program requires a very simple formal agreement, Adora doesn\'t even need your donor list to engage your supporters, we trust you to do that. When you become a Charity Partner you will be part of our <a title=\"Adora Affiliate Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\">Affiliate Program</a> but with some amazing advantages:\n<ul>\n	<li>Your users will bring you funding for as long as they use the app, no 12-6 month expiration.</li>\n	<li>You will receive free advertising on the network that grows with your Adora user base (Ask us about this)</li>\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\n	<li>You may be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving (coming in 2016).</li>\n</ul>\nThe key to your funding and the scope of all of these benefits will be based on your effort in promoting your Charity on the Adora App.\n\n<strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-652 size-medium\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"Choice\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" /></a>Special Crowdfunding Opportunity</strong>\n\nNow in October, in the next few weeks, we will be lunching a crowdfunding campaign. In this campaign we will be giving 30-50% of our total raised to charities that help us promote the campaign. We\'ll tell you more once you are on board.\n\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This exposure will encourage others to go out and do more good.\n\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\n\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner\n\n<i>*Note: This offer is subject to change at any time, and may no longer be available after October 23rd.</i>\n\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-autosave-v1','','','2014-10-08 02:50:17','2014-10-08 02:50:17','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(684,3,'2014-10-08 02:50:50','2014-10-08 02:50:50','Adora exists to help you do more good.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-208 alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Charity.jpg\" alt=\"Charity\" width=\"401\" height=\"244\" /></a>Through Adora we hope to help all of our charitable partners do more good through better exposure, more consistent funding, and increased volunteer involvement.\r\n\r\nHere is how it works:\r\n\r\nThe Adora Charity Funding Program requires a very simple formal agreement, Adora doesn\'t even need your donor list to engage your supporters, we trust you to do that. When you become a Charity Partner you will be part of our <a title=\"Adora Affiliate Program\" href=\"http://getadora.com/affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\">Affiliate Program</a> but with some amazing advantages:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Your users will bring you funding for as long as they use the app, no 12-6 month expiration.</li>\r\n	<li>You will receive free advertising on the network that grows with your Adora user base (Ask us about this)</li>\r\n	<li>Free ad design consulting</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a Charity specific reporting profile - Track ad performance and donations in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will be made Monthly &amp; Quarterly (75/25 ask us), we pay for transaction fees</li>\r\n	<li>Earn a guaranteed referral fee every month for every user you bring to us</li>\r\n	<li>Donations will not be limited, users will be able to donate as much as they want to your charity</li>\r\n	<li>Listed on the Featured Charity List (users will choose one regardless of referral source)</li>\r\n	<li>Your Charity will eligible for Adora Grant Funding (Ask us)</li>\r\n	<li>You may be invited to be part of the beta Social Network focused on doing good, volunteer work, spontaneous good works, and of course, charitable giving (coming in 2016).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe key to your funding and the scope of all of these benefits will be based on your effort in promoting your Charity on the Adora App.\r\n\r\n<strong><a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-652 size-medium\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Choice-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"Choice\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" /></a>Special Crowdfunding Opportunity</strong>\r\n\r\nNow in October, in the next few weeks, we will be lunching a crowdfunding campaign. In this campaign we will be giving 30-50% of our total raised to charities that help us promote the campaign. We\'ll tell you more once you are on board.\r\n\r\nWe’re planning a very aggressive PR campaign that will lead up through the holiday season. During this period we will be visiting some of our partner charities to record and document the use of funds we’ve donated. These professionally produced videos will be available for your charity to use as well as Adora’s use. This exposure will encourage others to go out and do more good.\r\n\r\nBy partnering with us we will be able to work together to do more good.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to receive more information, please fill out and return the ‘Letter of Interest’ section below and we will contact you to talk about how to become an Adora partner\r\n\r\n<i>*Note: This offer is subject to change at any time, and may no longer be available after October 23rd.</i>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWR8S5X4Z7N\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Charity Funding Program','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2014-10-08 02:50:50','2014-10-08 02:50:50','',68,'http://getadora.com/68-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(685,3,'2014-10-08 02:53:25','2014-10-08 02:53:25','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-591  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a> <a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-592  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a>Adora Advertising is different for one HUGE reason... When anyone looks at our ads they KNOW they are doing good.\n\nWith every other ad platform - Facebook, Google, Twitter, Yahoo, you name it - people are turned off by advertising. They don\'t want it. They didn\'t say \"yes\" to the ads, even if they said \"yes\" to the product or service.\n\nRight now we are preparing to populate our app with ads. Most large brands and ad agencies need us to have a large user base before they will even consider advertising with us, so like many organizations we have the \"Chicken or the egg\" dilemma.\n\nThis is where you get the deal...! We are offering small and medium sized B2C startups/businesses the opportunity to secure excellent advertising at a great price.\n\nRight now, <em>for a limited time,</em> you can test our platform for <strong>FREE</strong>. We are giving away two different ad packages:\n\nSmall Biz Pack -        10,000 impressions\nMedium Biz Pack -   100,000 impressions\n\n<strong>Fill out the interest form below and we\'ll contact you to start the process.</strong>\n\nEXTRA: Starting in November we are going to be Featuring a new business every week, and those businesses will get unlimited* advertising through the end of the year.\n\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWL6X2G4C68\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Advertising','','inherit','open','open','','51-autosave-v1','','','2014-10-08 02:53:25','2014-10-08 02:53:25','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(686,3,'2014-10-08 02:53:55','2014-10-08 02:53:55','<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-591  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.jpg\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a> <a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-592  alignright\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/LockScreenExample1.png\" alt=\"LockScreenExample1\" width=\"191\" height=\"400\" /></a>Adora Advertising is different for one HUGE reason... When anyone looks at our ads they KNOW they are doing good.\r\n\r\nWith every other ad platform - Facebook, Google, Twitter, Yahoo, you name it - people are turned off by advertising. They don\'t want it. They didn\'t say \"yes\" to the ads, even if they said \"yes\" to the product or service.\r\n\r\nRight now we are preparing to populate our app with ads. Most large brands and ad agencies need us to have a large user base before they will even consider advertising with us, so like many organizations we have the \"Chicken or the egg\" dilemma.\r\n\r\nThis is where you get the deal...! We are offering small and medium sized B2C startups/businesses the opportunity to secure excellent advertising at a great price.\r\n\r\nRight now, <em>for a limited time,</em> you can test our platform for <strong>FREE</strong>. We are giving away two different ad packages:\r\n\r\nSmall Biz Pack -        10,000 impressions\r\nMedium Biz Pack -   100,000 impressions\r\n\r\n<strong>Fill out the interest form below and we\'ll contact you to start the process.</strong>\r\n\r\nEXTRA: Starting in November we are going to feature a new business every week, and those businesses will receive unlimited* advertising through the end of the year.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://secure.echosign.com/public/embeddedWidget?wid=AEIRWL6X2G4C68\" type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"JavaScript\"></script>','Adora Advertising','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-10-08 02:53:55','2014-10-08 02:53:55','',51,'http://getadora.com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(687,6,'2014-10-09 17:35:24','2014-10-09 17:35:24','','Make QR Code','','publish','closed','closed','','make-qr-code','','','2014-10-09 17:35:24','2014-10-09 17:35:24','',0,'http://getadora.com/?post_type=surl&#038;p=687',0,'surl','',0),(692,1,'2014-10-16 23:25:47','2014-10-16 23:25:47','<b>TERMS &amp; CONDITIONS</b>\r\n\r\nYou should assume that everything you see or read on the Site or on the Adora mobile app is copyrighted and may not be used except as provided in these Terms &amp; Conditions or in the text on the Site without the express written permission of Adora. This page (together with the documents referred to on it) sets out the Terms &amp; Conditions for use of this web site. We reserve the right, at our discretion, to update or revise these Terms &amp; Conditions without any notice to the user. Please check the Terms periodically for changes.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>INTELLECTU