\"fb-xfbml-parse-ignore\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Download Adora</h1>\n<div class=\"fb-xfbml-parse-ignore\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div class=\"fb-xfbml-parse-ignore\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/adora-charity/id930725815?mt=8#\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-707 aligncenter\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/AppStore.png\" alt=\"Adora Mobile App on the Apple App Store\" width=\"270\" height=\"80\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"fb-xfbml-parse-ignore\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div class=\"fb-xfbml-parse-ignore\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.adoracharity&amp;hl=en\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-708 alignnone\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/PlayStore.png\" alt=\"Adora Mobile App on the Google Play Store\" width=\"270\" height=\"80\" /></a></div>\n</div>','Adora in the News','','inherit','open','open','','857-autosave-v1','','','2015-01-30 00:34:20','2015-01-30 00:34:20','',857,'http://getadora.com/857-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(833,1,'2014-12-26 17:13:58','2014-12-26 17:13:58','Throughout <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/adora-the-lockscreen-charity-app/\" target=\"_blank\">Adora’s Indiegogo Campaign</a> we will be featuring Charities and Nonprofit organizations that are partnering with Adora to help us all do more good. We are so excited to tell you all about <a href=\"http://www.communityactionuc.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Community Action</a>!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignright\" src=\"http://communityactionprovo.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/volunteer-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"311\" height=\"233\" /><strong>Community Action Services and Food Bank</strong> is a non-profit organization that provides a two-step process to solving poverty: first, to <i>stabilize</i> the person and then <i>rebuild </i>their life. Since 1967, the agency has stabilized persons in need by meeting their basic critical needs (such as food and housing) while providing them with the long-term solutions needed to rebuild their financial and social self sufficiency, enabling them to break out of poverty.\r\n\r\nWhat is so exciting about this particular nonprofit is that <b>they will be receiving direct funding from </b><a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/adora-the-lockscreen-charity-app/\" target=\"_blank\"><b>this campaign</b></a><b> to get meals to people in need.</b> Each and every perk that is offered also includes meals for those in need. <img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"http://communityactionprovo.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/DSC_8713.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"309\" height=\"204\" />Through Community Action, Adora will be able to do so much good. They have been helping people for nearly 40 years and have many <a href=\"http://communityactionprovo.org/about-us/poverty-in-utah/success-stories/\" target=\"_blank\">success stories</a> and we are excited to proud to be working with them.\r\n\r\nShow them some love and check them out on <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/communityaction\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/casfb\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> and then grab any of the perks that include a Meal for someone in need to get YOUR funds directly to them while also supporting and helping <a title=\"Download Adora\" href=\"http://getadora.com/download/\" target=\"_blank\">Adora</a>! together Let\'s do some good!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/go/indiegogo \"><img class=\" wp-image-834  aligncenter\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/partnershipdosomegood.jpg\" alt=\"partnershipdosomegood\" width=\"450\" height=\"282\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Adora’s Featured Charity: Community Action Services and Food Bank','','publish','open','open','','featured-charity-community-action','','','2014-12-26 17:56:45','2014-12-26 17:56:45','',0,'http://getadora.com/?p=833',0,'post','',0),(834,1,'2014-12-26 17:06:59','2014-12-26 17:06:59','','partnershipdosomegood','','inherit','open','open','','partnershipdosomegood','','','2014-12-26 17:06:59','2014-12-26 17:06:59','',833,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/partnershipdosomegood.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(835,1,'2014-12-26 17:07:36','2014-12-26 17:07:36','Throughout <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/adora-the-lockscreen-charity-app/\">Adora’s Indiegogo Campaign</a> we will be featuring Charities and Nonprofit organizations that are partnering with Adora to help us all do more good. We are so excited to tell you all about <a href=\"http://www.communityactionuc.org/\">Community Action</a>!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"http://communityactionprovo.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/DSC_8713.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"371\" height=\"246\" />Community Action Services and Food Bank is a non-profit organization in Provo, Utah that provides a two-step process to solving poverty: first, to <i>stabilize</i> the person and then <i>rebuild </i>their life. Since 1967, the agency has stabilized persons in need by meeting their basic critical needs (such as food and housing) while providing them with the long-term solutions needed to rebuild their financial and social self sufficiency, enabling them to break out of poverty.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/go/indiegogo \"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-834 size-full\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/partnershipdosomegood.jpg\" alt=\"partnershipdosomegood\" width=\"391\" height=\"245\" /></a>What is so exciting about this particular nonprofit is that <b>they will be receiving direct funding from </b><a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/adora-the-lockscreen-charity-app/\"><b>this campaign</b></a><b> to get meals to people in need.</b> They have been helping people for nearly 40 years and have many <a href=\"http://communityactionprovo.org/about-us/poverty-in-utah/success-storie