e.jpg\" alt=\"AZTechBeat_Feature\" width=\"626\" height=\"449\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"fb-xfbml-parse-ignore\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://techsmash.net/adora-easiest-way-give-back-world/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-855 alignleft\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/TechSmash_Feature.jpg\" alt=\"TechSmash_Feature\" width=\"764\" height=\"500\" /></a></div>\r\n</div>','Adora in the News','','inherit','open','open','','857-revision-v1','','','2015-01-23 23:05:46','2015-01-23 23:05:46','',857,'http://getadora.com/857-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(875,1,'2015-01-24 00:04:15','2015-01-24 00:04:15','','TechSmashNick&Nate1','','inherit','open','open','','techsmashnicknate1','','','2015-01-24 00:04:15','2015-01-24 00:04:15','',869,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/TechSmashNickNate1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(876,1,'2015-01-24 00:06:34','2015-01-24 00:06:34','','TechSmashNick&Nate3','','inherit','open','open','','techsmashnicknate3','','','2015-01-24 00:06:34','2015-01-24 00:06:34','',869,'http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/TechSmashNickNate3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(877,1,'2015-01-24 00:08:23','2015-01-24 00:08:23','TechSmash is a tech site that covered Adora for our first round of \"Hey Check Us Out\" reaching out and now they\'ve reached right back out to us with a really awesome campaign.\r\n\r\nNick &amp; Nate are two twins who suffer from Mitochondrial Disease, a failure of the mitochondria present in every cell to do it\'s job right. This disease causes early cell injury and death leading to whole systems in the body to fall into failure. These two 8 yr old twins and their family struggle with the effects of this disease every day.\r\n\r\nBUT there is more that can be done to help and the funding provided by TechSmash and Adora can help this family now and long into the future.\r\n\r\nFor those who don\'t know how Adora works here is a simple breakdown:\r\n<blockquote><strong>We let you send advertising revenue that you generate by using the Adora App to a charity or cause of your choice.</strong></blockquote>\r\nThis is also what TechSmash is doing by sending the ad revenue they get from the YouTube video to Nick &amp; Nate.\r\n\r\nSo here is a step by step guide to helping Nick &amp; Nate through the Adora App\r\n\r\nStep 1: Download the Adora App\r\n\r\nYou can do this by searching for \"Adora Charity\" on the app store <strong>or</strong> clicking on one of the links below\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Adora App on the Google Play Store\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.adoracharity&amp;hl=en\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-708\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/PlayStore.png\" alt=\"Adora Mobile App on the Google Play Store\" width=\"270\" height=\"80\" /></a><a title=\"Adora App on the Apple App store\" href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/adora-charity/id930725815\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-707\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/AppStore.png\" alt=\"Adora Mobile App on the Apple App Store\" width=\"270\" height=\"80\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStep 2: Sign in/up\r\n\r\nThere is a short sign up process AND the last step in this process is...\r\n\r\nChoosing a cause and adding a charity of your choice, At the bottom of the options there is a field where you can input a specific cause or charity\r\n\r\nIn this field input \"n&amp;n\" to send your donations to Nick and Nate.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/TechSmashNickNate1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-875\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/TechSmashNickNate1.jpg\" alt=\"TechSmashNick&amp;Nate1\" width=\"300\" height=\"533\" /></a> <a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/TechSmashNickNate3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-876\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/TechSmashNickNate3.png\" alt=\"TechSmashNick&amp;Nate3\" width=\"300\" height=\"533\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStep 3: Then finish your profile!','Help Nick & Nate, A TechSmash Initiative to bring exposure to Mitochondrial Disease','','inherit','open','open','','869-revision-v1','','','2015-01-24 00:08:23','2015-01-24 00:08:23','',869,'http://getadora.com/869-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(878,1,'2015-01-28 00:01:42','2015-01-28 00:01:42','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><em><strong>We have a step-by-step guide for how you can help Nick &amp; Nate through Adora a little further down the page.</strong></em></span></p>\nTechSmash is a tech site that covered Adora for our first round of \"Hey Check Us Out\" reaching out and now they\'ve reached right back out to us with a really awesome campaign.\n\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/NickNate.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-887\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/NickNate.jpg\" alt=\"Nick&amp;Nate\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a>Nick &amp; Nate are twins who suffer from Mitochondrial Disease, a failure of the mitochondria present in every cell to do it\'s job right. This disease causes early cell injury and death leading to whole systems in the body to fall into failure. These two 8 year old and their family struggle with the effects of this disease every day.\n\nBUT there is more that can be done to help and the funding provided by TechSmash and Adora can help this family now and long into the future.\n\nFor those who don\'t know how Adora works here is a simple breakdown:\n<blockquote><strong>We let you send advertising revenue that you generate by using the Adora App to a charity or cause of your choice.</strong></blockquote>\nThis is also what TechSmash is doing by sending the ad revenue they get from the YouTube video to Nick &amp; Nate.\n\nSo here is a step by step guide to helping Nick &amp; Nate through the Adora App\n\n<strong>Step 1: Download the Adora App</strong>\n\nYou can do this by searching for \"Adora Charity\" on the app store <strong>or</strong> clicking on one of the links below\n\n<a title=\"Adora App on the Google Play Store\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.adoracharity&amp;hl=en\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-708\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/PlayStore.png\" alt=\"Adora Mobile App on the Google Play Store\" width=\"270\" height=\"80\" /></a><a title=\"Adora App on the Apple App store\" href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/adora-charity/id930725815\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-707\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/AppStore.png\" alt=\"Adora Mobile App on the Apple App Store\" width=\"270\" height=\"80\" /></a>\n\n<strong>Step 2: Sign in/up</strong>\n\nThere is a short sign up process AND the last step in this process is...\n\nChoosing a cause and adding a charity of your choice. At the bottom of the options there is a field where you can input a specific cause or charity.\n\nIn this field input \"n&amp;n\" then hit the <strong>plus</strong> <strong>sign</strong> to send your donations to Nick and Nate.\n\n<a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/TechSmashNickNate1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-875\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/TechSmashNickNate1.jpg\" alt=\"TechSmashNick&amp;Nate1\" width=\"300\" height=\"533\" /></a> <a href=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/TechSmashNickNate3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-876\" src=\"http://getadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/TechSmashNickNate3.png\" alt=\"TechSmashNick&amp;Nate3\" width=\"300\" height=\"533\" /></a>\n\n<strong>Step 3: Then finish your profile!</strong>\n\nWe want to thank TechSmash for their desire to bring attention to a disease that is not as well known, and for doing it in a way that helps educate people on the amazing concept of using advertising dollars to make an impact on charitable causes and situations!\n\nClick to view the <a href=\"http://techsmash.net/adora-easiest-way-give-back-world\" target=\"_blank\">article about Adora on TechSmash</a> or to view the <a href=\"http://techsmash.net/share-to-help-nick-and-nate/12779\" target=\"_blank\">original post about Nick &amp; Nate on TechSmash</a>.','Help Nick & Nate, A TechSmash Initiative to bring exposure to Mitochondrial Disease','','inherit','open','open','','869-autosave-v1','','','2015-01-28 00:01:42','2015-01-28 00:01:42','',869,'http://getadora.com/869-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(879,1,'2015-01-24 00:13:59','2015-01-24 00:13:59','TechSmash is a tech site that covered Adora for our first round of \"Hey Check Us Out\" reaching out and now they\'ve reached right back out to us with a really awesome campaign.\r\n\r\nNick &amp; Nate are two twins who suffer from Mitochondrial Disease, a failure of the mitochondria present in every cell to do it\'s job right. This disease causes early cell injury and death leading to whole systems in the body to fall into failure. These two 8 yr old twins and their family struggle with the effects of this disease every day.\r\n\r\nBUT there is more that can be done to help and the funding provided by TechSmash and Adora can help this family now and long into the future.\r\n\r\nFor those who don\'t know how Adora works here is a simple breakdown:\r\n<blockquote><strong>We let you send advertising revenue that you generate by using the Adora App to a charity or cause of your choice.</strong></blockquote>\r\nThis is also what TechSmash is doing by sending the ad revenue they get from the YouTube video to Nick &amp; Nate.\r\n\r\nSo here is a step by step guide to helping Nick &amp; Nate through the Adora App\r\n\r\nStep 1: Download the Adora App\r\n\r\nYou can do this by searching for \"Adora Charity\" on the 