te3.png\" alt=\"TechSmashNick&amp;Nate3\" width=\"300\" height=\"533\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Then finish your profile!</strong>\r\n\r\nWe want to thank TechSmash for their desire to bring attention to a disease that is not as well known, and for doing it in a way that helps educate people on the amazing concept of using advertising dollars to make an impact on charitable causes and situations!\r\n\r\nClick to view the <a href=\"http://techsmash.net/adora-easiest-way-give-back-world\" target=\"_blank\">article about Adora on TechSmash</a> or to view the <a href=\"http://techsmash.net/share-to-help-nick-and-nate/12779\" target=\"_blank\">original post about Nick &amp; Nate on TechSmash</a>.','Help Nick & Nate, A TechSmash Initiative to bring exposure to Mitochondrial Disease','','inherit','open','open','','869-revision-v1','','','2015-01-28 00:05:26','2015-01-28 00:05:26','',869,'http://getadora.com/869-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(890,1,'2015-01-30 00:31:01','2015-01-30 00:31:01','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Adora is popping up all over and really gaining momentum! Check out some of our recent appearances in the news and on different blogs and sites!</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><script src=\"http://KPHO.images.worldnow.com/interface/js/WNVideo.js?rnd=514695;hostDomain=www.kpho.com;playerWidth=640;playerHeight=400;isShowIcon=true;clipId=10981845;flvUri=;partnerclipid=;adTag=Video%2520Player;advertisingZone=;enableAds=true;landingPage=;islandingPageoverride=false;playerType=STANDARD_EMBEDDEDscript;controlsType=fixed\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script><a title=\"CBS 5 - KPHO \" href=\"http://www.kpho.com\">CBS 5 - KPHO </a>  \r\n\r\n<div id=\"fb-root\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\r\n\r\n<script>// <![CDATA[\r\n(function(d, s, id) { var js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0]; if (d.getElementById(id)) return; js = d.createElement(s); js.id = id; js.src = \"//connect.facebook.net/en_US/all.js#xfbml=1\"; fjs.parentNode.insertBefore